NK101(de)002:1: // byang chub kyi sems mi nub pa'i rgyal mtshan rdo
NK101(de)002:2: rje sems dpa' nam mkha' che'i 'grel bshad gsang bdag
NK101(de)002:3: dga' rab dpa' bo'i dgongs rgyan zhes bya ba bzhugs
NK101(de)002:4: so // na mo gu ru rat+na b+h+yah khyad chos drug ldan chos sku 'od mi 'gyur //
NK101(de)002:5: lnga ldan longs sku'i mnga' bdag rdo rje sems //
NK101(de)002:6: thugs rje sprul sku'i ston mchog dga' rab rje //
NK101(de)002:7: dbyer med 'khor lo'i mgon la gus btud de //
NK101(de)002:8: theg mchog rdzogs chen rgyud rnams kun gyi bcud //
NK101(de)002:9: yang sprul dpa' bo'i mtshan dpe'i nyi ma mchog /
NK101(de)002:10: gling 'dir shar tshe zhal 'don mdzad bzhin du //
NK101(de)002:11: byung ba'i rmad byung snying po'i don rnams dbye //
NK101(de)002:12: de la 'dir bstan pa yongs kyi snying po /
NK101(de)002:13: gsung rab ma lus pa'i nying khung /
NK101(de)002:14: rgyud thams cad kyi rgyal po /
NK101(de)002:16: man ngag thams cad kyi nges don /
NK101(de)002:17: gsang ba bas kyang ches gsang ba /
NK101(de)002:18: yang gsang rmad du byung ba /
NK101(de)002:19: dngos po thams cad rang grol du gtan la 'bebs par byed pa /
NK101(de)002:20: byang chub kyi sems mi nub pa'i rgyal mtshan rdo
NK101(de)002:21: rje sems dpa' nam mkha' che zhes bya ba 'di
NK101(de)002:22: nyid tshig gi don gyi bshad pa la gsum ste
NK101(de)002:23: / gang zag dbang po rab la mtshan dang phyag 'tshal ba bstan pa /
NK101(de)002:24: 'bring la dkyus kyi sa bcad pa /
NK101(de)002:25: tha ma la yan lag rgyas par bshad pa'o //
NK101(de)002:28: badz+ra swa b+h+aa wa ma h+aa kar+sha k+aa ri ka /
NK101(de)002:30: rdo rje sems dpa' nam mkha' che zhes bya ba /
NK101(de)002:32: rgyal mo tsha ba'i skad du /
NK101(de)002:33: be bo shan ca man tsa go /
NK101(de)002:36: dpe las mtshan du btags pa nam mkha' zhes bya /
NK101(de)002:37: don las mtshan du btags pa rdo rje sems dpa' zhes bya /
NK101(de)002:38: yon tan las mtshan du btags pa che zhes bya ba dang gsum las /
NK101(de)002:39: dang po la 'byung chen gtos kyi nam mkha' 'di
NK101(de)002:40: la mtha' dbus med cing 'pho 'gyur dang bral ba
NK101(de)002:41: / de las cho 'phrul cir yang mi 'gag pa /
NK101(de)002:42: cho 'phrul 'byung yang nam mkha' dang gnyis med pa /
NK101(de)002:43: brtags na ci'i ngo bor yang ma grub pa'i khyad par gyi chos bzhi yod pa ltar /
NK101(de)002:45: gzhi mi 'gyur lhun gyis grub pa'i rdo rje sems dpa'/
NK101(de)002:46: ngo bo ma nges rang rig cir yang gsal ba'i rdo rje sems dpa'/
NK101(de)002:47: don mi 'byed gnyis 'dzin spros pa gcod pa'i rdo rje sems dpa'/
NK101(de)002:48: bdag nyid mi gnas rig pa yul med du grol ba'i rdo rje sems dpa' bzhi dang /
NK101(de)002:50: gzhi lhun grub dmigs mtha' dang bral ba chos nyid dbyings su sangs rgyas pa'i che ba /
NK101(de)002:51: ngo bo nges med rol pa cir yang 'char ba
NK101(de)002:52: bdag nyid chen po dbus mtha' med pa'i che ba
NK101(de)002:53: / don skye med gnyis su med pa de nyid yin pa'i che ba /
NK101(de)002:54: bdag nyid thog mtha' med par rtogs pa mngon du
NK101(de)002:55: gyur pa mngon par sangs rgyas pa'i che ba dang
NK101(de)002:56: bzhi ste / ci ste che na de bzhis a
NK101(de)002:57: nu man chad kyi theg pa 'og ma zil gyi
NK101(de)002:58: bzhi ste / gnon pas so // de yang dpe
NK101(de)002:59: bzhi don bzhi che ba bzhi dbyer med du sbyor
NK101(de)002:60: bzhi ste / gnon pas so // ba yin pas
NK101(de)002:61: / 'o na a ti yo ga bya ba'i che
NK101(de)002:62: ba zla ba khur du byas pa lta bu zhig
NK101(de)002:65: gzhi ngo bo don dang bdag nyid mnyam pa nyid
NK101(de)002:66: phyogs med chen po'i rang bzhin la gang gis kyang
NK101(de)002:68: mnyam pa ris med thams cad nas thams cad du sangs rgyas pa'i che ba ste /
NK101(de)002:69: des rdzogs pa chen po'i che ba bzhi ru 'dzin pa rang yang zil gyis gnon pa yin te /
NK101(de)002:70: byang chub kyi snying po bstan pa las /
NK101(de)002:71: mngon sum snang ba'i rang bzhin ye sangs rgyas //
NK101(de)002:72: de yi mtshan nyid chos dbyings mu mtha' grol //
NK101(de)002:73: de mkhyen ye shes mtha' dbus kun khyab rgyas //
NK101(de)002:74: de nyid de yin de mtshon nges pa'i tshig /
NK101(de)002:75: dgos pas sprad kyi sgra la don mi bzhag /
NK101(de)002:78: rdzogs chen rang gzhung mngon sum par sangs rgyas pas che la /
NK101(de)002:80: nyan thos spong ba dang rang rgyal 'gegs la byang sems kyis spyod pa rnams las che zhing /
NK101(de)002:82: tshogs brgyad yul dang bcas pa nyid //
NK101(de)002:85: rnam pa sgyu mar mngon sum du lhun gyis grub pas che ste /
NK101(de)002:86: ji ltar che na de ltar rtogs pa'i ngang la
NK101(de)002:87: gnas pas bag chags kyi rten kun gzhi grol bas
NK101(de)002:88: / dngos mtshan dang ma rig pa'i mun pa sangs te ye shes phyogs ris med par rgyas pas /
NK101(de)002:89: mtshan nyid sde gsum zil gyis gnon pa'i gnyen pos che bas na /
NK101(de)002:90: de las rdzogs chen rang gzhung mngon par sangs rgyas che /
NK101(de)002:91: spong 'gegs sbyong las tshogs brgyad yul dang bcas /
NK101(de)002:92: rang rig spros bral sgyu mar lhun grub pas //
NK101(de)002:93: der gnas bag chags rten grol dngos mtshan dang //
NK101(de)002:94: ma rig mun sangs ye shes phyogs med rgyas //
NK101(de)002:95: dman pa'i theg pa zil gnon gnyen por che //
NK101(de)002:98: rdzogs pa chen po bdag nyid chen por sangs rgyas pas che la /
NK101(de)002:100: rnal 'byor chen po la sogs rtsol sgrub kyi gzhan
NK101(de)002:101: dbang la ltos nas 'bras bu thob par 'dod pa
NK101(de)002:104: bdag nyid chen por rang nyid ye nas dbang thob zin pas che ste /
NK101(de)002:106: 'og ma'i tshul ngan pa'i rtsol ba sangs nas rang
NK101(de)002:107: rig pa'i ye shes phyogs med du rgyas pas ma
NK101(de)002:108: h+aa zil gyis gnon pa'i gnyen por che bas na
NK101(de)002:110: rnam 'byor chen po la sogs rtsol sgrub kyi //
NK101(de)002:111: gzhan dbang la ltos zil gnon gnyen por yang //
NK101(de)002:112: bdag nyid chen por rang nyid ye dbang bas //
NK101(de)002:113: tshul ngan rtsol sangs rang rig phyogs med rgyas //
NK101(de)002:116: rdzogs pa chen po chos nyid dbyings su sangs rgyas pas che la /
NK101(de)002:118: a nu la sogs rgyu 'bras su 'dod pa'i gnyen por che zhing /
NK101(de)002:120: rgyu rkyen 'bras bu thams cad chos kyi dbyings su ro gcig pas che ste /
NK101(de)002:122: rgyus ma bskyed rang gi ngo bos cir yang mi gnas /
NK101(de)002:123: gnyen pos 'gag pa min pas de ltar 'dod pa sangs la /
NK101(de)002:124: mu bzhi mtha' drug kun mkhyen la rgyu 'bras kyi
NK101(de)002:125: mtshan ma zil gyis gnon pa'i ye shes rgyas pas
NK101(de)002:126: che bas na / de nyid las /
NK101(de)002:127: rjes 'jug la sogs rgyu 'bras gnyen por yang //
NK101(de)002:128: rgyu rkyen 'bras bu chos dbyings ro gcig pas //
NK101(de)002:129: ma bskyed mi gnas 'gag min de 'dod sangs //
NK101(de)002:130: kun mkhyen mtshan ma zil gnon ye shes rgyas //
NK101(de)002:133: rdzogs pa chen po de nyid yin par sangs rgyas pas che la /
NK101(de)002:135: sems dpa' rnal 'byor la sogs blang dor can du 'dod pa las che zhing /
NK101(de)002:137: blang bya dor bya thams cad chos nyid de nyid yin par sangs rgyas pas che ste /
NK101(de)002:139: yin pa blang bya dang min pa dor bya'i phyogs
NK101(de)002:140: ris thams cad sangs la mnyam nyid rang gsal du
NK101(de)002:143: sems dpa'i rnal 'byor la sogs blang dor can //
NK101(de)002:144: zil gnon gnyen po thams cad de yin pas //
NK101(de)002:145: yin min phyogs sangs mnyam nyid rang gsal rgyas //
NK101(de)002:148: de ltar lhun gyis gnas pa'i bde ba chen po
NK101(de)002:149: don dam pa'i ye shes kyi khyad par du 'phags
NK101(de)002:150: te / rtsol ba dang rgyu 'bras dang blang dor
NK101(de)002:151: gyi phyogs gsum la bzlas pas rang gsal du ye
NK101(de)002:153: gzhan sel sangs rgyas dngos po dang mtshan mar 'dod pa dang /
NK101(de)002:154: nyi tshe ba'i stong pa nyid du 'dod pa las grol zhing /
NK101(de)002:155: don gnyer 'bras bu'i de kho na nyid rmongs pa
NK101(de)002:156: la mtshon pa'i dgos pa yod pa'i phyir brda don
NK101(de)002:158: de yang tshig tu btags pa tsam la nges pa'i
NK101(de)002:159: don du 'dod pa de zil gyis gnon pas che
NK101(de)002:161: lhun gnas bde chen don dam ye shes 'phags //
NK101(de)002:162: phyogs gsum la bzlas rang gsal ye sangs rgyas //
NK101(de)002:163: dngos mtshan nyi tshe'i stong pa las grol zhing //
NK101(de)002:164: don nyid rmongs la mtshon phyir brda sprad kyi //
NK101(de)002:165: de yang tshig tsam nges 'dod zil gnon che'o //
NK101(de)002:167: de'ang dang po mngon sum par sangs rgyas pas shes bya'i rang bzhin bstan la /
NK101(de)002:168: bdag nyid chen po dang chos kyi dbyings su sangs rgyas pa gnyis kyis mtshan nyid bstan zhing /
NK101(de)002:169: thams cad de nyid yin par sangs rgyas pas nges tshig bstan nas /
NK101(de)002:170: tha ma sangs rgyas med pa'i che bas rgyas gdab
NK101(de)002:171: ste brda don du 'dzin pa las bkrol ba des
NK101(de)002:172: na che ba lnga ldan gyi rdzogs pa chen po
NK101(de)002:173: zhes bya ste / de nyid las /
NK101(de)002:174: dang pos shes bya'i rang bzhin gnyis mtshan nyid //
NK101(de)002:175: gcig gis nges tshig thams cad rgyas btab pa //
NK101(de)002:176: che lngas khyad 'phags des na rdzogs pa che //
NK101(de)002:179: bcom ldan 'das dpal rdo rje sems dpa' phyag 'tshal lo //
NK101(de)002:181: 'di la bsdus don dang tshig don gnyis las /
NK101(de)002:184: bcom ldan 'das dpal rdo rje sems dpa' la /
NK101(de)002:186: sngon byung du sprul pa'i sku mchog mkhas pa dga'
NK101(de)002:187: rab rdo rje dang rjes 'jug tu 'di la 'jug
NK101(de)002:188: pa rnams kyis / tshul ji ltar na /
NK101(de)002:189: phyi lus kyi phyag yan lag lnga sa la gtug pa'am /
NK101(de)002:190: mar me mdzad kyi brkyang phyag lta bu /
NK101(de)002:191: nang ngag gi phyag dbyangs snyan pa dang tshig tu brjod pa /
NK101(de)002:192: gsang ba yid kyi phyag rtogs pa dbyer med klong du gyur pa chu la bzhag pa lta bu'o //
NK101(de)002:196: don gyi gnas lugs mthong bas na phyag ces bya'o //
NK101(de)002:197: de ltar lus ngag yid gsum gus pa'i tshul du 'tshal lo //
NK101(de)002:199: ya rabs kyi tshul dang mthun te /
NK101(de)002:200: de'i cha rkyen phyag dang zhe sa yin pas dang /
NK101(de)002:201: theg pa 'og ma dang sgo bstun te /
NK101(de)002:202: lha dkon mchog gus pas yul du byas pas dang /
NK101(de)002:203: gzu lums dang ras chod tshar gcod de /
NK101(de)002:204: sngags kyi bla ma dang bde bar gshegs pa gong na gnyen par btud pas dang /
NK101(de)002:205: bar chad med cing yon tan 'byung ste /
NK101(de)002:206: bar chad sel na dam pa chos kyi gru rgyas pa'i dgos ched bzhi dang ldan pa'o //
NK101(de)002:207: gnyis pa gzhi mi 'gyur lhun gyis grub pa'i phyogs med kyis phyogs 'dzin mtha' dag bcos /
NK101(de)002:208: ngo bo ma nges rang byung gi ye shes cir yang 'char bas yon tan phyogs med du ldan /
NK101(de)002:209: don mi 'byed skye ba med pa'i rang bzhin la
NK101(de)002:210: gnyis su med pas mtha' yi rtog pa thams cad
NK101(de)002:211: las 'das / bdag nyid mi gnas thog tha dang
NK101(de)002:212: bral bar chos thams cad kyi 'byung gzhir gyur pas
NK101(de)002:213: las 'das / dpal / 'dus ma byas shing skye 'jig mtha' dag dang bral bas rdo rje /
NK101(de)002:214: rgya chad phyogs lhung med par kun khyab ma bcos par 'od gsal bas sems /
NK101(de)002:215: rtag chad kyi mtha' la mi gnas par mtshan ma thams cad zil gyis gnon pas dpa' ba ni /
NK101(de)002:216: dper na 'jig rten gyi dpa' bos g.yul ngo bzlog pa dang 'dra la /
NK101(de)002:217: de lta bu'i don la goms pa klong du gyur pas na phyag 'tshal ba ste /
NK101(de)002:219: lta ba don dam snying po la //
NK101(de)002:220: ji ltar chu la chu bzhag dang //
NK101(de)002:221: ji ltar mar la mar bzhin du //
NK101(de)002:222: gang gis rang gi ye shes 'di //
NK101(de)002:223: legs mthong gang yin 'dir phyag yin //
NK101(de)002:225: gnyis pa ni lus kyi tshul du mdor bstan pa ste /
NK101(de)002:226: nam mkha' che dbu zhabs kyi don thams cad bsdus pas thig le chen po drug tu 'dus /
NK101(de)002:227: de yang thig le'i ngo bo ni dbyings skye 'gag med pa'i chos kyi sku /
NK101(de)002:228: sems can rang rang gi rig pa byang chub kyi sems so //
NK101(de)002:230: tshig gis ma spros kun la khyab bas thig le /
NK101(de)002:231: gdal ba chen por mtha' dbus med pas thig le /
NK101(de)002:232: grwa zur med par zang thal yin pas thig le /
NK101(de)002:233: kun nas gcig tu bzlums par nyag gcig tu gnas pas thig le zhes bya'o //
NK101(de)002:237: dbyings rnam par dag pa'i thig le //
NK101(de)002:238: ye shes chen po'i thig le /
NK101(de)002:239: kun tu bzang po'i thig le /
NK101(de)002:240: lhun gyis grub pa'i thig le drug go //
NK101(de)002:241: 'o na thig le gcig la dbye ba drug byas pa mi 'gal lam zhe na /
NK101(de)002:242: 'di rnams ra yi rwa ltar so sor reng nge yod na 'gal yang /
NK101(de)002:244: dper na skyes bu rig gnas dang dpa' rtsal sogs
NK101(de)002:245: yon tan gyi gnas dgu dang ldan pa zhig la
NK101(de)002:246: / yul 'joms pa'i ngos nas dpa' bor btags /
NK101(de)002:247: rtsal che ba'i ngos nas rtsa ldan /
NK101(de)002:248: nor mang ba'i ngos nas phyug po /
NK101(de)002:249: 'dun ma'i gzhi'i ngos nas gtso bo /
NK101(de)002:250: rig shes kyi ngos nas bzang po sogs su btags kyang /
NK101(de)002:251: de rnams logs na med par de'i yon tan gyi cha nas btags pa ltar /
NK101(de)002:252: rang rig pa byang chub kyi sems dus gsum du
NK101(de)002:253: 'dus ma byas shing ma skyes pa la chos nyid
NK101(de)002:254: kyi thig le / de kho na la rol pa cir yang mi 'gag pas dbyings kyi thig le /
NK101(de)002:255: de ltar yon tan zad mi shes pas chos nyid
NK101(de)002:256: kyi thig le nam mkha' lta bur ma skyes pa
NK101(de)002:257: dang / dbyings kyi thig le nam mkha'i cho 'phrul lta bur mi 'gag pa gnyis /
NK101(de)002:258: tshig la snga phyi byung yang don la tha dad med /
NK101(de)002:259: mtshon tshul nas res mos mtshon kyang ngo bo la
NK101(de)002:260: skye 'gag gnyis su med de gnyis 'dzin gyi spros
NK101(de)002:262: dbyings rnam par dag pa'i thig le /
NK101(de)002:263: de'i don la shar nub dang phyi nang med pas ye shes chen po'i thig le /
NK101(de)002:264: de la bzang ngan blang dor dang dgag sgrub skyon yon med pas kun tu bzang po'i thig le /
NK101(de)002:265: de ru thams cad 'dus shing mtha' ma spangs rang
NK101(de)002:266: sar grol bas lhun gyis grub pa'i thig le zhes
NK101(de)002:268: ma bcos pa las yon tan mtha' dag rdzogs //
NK101(de)002:269: shar tshad don dang bcas te ye nas dag /
NK101(de)002:270: de mkhyen rang gsal de la phyogs ris grol //
NK101(de)002:271: ma btsal gdod nas rdzogs pa'i bla dwags yin //
NK101(de)002:275: mtshan nyid 'dzin cing ngo bos khyad par 'dzin //
NK101(de)002:276: snang myong rigs pa'i chos las dkar spyod kyis //
NK101(de)002:277: ltung ba las 'dzin de dag gnas lugs nyid //
NK101(de)002:278: rang bzhin spros pa kun bral nyid nges te //
NK101(de)002:279: de mkhyen mtshan nyid rang rig ye shes nyid //
NK101(de)002:280: de yi rnam pa thugs rje'i sprul par shar //
NK101(de)002:281: sgyu ma rtsal 'dzin rdo rje btsan po mchog /
NK101(de)002:282: gdod nas 'du 'bral med par rdzogs pa che //
NK101(de)002:283: de min mu bzhi mtha' brgyad 'khor 'das chos //
NK101(de)002:284: cir yang 'char bar mi rigs de yi phyir //
NK101(de)002:285: chos kyi chos nyid gnas lugs der rigs pa'o //
NK101(de)002:286: gnas skabs chos nyid 'khrul snang rang mtshan nyid //
NK101(de)002:287: sa sra chu gsher me tsha rlung yang g.yo //
NK101(de)002:288: zhe sdang kun nas mnar sems la sogs pa //
NK101(de)002:289: kun nas ma 'dres ye gnas so sor shar //
NK101(de)002:290: spyi mtshan mi rtag sdug bsngal stong bdag med //
NK101(de)002:292: chos can rnams kyi chos nyid spyi dang rang gi
NK101(de)002:293: mtshan nyid 'dzin cing las rnam par dkar bas ltung
NK101(de)002:295: rigs pas bden pa'i don 'dzin pa dang /
NK101(de)002:296: ngo bo yis khyad par gyis chos 'dzin pas chos zhes bya la /
NK101(de)002:297: bzhi po de yi gnas lugs ni /
NK101(de)002:300: rang bzhin ngos bzung med pa las mi 'da' bas /
NK101(de)002:301: des mtshon pa dngos po'i rkyen du chos nyid ces
NK101(de)002:302: bya ba yin pas nges na mtshan ma ru 'dzin
NK101(de)002:303: pa dang / rgyu 'bras su 'dzin pa dang /
NK101(de)002:304: gnas skabs kyi rigs pa bden par 'dzin pa dang /
NK101(de)002:305: ngo bo chos can dang khyad par gyi chos su
NK101(de)002:306: 'dzin pa rnams kyi 'dod pa'i spros pa gcod pas
NK101(de)002:308: de'ang chos bzhi po rang re'i rang bzhin lhun grub
NK101(de)002:309: gsum las gzhan du mi 'gyur bar spros pa ye
NK101(de)002:310: nas med pas / chos bzhi po de dag dor
NK101(de)002:311: ba min gyi ngang tshul lhun grub gsum po de
NK101(de)002:315: rang mtshan ltung ba rigs pas ngo bo yis //
NK101(de)002:316: khyad par 'dzin pas chos rnams de yi gnas lugs ni //
NK101(de)002:317: rang gsal lhun grub ngos med las mi 'da' //
NK101(de)002:318: des mtshon dngos po'i rkyen du chos nyid ces //
NK101(de)002:319: des na mtshan ma rgyu 'thas gnas skabs rigs //
NK101(de)002:320: chos can chos nyid 'dod pa'i spros pa gcod //
NK101(de)002:321: rang re'i rang bzhin mi 'gyur spros pa med //
NK101(de)002:322: de dag dor min ngang tshul de lta'o //
NK101(de)002:325: de ltar chos thams cad kyi ngang tshul rnam par
NK101(de)002:326: dag pa'i chos nyid de yang sangs rgyas kyi yon
NK101(de)002:327: tan dang bstan pa rgya mtsho'i 'byung gnas kyi yon
NK101(de)002:328: tan gzhir gnas su ye nas rdzogs pas /
NK101(de)002:329: chad pa nyi tshe ba'i spros pa'i mtha' las kyang 'das pa yin te /
NK101(de)002:330: des na gzhir gnas kyi chos nyid chad pa nyi
NK101(de)002:331: tshe'i spros pa las te rol pa cir yang mi
NK101(de)002:332: 'gags pas dbyings kyi thig ler rdzogs pa'o //
NK101(de)002:334: de ltar ngang tshul rnam par dag pa nyid //
NK101(de)002:335: bstan pa rgya mtsho'i 'byung gnas gzhir gnas rdzogs //
NK101(de)002:336: chad pa nyi tshe'i spros pa'ang 'das pa ste //
NK101(de)002:337: chos nyid dbyings kyi thig le rdzogs pa'o //
NK101(de)002:340: kun gyi 'byung gnas su gyur pa de tshe nyid
NK101(de)002:341: na'ang 'byung ba'i sa dang 'byung ba'i tshul dang 'byung
NK101(de)002:342: ba po'i dbyings kyi phyogs ris dang kun brtags thams
NK101(de)002:343: cad rang bzhin gyis rnam par dag pas /
NK101(de)002:344: dbyings zhes chad stong gi spros pa gcod pa'i dgos pas tha snyad du btags kyis /
NK101(de)002:345: rang ngo ye nas rnam par dag pas /
NK101(de)002:346: spros pa yod do cog thams cad kyang rnam par
NK101(de)002:347: bcad pa'i ngang yin pas dbyings rnam par dag pa'i
NK101(de)002:350: de tshe nyid na 'byung ba 'byung tshul 'byung //
NK101(de)002:351: phyogs ris kun brtags rnam par rang dag pas //
NK101(de)002:352: dbyings zhes dgos pas brtags kyis ye dag pas //
NK101(de)002:353: spros pa'o cog kyang rnam par bcad pa'i ngang //
NK101(de)002:356: gshis kyi gnas lugs de dag mkhyen pa ni /
NK101(de)002:357: rang rig pa'i ngo bo rang 'od gsal ba'i ye shes yin pas /
NK101(de)002:358: nyan thos ltar spang ba dang /
NK101(de)002:359: rang rgyal ltar dgag pa dang /
NK101(de)002:360: byang chub ltar sbyong ba dang /
NK101(de)002:361: gsang sngags ltar rtsol ba'i spros pa thams cad ye nas gsal sgrib med par rang grol bas /
NK101(de)002:362: gshis la phyogs ris med par mkhyen pas rtsol brgyad
NK101(de)002:363: las khyad par can du gyur par rang shar ba
NK101(de)002:364: ni ye shes chen po'i thig le yin te /
NK101(de)002:366: de mkhyen rang rig 'od gsal ye shes pas //
NK101(de)002:367: spang dgag sbyong rtsol spros pa ye gsal grol //
NK101(de)002:368: phyogs ris med par mkhyen pas khyad par can //
NK101(de)002:369: rang shar ye shes chen po'i thig le yin //
NK101(de)002:372: de la phyogs ris med par dgag sgrub dang blang dor thams cad bral te /
NK101(de)002:373: chos thams cad ye nas byang chub kyi sems bde ba chen po yin pas /
NK101(de)002:379: gang yang min par 'dod pa'i spros pa thams cad bcad pas /
NK101(de)002:380: bde ba chen por thams cad shong bas yangs pa chen po kun tu bzang po'i thig le ste /
NK101(de)002:382: de la phyogs ris dgag sgrub blang dor bral //
NK101(de)002:383: thams cad ye nas byang sems bde chen pas //
NK101(de)002:384: yod med yin min 'dod pa'i spros pa bcad //
NK101(de)002:385: bde chen yangs pa chen po'i thig le'o //
NK101(de)002:388: de yi rol pa'i rgyan du thams cad rdzogs te
NK101(de)002:389: sgyu ma ltar yul gyi rnam pa kun kyang nges
NK101(de)002:390: pa med pa'i rol bar lhun gyis grub pas rigs
NK101(de)002:391: kyi khyad par du mar rang shar pa las /
NK101(de)002:397: a nus sgrub pa las grol bas lhun gyis gnas
NK101(de)002:398: pa'i bde ba chen por rdzogs pa'i phyir lhun gyis
NK101(de)002:401: de yi rol pa rgyan rdzogs sgyu ma ltar //
NK101(de)002:402: rnam pa lhun grub rigs kyi khyad par shar //
NK101(de)002:403: spong 'gegs sbyongs sgyur rtsol sgrub las grol bas //
NK101(de)002:404: lhun gnas bde chen rdzogs pa'i thig le'o //
NK101(de)002:406: de'ang dang po gsum gyis gshis bstan la /
NK101(de)002:407: ye shes chen pos ngo bo bstan cing /
NK101(de)002:408: tha ma gnyis kyis ye shes dang gshis kyi yon tan bstan pa ste /
NK101(de)002:410: gsum gyis gshis bstan gcig gis ngo bo bstan //
NK101(de)002:411: gnyis kyis yon tan khyad par dam pa bstan //
NK101(de)002:413: drug po de yang sems nyid gcig pu'i ngos nas btags pa ma gtogs pa /
NK101(de)002:414: don logs pa zhig ka nas ma grub bo //
NK101(de)002:415: don de legs par go na nam mkha' che dbu zhabs kyi don thams cad de ru 'dus so //
NK101(de)002:416: gsum pa yan lag gi tshul du rgyas par bshad na /
NK101(de)002:417: skabs nyi shu rtsa bdun gyis ston pa yin te /
NK101(de)002:418: dang po chos nyid kyi skabs nas /
NK101(de)002:419: mtha' lung 'grel ba ming tsam brdar bstan pa'i skabs yan chad la zer te /
NK101(de)002:421: skabs zhes bya ba'i man ngag ni //
NK101(de)002:422: sems nyid rdzogs pa'i snying po de //
NK101(de)002:423: sgrib med rang byung ye shes la //
NK101(de)002:424: chos kun dus gsum sgrib med pas //
NK101(de)002:425: chos nyid don la 'gag pa med //
NK101(de)002:426: so so dag gis go skabs 'byed //
NK101(de)002:427: des na skabs zhes bstan pa yin //
NK101(de)002:429: sems kyi chos nyid de rnams la //
NK101(de)002:430: ma 'gags pa yi skabs zhes bya //
NK101(de)002:431: zhes gsungs pas de rnams gsal bar bshad pa ste /
NK101(de)002:432: de yang rdo rje sems dpa' nam mkha' che la /
NK101(de)002:436: phyag rgya nyi shu rtsa lnga zhes su grags pa las /
NK101(de)002:437: da res man ngag klong chen gyi lugs kyis /
NK101(de)002:438: phyag rgya so sor mi 'dod par 'phrul gyi gzer
NK101(de)002:439: bu rnam pa lngas mi 'gyur bar rgyas 'debs par
NK101(de)002:440: byed pa'i gnad kyis go sa bye brag tu mi
NK101(de)002:441: 'byed par shugs chod du 'dod pas phyag rgya yang
NK101(de)002:443: 'o na skabs dang thig le'i sa gcod du mi 'dogs pa 'thad dam snyam na /
NK101(de)002:444: 'di ka rang lugs kyi sa gcod du 'thad de /
NK101(de)002:445: skabs dang thig le gnyis kyis dkyus kyi go skabs phye nas 'byung bas so //
NK101(de)002:446: de nyid nying lag gi tshul du shin tu rgyas par bshad pa la /
NK101(de)002:447: skabs re re la'ang dpe don rigs pa gtan tshigs
NK101(de)002:448: bzhi bzhis ston pas dgongs pa nyi shu rtsa bdun
NK101(de)002:449: gyis chos nyid nyams su blang pa dang gcig /
NK101(de)002:450: mthun dpe nyi shu rtsa bdun gyis chos nyid dpe yis mtshon tshul dang gnyis /
NK101(de)002:451: rigs pa nyi shu rtsa bdun gyis chos nyid kyis 'thad pa sgrub pa dang gsum /
NK101(de)002:452: gtan tshigs nyi shu rtsa bdun gyis chos nyid gtan la dbab pa dang bzhi'o //
NK101(de)002:453: de ltar rtsa bdun phrag bzhis ston pa las /
NK101(de)002:454: skabs dang thig le dang po la /
NK101(de)002:456: gzhi ji bzhin pa rang lugs chen po'i dgongs pa
NK101(de)002:457: nam mkha' ltar khyab gdal chen po'i klong du bstan
NK101(de)002:458: pa / ngo bo rang dang gzhan gyi tha snyad
NK101(de)002:459: las 'das te chos thams cad kyi bdag nyid yin
NK101(de)002:461: bya rtsol dang bral ba'i gtan tshigs bstan pa //
NK101(de)002:462: thig le'i nges tshig bstan pa dang lnga las /
NK101(de)002:464: chos nyid kyi skabs zhes te /
NK101(de)002:465: chos nyid ni rgyu rkyen las ka nas ma byung ste /
NK101(de)002:466: 'dus byas kyi gnyen por 'gyur mi srid pas /
NK101(de)002:467: rig pa byang chub kyi sems nyid sangs rgyas sgam ste ma mdzad /
NK101(de)002:468: sems can sgrin te ma bcos /
NK101(de)002:469: gzhi phyi mo dngos po gshis kyi gnas lugs /
NK101(de)002:470: nam mkha' lta bu rgya chad dang phyogs lhung med
NK101(de)002:471: par kun la khyab pa nyid ston pa'i skabs la
NK101(de)002:474: ji ltar snang ba'i chos rnams kun //
NK101(de)002:475: ye nas 'dus byas ma yin pas //
NK101(de)002:476: chos nyid dag tu gnas pa de //
NK101(de)002:477: chos nyid skabs zhes bstan pa yin //
NK101(de)002:480: rdo rje sems dpa' nam mkha' che //
NK101(de)002:481: zhes pa la sogs pa ste /
NK101(de)002:486: de kho na nyid kyi 'dug tshul /
NK101(de)002:487: lhun gyis grub pa'i chos nyid yin te /
NK101(de)002:488: dngos po'i gnas lugs ni cir yang gnas pa yin /
NK101(de)002:489: rang byung gi ye shes ni cir yang 'byung ba /
NK101(de)002:490: shes bya'i gshis ni sus kyang ma bcos pa /
NK101(de)002:491: de kho na nyid kyi 'dug tshul ni cir yang 'dug pa /
NK101(de)002:492: lhun gyis grub pa'i chos nyid ni cir yang grub
NK101(de)002:493: pa ste de la gzhi ji bzhin pa zhes zer
NK101(de)002:494: ro // rang lugs chen po ni /
NK101(de)002:495: sems can la sangs rgyas rang lugs /
NK101(de)002:500: nyon mongs la ye shes rang lugs su gnas pas sus kyang bcos bsgyur byar med /
NK101(de)002:501: dgongs pa ni ma bcos pa'i ngang ngo //
NK101(de)002:502: nam mkha' lta bu khyab gdal chen po'i klong ni /
NK101(de)002:503: nam mkha' la mtha' dbus dang 'pho 'gyur med pa bzhin du /
NK101(de)002:504: chos nyid la rgya chad dang phyogs lhung med pas nam mkha' lta bu la /
NK101(de)002:505: khyab gdal chen po'i klong ni /
NK101(de)002:506: mtho ste yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas nas /
NK101(de)002:507: dma' ste dmyal ba'i gting yan chad la /
NK101(de)002:508: chos nyid de dbri bsnan che chung bzang ngan med
NK101(de)002:509: par gnas pas ma bcos pa'i klong du bstan pa
NK101(de)002:510: zhes bya'o // de la bdag gzhan gnyis su ma grub pas /
NK101(de)002:511: ngo bo rang dang gzhan gyi tha snyad las 'das pa'i rigs pa /
NK101(de)002:512: de la 'bras bu gzhan nas rtsol du med pas
NK101(de)002:513: rtsol ba dang bral ba'i gtan tshigs bstan pa yin
NK101(de)002:515: rdo rje sems dpa' nam mkha' che zhes 'pho 'gyur med pa'i dgongs pa bstan te /
NK101(de)002:517: btags pa ming gi rdo rje tsam la mi bya bar /
NK101(de)002:518: sems can rang rang gi rig pa byang chub kyi sems de nyid /
NK101(de)002:519: 'dus ma byas shing skye 'jig med pas rdo rje /
NK101(de)002:520: dbyer mi phyed pas na'ang rdo rje /
NK101(de)002:521: mtha' thams cad 'joms pas na'ang rdo rje ste /
NK101(de)002:522: dper na rdo rje pha lam gyis phar la sra ba'i dngos po thams cad gcod cing 'bigs la /
NK101(de)002:523: tshur la gang gis kyang mi chod cing mi shigs pa ltar ro //
NK101(de)002:524: sems ni gsal ba rgyun mi 'chad pas dang /
NK101(de)002:525: ma bcos par 'od gsal ba yin la /
NK101(de)002:526: dpa' ba ni rtag chad kyi mtha' thams cad 'joms pa dang /
NK101(de)002:527: mtshan ma'i chos mtha' dag zil gyis gnon pas /
NK101(de)002:528: 'jig rten na dpa' bo lta bu la bya ste /
NK101(de)002:529: de yi 'byung chen gtos kyi nam mkhas thams cad kyi go 'byed pa ltar /
NK101(de)002:530: rdo rje gsang ba'i nam mkha' ni chos nyid yin te /
NK101(de)002:531: 'khor 'das snang srid kyi go 'byed pa dang /
NK101(de)002:532: mi g.yo zhing ltos pa med pas 'byung ba thams cad las nam mkha' che ba ltar /
NK101(de)002:533: 'khor 'das theg pa thams cad las chos nyid che
NK101(de)002:534: ba ste che ba lnga'i don ni bshad zin la
NK101(de)002:535: / des na yangs dog med pa'i dgongs pa bstan te /
NK101(de)002:536: kun bzang yangs pa chos kyi dbyings //
NK101(de)002:537: zhes ma 'dres pa dang yongs su rdzogs pa la bya ste /
NK101(de)002:538: ngo bo ma nges cir yang 'char bas so sor ma 'dres la /
NK101(de)002:539: gzhi mi 'gyur lhun gyis grub par thams cad gcig
NK101(de)002:540: pas yongs su rdzogs te don skye med gnyis su
NK101(de)002:541: med cing bdag nyid chen po bsam gyis mi khyab
NK101(de)002:542: pa'o // de na yang sprul dga' rab rdo rje'i
NK101(de)002:543: zhal snga nas bka' stsal ba'i klong chen rab 'byams
NK101(de)002:544: pa'o // las / rang bzhin lhun gyis grub pa chos nyid gzhi yi klong /
NK101(de)002:545: ngo bo nges pa med par rang byung ye shes klong /
NK101(de)002:546: don la skye ba med pas gnyis su med pa'i klong /
NK101(de)002:547: bdag nyid thog mtha' med pas 'bras bu ye grub klong /
NK101(de)002:548: zhes gsungs pa ltar gzhi ngo bo don bdag nyid
NK101(de)002:549: gcig gi rang bzhin bzang ngan blang dor med pas
NK101(de)002:550: kun bzang / lhun gyis grub pa'i klong la gang yang ma bkag pas yangs pa /
NK101(de)002:551: mu mtha' med cing zad mi shes pas chos kyi dbyings so //
NK101(de)002:552: rnam dag lam chen kun grol phyir //
NK101(de)002:553: zhes rnam par dag pa'i dgongs pa bstan te /
NK101(de)002:554: gzhi mi 'gyur lhun gyis grub pa'i chos nyid la
NK101(de)002:555: phyogs 'dzin gyi spros pa thams cad rnam par dag
NK101(de)002:556: pas dang / ngo bo ma nges rig pa rang
NK101(de)002:557: byung gi ye shes kyi skye 'gag med pa la
NK101(de)002:558: gnyis 'dzin gyi spros pa gang yang gdod ma nas
NK101(de)002:559: rang bzhin gyis rnam par dag go //
NK101(de)002:560: rgyal 'gro lam pas bsdus pa thams cad kyi 'byung gzhir gyur pas dang /
NK101(de)002:561: mtho dman med par gcig tu 'gro ba'i lam chen /
NK101(de)002:562: ye grol chen por sangs rgyas pa dang /
NK101(de)002:563: bzang ngan med pa'i klong du grol bas kun grol phyir zhes so //
NK101(de)002:564: ma skyes mi 'gag cir mi dgongs //
NK101(de)002:565: zhes skye 'gag med pa'i dgongs pa bstan te /
NK101(de)002:566: don skye ba med pa'i rang bzhin la bsgoms pas
NK101(de)002:567: nyams myong mi skye ste nges shes rang rgyud pa
NK101(de)002:569: chos nyid skye med la ngo bo cir yang mi
NK101(de)002:570: 'gag pas ma bsgoms kyang ye shes mi 'gag ste
NK101(de)002:571: / snang ba mi 'gag la rol pa cir yang 'char bas /
NK101(de)002:572: skye 'gag gnyis med kyi chos nyid bsam pas bzung
NK101(de)002:573: bas blo yi rtsol ba dang bral ba'i gnad kyis
NK101(de)002:574: yul cir yang mi dgongs pa'i dgongs pa chen po'o
NK101(de)002:575: // 'o na de ltar bu'i dgongs pa de la ched du bsgom bya yod dam med /
NK101(de)002:576: yod na theg pa 'og ma pa dang khyad med du 'gyur la /
NK101(de)002:577: med na so skyes rang ga ma dang khyad par med par thal lo zhe na /
NK101(de)002:578: skyon rang byung ye shes kyis bsal ba dang /
NK101(de)002:579: la skye 'gag med par bzla ba ste /
NK101(de)002:580: bsgoms kyang skyon med rang byung rol pa /
NK101(de)002:581: ma bsgoms skyon med mtshan ma rang grol /
NK101(de)002:582: mdor na bsgoms ma bsgoms gnyis su med par chos
NK101(de)002:583: nyid kyi klong na lhod de shigs se gnas pa
NK101(de)002:584: de yi klong chen po'i ting nge 'dzin te bsgoms
NK101(de)002:585: kyang nyams myong mi skye chos nyid gnyis med du
NK101(de)002:586: la zlo / ma bsgoms kyang ye shes mi 'gag chos nyid 'gag med du la zlo /
NK101(de)002:587: dus dang rnam pa kun tu bsgoms dang ma bsgoms
NK101(de)002:588: med par bde ba chen po 'pho 'gyur med pa'i
NK101(de)002:589: klong las gzhan du 'char sa med pas la skye
NK101(de)002:590: 'gag med par de ltar bzla ste /
NK101(de)002:591: 'di ni kun la shes par bya'o //
NK101(de)002:592: spyir brgyud srol 'di la sprul pa'i lo ts+aa ba
NK101(de)002:593: chen po'i bee ro tsa nas g.yu sgra snying po
NK101(de)002:594: la gdams pa'i bsam gtan don gsum pa las /
NK101(de)002:595: snying po ji ltar gnas pa las /
NK101(de)002:596: sgro skur ma yin don mthun nyid //
NK101(de)002:597: rang gi tshogs brgyad skye ba gsum //
NK101(de)002:598: gtan tshigs tshad ma rigs pa sgras //
NK101(de)002:599: gzhigs 'jal brtags mtshon brgyud pa yis //
NK101(de)002:600: gtan la phab ste lung las gcad //
NK101(de)002:601: ces gsungs pas sgra dang tshad ma brgyud pa'i lung bzhin du sbyar na /
NK101(de)002:603: tshad ma mngon sum rjes su dpag pas kyang //
NK101(de)002:604: rang mtshan spyi yi rnam pa de 'thad sgrub //
NK101(de)002:605: snang la mi rtog don la ma 'khrul bar //
NK101(de)002:606: sgo lngas yul lda rnam pa sgyu mar bcad //
NK101(de)002:607: sdug bsngal rtsol bsgrub bcas tshe nges shes 'char //
NK101(de)002:608: sprul sku ma brtsal gnas pa 'thad pas grub //
NK101(de)002:609: yid kyi ye shes zin dang ma bzung bar //
NK101(de)002:610: spros pa'i rang bzhin spros bral nyid du zin //
NK101(de)002:611: bsam gyis mi khyab dus su nges shes 'char //
NK101(de)002:612: chos sku ma brtsal gnas pa 'thad pas sgrub //
NK101(de)002:613: rang rig mngon sum ngar 'dzin nyon mongs tshe //
NK101(de)002:614: sings kyis rig la gang du'ang mi rtog par //
NK101(de)002:615: rang rig bde chen shar dus nges shes 'char //
NK101(de)002:616: longs sku lhun gyis gnas pa 'thad pas grub //
NK101(de)002:617: rang rig stong nyid sprul pa'i rnam pa can //
NK101(de)002:618: rang la gnas pas bag chags rnyog gzhi dwangs //
NK101(de)002:619: rnal 'byor shin tu rdzogs gsal sku gsum ngang //
NK101(de)002:620: rtog pa rang grol ye shes ma 'khrul 'thad //
NK101(de)002:621: de ltar rang mtshan rdzogs chod ma nus la //
NK101(de)002:622: 'khrul snang 'bras bu ngo bo nyid kyi rgyu //
NK101(de)002:623: byang chub sems de lhun gyis gnas par dpag /
NK101(de)002:624: rnam shes tshogs brgyad yul dang bcas pa yi //
NK101(de)002:625: rang bzhin ye nas stong gsal sprul par bcas //
NK101(de)002:626: nor ba med pas ma bcos rang bzhin dpag /'khrul shes yul dang bcas pa de bden na //
NK101(de)002:627: de yis grol bar rigs te de sdug bsngal //
NK101(de)002:628: rigs pa'i yul dang rgyal ba'i dgongs pa dang //
NK101(de)002:629: rnal 'byor dgongs pa'i ngo na de mi dmigs //
NK101(de)002:630: nges don gshis la'ang mi dmigs de rjes dpag /
NK101(de)002:631: gnas skabs 'khrul snang rigs pas yul shes pa //
NK101(de)002:632: grub kyang nges pa'i rigs pas de mi 'thad //
NK101(de)002:633: 'khrul ngor 'thad phyir don dang 'gal bar nges //
NK101(de)002:634: thag pa sbrul du 'dzin pa 'khrul pa bzhin //
NK101(de)002:635: tha snyad tshig gi sgro skur des bsal la //
NK101(de)002:636: nges don rang rig nyams la gnas par bya'o //
NK101(de)002:637: mtshan ma kun rdzob zhes pa las grol ba'i //
NK101(de)002:638: kun bral ji ma spangs pa'i rang rigs pa //
NK101(de)002:639: thams cad yul med kun gsal stong nyid de //
NK101(de)002:640: de yang dgos pas tha snyad brjod pa tsam //
NK101(de)002:642: de yang blo gros kyi rtsal dang bstun te tshad ma gnyis kyis 'jal ba'i tshul yang /
NK101(de)002:643: slob dpon chen po 'jam dpal bshes gnyen gyis /
NK101(de)002:644: don nyid sgro bral mngon sum la //
NK101(de)002:645: ma mthong cha gzhan lus med pas //
NK101(de)002:646: rtags la brten pas dpag tu med //
NK101(de)002:647: de ldan rigs rgyud chig chod pa'o //
NK101(de)002:648: gzhan du rtags tsam 'dzin pa yang //
NK101(de)002:649: shes bya kun la 'jug nus la //
NK101(de)002:650: de la'ang snying po ma dmigs pas //
NK101(de)002:651: 'jug mkhan rang rig ye shes la //
NK101(de)002:652: shes bya de nyid rnam pa ste //
NK101(de)002:654: rang bzhin dmigs pa kun grol ba //
NK101(de)002:655: ma 'dres yongs rdzogs spyi tsam dpag /
NK101(de)002:656: bsam sgom gnyis kyis bsring bskyed drang //
NK101(de)002:657: de yi rang bzhin de yin pas //
NK101(de)002:659: phal cher de la brten dgos te //
NK101(de)002:660: log stobs nus rtsal rgyas phyir ro //
NK101(de)002:664: de yi mtshan nyid ci 'drar sems //
NK101(de)002:665: gshis nyid dgos pas ming btags kyis //
NK101(de)002:667: der gnas nyams dang 'dir de bzhin //
NK101(de)002:668: rang gi mtshan nyid brjod bya min //
NK101(de)002:669: bu ram mngar bar btags pa ltar //
NK101(de)002:670: 'on kyang rmongs la don mtshon phyir //
NK101(de)002:671: don la dmigs dang sgra la byung //
NK101(de)002:672: mthun par gsal la thun mong du //
NK101(de)002:673: grags pa'i sgra yis mngon par zhen //
NK101(de)002:674: brjod na bde gsal ngos med mkhyen //
NK101(de)002:675: zhes pa rnams sbyar te kun la shes par bya'o //
NK101(de)002:677: byams pas don ni rnam sbyangs phyir //
NK101(de)002:679: don chos nyid kyi rigs pa bstan te /
NK101(de)002:680: byams pa chen po ni chos nyid ma dang 'dra
NK101(de)002:681: bas 'khor 'das thams cad kyi gzhi ma byas nas
NK101(de)002:683: don chos nyid phyogs med kyi byas pas rnam par
NK101(de)002:684: rtog pa phyogs su 'dzin pa thams cad ka nas
NK101(de)002:685: dag zin pas rnam par sbyangs pa'i phyir na /
NK101(de)002:686: snying rje chen po cir mi mdzad //
NK101(de)002:687: ces yul dang yul can med pa'i rigs pa bstan te /
NK101(de)002:688: theg pa 'og ma pa bzhin du sems can la
NK101(de)002:689: dmigs pa'i snying rje chung ngu ni rdul tsam yang
NK101(de)002:690: mi dmigs te / a ti yo ga rig pa
NK101(de)002:691: yul med phyogs bral nges med du shar ba'i snying
NK101(de)002:692: mi dmigs te / rje chen po'o // des na
NK101(de)002:693: 'og ma bzhin du che chung dang dmigs gtad cir
NK101(de)002:695: che bas che ba zab mo yi //
NK101(de)002:697: gnyis su med pa'i rigs pa bstan te /
NK101(de)002:698: 'di la rdzogs pa chen po thog bab kyi gdams ngag zer te /
NK101(de)002:699: snang srid 'byung ba khro ba las che ba ni
NK101(de)002:700: chos nyid mya ngan las 'das pa yin la de
NK101(de)002:701: bas kyang phyogs che zhing zab pa ni rig pa
NK101(de)002:702: yul dang yul can gnyis su med pa /
NK101(de)002:703: zab mo byang chub kyi sems thig le nyag gcig yin te /
NK101(de)002:704: de go na 'khor 'das thog bardzisa car phog tu grol bas so //
NK101(de)002:705: yon tan cir yang basngagasa pa med //
NK101(de)002:707: skyon yon med pa'i rigs pa bstan te /
NK101(de)002:708: rang gi rig pa byang chub kyi sems yul med pa de la /
NK101(de)002:709: yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kyi che ba'i
NK101(de)002:710: yon tan mtshan dang dpe byad stobs dang mi 'jigs
NK101(de)002:711: pa la sogs pa bogs 'don du med pas bzang
NK101(de)002:713: skyon gyis ma phri bas ngan par brjod du'ang med do //
NK101(de)002:715: don rnams ji bzhin mi bskyod de /
NK101(de)002:716: zhes g.yo 'gul med pa'i gtan tshigs bstan te /
NK101(de)002:717: 'khor 'das gnyis ka'i rtsa ba byang chub kyi sems yin la /
NK101(de)002:718: de la sus kyang bcos bsgyur byar med pas /
NK101(de)002:719: gzhi ji bzhin pa rang rig chen po'i klong lam la /
NK101(de)002:720: bzang ngan gang gis kyang mi bskyod de /
NK101(de)002:721: mnyam pa nyid la phyogs ris med pas bzang rtog
NK101(de)002:722: ngan rtog gang yang 'dra ste rtogs pas bogs ma
NK101(de)002:724: ma rtogs pas ngan du ma song bas mar mi bskyod de 'pho 'gyur med par gnas so //
NK101(de)002:725: bya ba med pas grol ba'ang grol //
NK101(de)002:727: bya bral gyi gtan tshigs bstan te /
NK101(de)002:728: bya ba med pa'i chos bcu gnyis la /
NK101(de)002:729: lhun grub gsum du sa ler ma 'dres yongs rdzogs
NK101(de)002:730: su mthong bas lta ba nyam nga med na chos
NK101(de)002:731: la byar med / de las mi 'da' bar rang
NK101(de)002:732: sar grol ba'i sgom pa la byas pa'i chos kyis
NK101(de)002:733: la byar med / sangs mi rgya / de ltar
NK101(de)002:734: rtogs nas blang dor bral ba'i spyod pa rang byung
NK101(de)002:736: rang gsal 'dzin zhen med pa'i nyams myong la rig pa gang dgar thong /
NK101(de)002:737: gzhi bzhag rang lugs su shes pa'i bcos thabs la rnam rtog dgrar mi lta /
NK101(de)002:738: rang snang du rtogs te gnyis 'dzin drungs phyung ba'i gdams ngag la dug lnga mdog ma sgyur /
NK101(de)002:739: mthar 'dzin bral ba'i 'ching zhags la dge sdig spong len ma byed /
NK101(de)002:740: chos nyid phyogs yan gyi 'bras bu la mi mthun pa skyon du ma 'dor /
NK101(de)002:741: rtsol bral rig pa'i dam tshig la gnyen po rgyud la ma brten /
NK101(de)002:742: rang bzhin ma bcos pa'i phrin las la bya ba
NK101(de)002:743: ci dang ci byed kyang shugs 'byung klong rdol rang
NK101(de)002:745: sbyang bgrod med pa'i sa lam la 'gro sa dang grol sa yod kyis re dogs ma byed /
NK101(de)002:746: phyogs med khyab gdal du shes pa'i go tshad la
NK101(de)002:747: rtogs rung ma rtogs rung grol ba yin pas blo
NK101(de)002:748: bde ba dang bcu gnyis po des /
NK101(de)002:749: rdzogs pa chen po bya bral gyi klong du la bzla ba yin te /
NK101(de)002:751: byar med 'di la gang gnas pa //
NK101(de)002:752: lus ni gang zag lha mi yang //
NK101(de)002:753: dgongs pa chos nyid sangs rgyas pas //
NK101(de)002:754: 'di yis sems can don byas nas //
NK101(de)002:755: rtsol sgrub mi byed bde bar gnas //
NK101(de)002:757: de lta ba'i bya rtsol med pa'i don de nyid
NK101(de)002:758: sems can thams cad la khyab gdal du gnas pas
NK101(de)002:760: de ka bzhin du bla mas bstan te rtogs pas
NK101(de)002:761: mngon du gyur pa las yang grol du gyur pa
NK101(de)002:762: zhes bya ste / rdzogs pa chen po byar med
NK101(de)002:763: de'ang de lta bu zhig go na byar rung gi
NK101(de)002:764: zhes bya ste / / gzhan du kha 'ud tsam la brten pas ci yang phan pa med de /
NK101(de)002:766: chags sdang gnas las ma 'phags par //
NK101(de)002:767: gzung dang 'dzin pa'i stegs byas nas //
NK101(de)002:772: rang byung ye shes brtsal med pas //
NK101(de)002:773: zhes pa rgyu rkyen med pa'i gtan tshigs bstan te /
NK101(de)002:774: rig pa byang chub kyi sems rgyu rkyen med pas rang byung ye shes /
NK101(de)002:775: shar nub med pas rang byung ye shes /
NK101(de)002:776: phyi nang sgrib g.yog med pas rang byung ye shes /
NK101(de)002:777: ka phyi mo nas rang byung bas gzhan nas brtsal du med pa'o //
NK101(de)002:778: grol nas grol ba'i lam yang ston //
NK101(de)002:780: ye grol chen po'i gtan tshigs bstan te /
NK101(de)002:781: 'o na 'di la thug pa med pa'i skyon du 'gyur ram snyam na /
NK101(de)002:782: mtha' la skyon du 'dzin na thug pa med pa'i skyon 'ong la /
NK101(de)002:783: rdzogs pa chen po shes bya mtha' med du gtan la phebs na /
NK101(de)002:784: skyon du che rgyu med de 'dod thog yin yang /
NK101(de)002:785: mtshon pa'i sgo ma 'gags pas 'khor 'das kyi chos
NK101(de)002:786: thams cad bya bral klong chen gyi ngang du ye
NK101(de)002:787: grol gyi ngo bor thig le nyag gcig tu sangs
NK101(de)002:789: da dung nyag gcig gi don de rtogs pa'i phyir bram ze chen pos /
NK101(de)002:790: las zin pa yi dam pa yi //
NK101(de)002:791: drung du sems thag cod par gyis //
NK101(de)002:792: zhes gsungs pa ltar mtshon tshad tsam du bla mas ston dgos pas /
NK101(de)002:793: rnam par grol ba'i lam thun mong ma yin pa yang 'thad pa ste /
NK101(de)002:795: rdo rje sems dpa' nga nyid kyang //
NK101(de)002:796: rdo rje'i gdan la yang sangs rgyas //
NK101(de)002:799: chos nyid kyi thig le zhes pa gzhan gyis sel med pa'i skabs yin pas /
NK101(de)002:800: 'dus ma byas shing ma bcos par ye nas gnas pas na chos nyid /
NK101(de)002:801: ma spros kun la khyab par gdal bas thig le'o //
NK101(de)002:802: 'o na dpe don rigs pa gtan tshigs bzhi po tha dad dam zhe na /
NK101(de)002:803: bshad pa dkyus kyi dbang du btang na de ltar 'gro yang /
NK101(de)002:804: gdams ngag don thog tu dril na /
NK101(de)002:805: bshad tshod de dag thams cad mdo thig le nyag gcig tu bsdu /
NK101(de)002:808: phugs thag da ltar gyi snang ba la bcad /
NK101(de)002:809: 'gro sa chos kyi dbyings su btang ba dang lngas rgyas gdab pas /
NK101(de)002:810: dang pos sems nyid khyab gdal la 'gran pa'i zla med pas blo bde /
NK101(de)002:811: gnyis pas theg pas so sos rtsol sgrub med pas blo bde /
NK101(de)002:812: gsum pas lam 'og mas spangs thob bral bas blo bde /
NK101(de)002:813: bzhi pas dus phyi mar re dogs dang g.yang sa thams cad dus gcig la chod pas blo bde /
NK101(de)002:814: lnga pas lam log par ma song ste 'khor bar
NK101(de)002:815: mi 'khyams pas blo bde ba ni phyag rgya'i dod
NK101(de)002:816: po khyad par dang ldan pa gnas kyi yang snying
NK101(de)002:818: phyag rgya dag gi nges pa ni //
NK101(de)002:819: sems nyid rdzogs pa'i snying po de //
NK101(de)002:820: ye nas byang chub sku yin pas //
NK101(de)002:821: skye ba med cing 'gyur ba med //
NK101(de)002:822: ye nas ye shes chen po'i sku //
NK101(de)002:823: 'gyur ba med pa'i rang bzhin la //
NK101(de)002:824: phyag rgya zhes ni bstan pa yin //
NK101(de)002:825: zhes gsungs pas skabs kun la de ltar shes par bya'o //
NK101(de)002:826: da ni skabs gnyis pa la /
NK101(de)002:828: snod bcud gzhir bzhengs kyi dgongs pa nyi ma'i snying
NK101(de)002:829: po lta bur gsal 'grib med pa'i klong du bstan
NK101(de)002:830: pa / las dang nyon mongs pa'i dbang gis cir yang 'char ba'i rigs pa bstan pa /
NK101(de)002:831: rang grol chen po'i gtan tshigs bstan pa dang bzhi las /
NK101(de)002:833: rang bzhin gyis gnas pa'i skabs /
NK101(de)002:835: rang bzhin ni ma bcos pa'am lhun gyis grub pa'i chos nyid la bya ste /
NK101(de)002:836: de su la gnas na 'khor 'das kyi chos thams
NK101(de)002:837: cad la rang gi rang bzhin nam spyi khyab tu
NK101(de)002:838: gnas pas de lta bu'i yin don zab mo zhig
NK101(de)002:839: 'dir ston pa'i skabs la bab bo //
NK101(de)002:841: 'dus ma byas pa'i chos nyid de //
NK101(de)002:842: 'gro ba rnams la rang bzhin gyis //
NK101(de)002:843: ye nas ma phye gnas pa'i phyir //
NK101(de)002:844: rang bzhin gnas pa'i skabs zhes bya //
NK101(de)002:848: zhes phyi snod kyi 'jig rten yang 'byung ba sa chu me rlung nam mkha' lnga ste /
NK101(de)002:849: de la phra rags su dbye na nyi shu rtsa lngar bshad kyang rtsa ba'i lnga la 'du /
NK101(de)002:850: de yang 'gro ba'i don mdzad pa'i phyir /
NK101(de)002:851: rin po che rnam pa lnga'am /
NK101(de)002:852: rdo rje rnam pa lnga'i ngo bor sangs rgyas te chos nyid gzhir bzhengs yin pa dang /
NK101(de)002:853: nang bcud kyi sems can yang 'byung ba lnga las
NK101(de)002:854: phung khams skye mched du grub ste rdo rje'i snying
NK101(de)002:855: por rang 'khrungs pa'i sangs rgyas yin te chos nyid
NK101(de)002:857: ji ltar gzhi nas bzhengs na /
NK101(de)002:858: 'khor 'das dbyings su gzhi nas bzhengs te lhag ma ma lus /
NK101(de)002:859: snang srid rig par gzhi nas bzhengs te lhag ma ma lus /
NK101(de)002:860: rang rig chos skur gzhi nas bzhengs te lhag ma
NK101(de)002:861: ma lus pas ji ltar byas kyang dgongs pa chos
NK101(de)002:863: nyi ma'i snying po lta bu ni /
NK101(de)002:864: nyi ma'i snying po la mun pa ka nas dag cing mun pa'i sel med pa ltar /
NK101(de)002:865: snod bcud kyi 'jig rten la log rtog ka nas dag cing ma rig pa'i sel med pa dang /
NK101(de)002:866: nyi ma'i snying po 'di snang ba rtsal rdzogs shing byung sa theb pa ltar /
NK101(de)002:867: snod bcud thams cad sangs rgyas su rtsal rdzogs shing
NK101(de)002:868: rang byung ye shes su byung sa theb pa la
NK101(de)002:869: bya zhing / gsal 'grib med pa ni ma rig pas bsgribs te mi gsal ba dang /
NK101(de)002:870: gnyen pos gsal du song ba med par shar nub med pa'i klong zhes bya'o //
NK101(de)002:871: de'i rang bzhin la nges pa med pas las dang
NK101(de)002:872: nyon mongs pas cir yang snang ba'i rigs pa byung
NK101(de)002:873: la / byung yang rang byung rang zhir shes pas rang grol chen po'i gtan tshigs kyang byung ngo //
NK101(de)002:874: des na 'byung ba chen po bcom ldan 'das ni
NK101(de)002:875: phyi snod kyi 'jig rten ye nas sangs rgyas pa'i
NK101(de)002:876: dgongs pa 'byung ba lngas ye nas 'gro don mdzad
NK101(de)002:877: pas spyi la khyab pa'i bcom ldan 'das yin te
NK101(de)002:878: / rin po rnam pa lnga'i ngo bor ram /
NK101(de)002:879: rgyu rkyen gyis ma bskyed par rang byung gi bcom ldan 'das yin pas /
NK101(de)002:880: rdo rje rnam pa lnga'i ngo bor sangs rgyas so //
NK101(de)002:881: 'gro ba kun la rang bzhin gnas //
NK101(de)002:883: des na nang bcud kyi 'gro ba rigs drug gi lus su skyes pa kun kyang /
NK101(de)002:884: de lnga las phung khams skye mched la sogs par grub pas /
NK101(de)002:885: rdo rje snying por rang 'khrungs pa'i sangs rgyas su rang bzhin gyis gnas so //
NK101(de)002:886: de lta bu'i dgongs pa de la ched du sgom pa yod med gong ltar shes dgos so //
NK101(de)002:888: phyin ci log tu rnam brtags kyang /
NK101(de)002:890: ma nges pa'i rang bzhin las brtags pa ltar cir yang snang ba'i rigs pa bstan te /
NK101(de)002:891: phyin ci log la gnyis las /
NK101(de)002:892: rkyen ngan las kyis btags pa'i phyin ci log /
NK101(de)002:893: so so skye bo gzung 'dzin la mngon par zhen pas /
NK101(de)002:895: bdag med la bdag tu bzung bas /
NK101(de)002:896: mnyam pa nyid las shugs kyis log pa dang /
NK101(de)002:897: khrid pa nyon mongs pas log pa /
NK101(de)002:898: mu stegs kyi ston pa rnams kyis gdul bya'i blo bsgyur te /
NK101(de)002:899: rtag pa gcig pu la sogs pa'i grub mthas khrid de /
NK101(de)002:902: don go na de dag gang yang mi spong bas bzhi pa ni /
NK101(de)002:903: grol ba rang byung gzhan las min //
NK101(de)002:905: rgyu rkyen med par grol ba'i gtan tshigs bstan te /
NK101(de)002:906: skye bo dang mu stegs su ma zad 'khor 'das
NK101(de)002:907: kyi chos thams cad rgyu chos nyid la rkyen rol
NK101(de)002:908: pa 'bras bu rang byung ye shes su grol ba
NK101(de)002:909: dang / gzhi lhun grub ngo bo nges med /
NK101(de)002:910: don skye med bdag nyid thog mtha' med par grol ba dang /
NK101(de)002:915: chos can chos nyid du grol bas 'bras bu gzhan
NK101(de)002:916: la mi re ste gzhi nas de ltar grol ba
NK101(de)002:917: la / da gdod brtsal du med pas gzhan las 'byung ba min no //
NK101(de)002:918: de'i 'jug sdud 'dra'o////da ni skabs gsum pa la /
NK101(de)002:920: thabs shes rab gnyis su med pa'i dgongs pa khyung
NK101(de)002:921: dar ma nam mkha' la lding ba lta bu bya
NK101(de)002:922: rtsol dang bral ba'i klong du bstan pa /
NK101(de)002:923: tshod 'dzin pa'i rigs pa bstan pa /
NK101(de)002:924: 'bras bu gzhan nas mi 'byung ba'i gtan tshigs bstan pa dang bzhi las /
NK101(de)002:926: rang bzhin gyis che ba la gnas pa'i skabs /
NK101(de)002:928: rang bzhin ni ma bcos pa'i chos nyid lhun gyis grub pa'i dgongs pa ste /
NK101(de)002:929: de sems can thams cad kyi sems kyi rang bzhin
NK101(de)002:930: du gnas kyang brtags par dka' zhing thun mong gi
NK101(de)002:931: spyod yul du ma gyur pas /
NK101(de)002:932: 'khor 'das lam pa las che bar gnas pa'i don ston pa'i skabs la bab bo //
NK101(de)002:935: 'dus ma byas pa'i chos nyid de //
NK101(de)002:936: ma bcos rang la gnas pa yis //
NK101(de)002:937: sangs rgyas che ba thob pa'i phyir //
NK101(de)002:938: rang bzhin che ba'i skabs kyi bstan //
NK101(de)002:941: che ba'i ye shes rnyed dka' ba //
NK101(de)002:943: rdzogs pa chen po a ti yo ga'i lugs kyis snang zhing srid pas bsdus pa'i chos thams cad /
NK101(de)002:944: gzhi nges med kyi rol pa phyogs med du shar
NK101(de)002:945: ba la mthar 'dzin gang yang mi spong ba thabs
NK101(de)002:947: don skye med bdag nyid thog mtha' med pa'i klong du grol ba la /
NK101(de)002:948: mtshan ma'i spros pa'am phyogs su 'dzin pa med pas /
NK101(de)002:949: 'dzin med cir yang mi rtog pa shes rab kyi
NK101(de)002:950: rgyal po yin te de gnyis tshig la snga phyi
NK101(de)002:951: byung yang don la tha dad med de /
NK101(de)002:952: rgyu chos nyid rkyen rol pa 'bras bu rang byung gi ye shes su gcig pas /
NK101(de)002:953: dpe nam mkha' don chos nyid rtags rang byung ye shes su gcig ste /
NK101(de)002:954: thabs shes rab gnyis su med cing dmigs pa'i mtha' las 'das pas ye klong chen po'i dgongs pa'o //
NK101(de)002:955: khyung dar ma nam mkha' la lding ba lta bu ni /
NK101(de)002:957: bar du rtsol bas g.yo ba /
NK101(de)002:958: tha mar mi rtsol bar rang lugs su 'jog pa ltar /
NK101(de)002:959: rdzogs pa chen po a ti yo ga pa'ang /
NK101(de)002:960: dang po bla ma'i gdams ngag gi stegs 'cha'/
NK101(de)002:961: bar du thos bsam sgom sgrub la rtsol ba g.yo ba /
NK101(de)002:962: tha mar mnyam pa ris med la ched du mi rtsol te /
NK101(de)002:963: rang lugs su 'jog pa yin pas bya rtsol dang bral ba'i klong du bstan pa zer la /
NK101(de)002:964: de la ched du rtsol na gol sa yin pas tshod 'dzin gyi rigs pa'ang de la bya zhing /
NK101(de)002:965: ma brtsal kyang rang la gnas pas 'bras bu rang las 'byung ba'i gtan tshigs bstan te /
NK101(de)002:966: des na che ba'i ye shes ni /
NK101(de)002:967: thun mong ma yin pa'i dgongs pa ste /
NK101(de)002:968: 'khor 'das theg pa thams cad las che ba'am /
NK101(de)002:969: mtha' ji snyed pa zil gyis gnon pas che ba
NK101(de)002:970: ni rang gi sems nyid don rang byung gi ye
NK101(de)002:971: shes phyi nang med par nges med phyogs ris ngang
NK101(de)002:973: gang gis kyang rnyed par dka' bas a nu man
NK101(de)002:974: chad kyi theg pa 'og ma pas ma rnyed pa'o
NK101(de)002:975: // de cis rnyed par dka' na chos nyid phyogs med la phyogs dang ris su rtsol ba'am /
NK101(de)002:976: rang la bzhag nas gzhan du tshol bas rnyed par dka' ba'o //
NK101(de)002:977: 'o na gting nas rang mi rnyed dam zhe na /
NK101(de)002:978: gting nas mi rnyed pa'am rigs chad ma yin mod /
NK101(de)002:979: rdzogs pa chen po rang gnas skabs su /
NK101(de)002:980: shes rab thabs la brten pas grub /
NK101(de)002:982: 'dzin pa med pa shes rab kyi rgyal po ma skyes pa dang /
NK101(de)002:983: bya ba med pa thabs kyi rgyal po ma 'gag pa la brten nas /
NK101(de)002:984: rang byung ye shes skye 'gag med pa'i don de /
NK101(de)002:985: tshegs med par rang la grub pa'o //
NK101(de)002:986: de lta bu'i dgongs pa la skyon bsal ba 'dra'o //
NK101(de)002:988: ming tsam gzhan la brten 'dra yang //
NK101(de)002:989: zhes ming mtha' tshod 'dzin du bstan pa'i rigs pa nyid de /
NK101(de)002:990: gong du thabs dang shes rab gnyis su smos pa
NK101(de)002:991: de rang yang ming tsam mam tshig gam brda tsam
NK101(de)002:992: gyis gzhan nas bskor te ston pa 'dra yang don
NK101(de)002:993: rang la rang byung du gnas pa'i phyir ro //
NK101(de)002:994: ming tsam zhes tshod 'dzin pa'i tshig yin pas /
NK101(de)002:995: tshig rang rgyud pa'i phyir 'brangs na don las gol bar 'gyur zhes bya ba'i tha tshig go //
NK101(de)002:997: mngon sum bde ba rang las 'byung //
NK101(de)002:998: zhes pa ye shes khong nas 'char ba'i gtan tshigs bstan te /
NK101(de)002:999: lar theg pa 'og ma pa'i lugs kyis dbang po'i
NK101(de)002:1000: mngon sum rang las tha dad kyi yul 'jal bar
NK101(de)002:1001: byed pa la / 'dir ye shes kyi rnam pa
NK101(de)002:1002: sgyu ma lhun grub kyis rgyu 'bras rang la yod
NK101(de)002:1003: pas yul du ma byas pa dang /
NK101(de)002:1004: yid kyi mngon sum dbang po'i rjes la skye ba la /
NK101(de)002:1005: 'dir rang bzhin spros bral lhun grub kyis chos nyid
NK101(de)002:1006: bsam gyis mi khyab pa la dmigs pa'i yul dang
NK101(de)002:1007: bral ba dang / rang rig pa'i mngon sum gsal
NK101(de)002:1008: rig gi ngo bos rang myong ltos med du gcod
NK101(de)002:1009: bral ba dang / pa la / 'dir rdzogs pa
NK101(de)002:1010: chen po'i chos nyid rang gis rig pas mtshan nyid
NK101(de)002:1012: rang rig pa'i rgyal po dbang du gyur pa dang /
NK101(de)002:1013: rnal 'byor gyi mngon sum bdag med kyi don dang
NK101(de)002:1014: pha rol gyi bzang rtog sogs snang ba yin pa
NK101(de)002:1015: la / 'dir yongs rdzogs dbyer med kyi dgongs pas
NK101(de)002:1016: sku gsum lhun rdzogs su gsal ba rab tu gyur
NK101(de)002:1017: pas tshogs brgyad kyi rtog pa yul med du grol
NK101(de)002:1018: te thig le nyag gcig tu shar bar mngon sum
NK101(de)002:1019: la / du mthong bas / 'bras klong las /
NK101(de)002:1020: yul la mtshan mar rtog dang ngar 'dzin can //
NK101(de)002:1021: rjes su ming la spros par 'brang bar bslad //
NK101(de)002:1022: de nyid sprul par rol pas de mkhyen pa'i //
NK101(de)002:1023: ye shes kun la bde bar longs spyod rdzogs //
NK101(de)002:1024: de nyid rnam dag dmigs med chos skur grol //
NK101(de)002:1025: sku gsum lhun grub kun bzang nyag gcig po //
NK101(de)002:1026: ma bslad ma bcos ma spangs ma bkag cing //
NK101(de)002:1027: ma sbyangs ma bsgyur ma brtsal ma bskyed grol //
NK101(de)002:1028: zhes gsungs pa ltar mngon sum bzhis ma 'dres yongs
NK101(de)002:1029: rdzogs su rtogs pa'i mthu la brten nas gnas lugs
NK101(de)002:1030: bya rtsol lam zag pa'i 'pho 'gyur med pa'i chos
NK101(de)002:1031: nyid bde ba chen po de nyid gzhan nas brtsal
NK101(de)002:1032: ba med par da lta rang gi snang grags kyi
NK101(de)002:1033: chos wal le khyug ge ba rang la rang byung
NK101(de)002:1034: dngos grub shar bar go bas 'bras bu dam pa
NK101(de)002:1035: nyid 'byung ste / slob dpon chen po sh+ri sid+hasa //
NK101(de)002:1036: sgyu ma'i ro la ma chags pas //
NK101(de)002:1037: chags med ye shes rdzogs pa'i lam //
NK101(de)002:1038: byang chub sems kyi rang gsal 'di //
NK101(de)002:1039: dngos med shes rab thabs kyis 'grub //
NK101(de)002:1041: de ltar dpe don rigs pa gtan tshigs bzhi la rgyas 'debs 'dra'o////da ni skabs bzhi pa la /
NK101(de)002:1043: tshogs drug lhug pa 'char ba'i dgongs pa skyes bu
NK101(de)002:1044: nad kyis gzir ba lta bur rang lugs chen po'i
NK101(de)002:1046: chos thams cad gnyis med la rtsol bas mi sgrub pa'i rigs pa bstan pa /
NK101(de)002:1047: brtags na mi rnyed cing ngo bo cir yang 'char ba'i gtan tshigs bstan pa dang bzhi las /
NK101(de)002:1049: brtsal ba dang bral ba'i skabs /
NK101(de)002:1050: zhes a nu yo ga man chad theg rim brgyad
NK101(de)002:1051: po gzhi phyogs med la phyogs su brtsal bas rang
NK101(de)002:1052: rang gi lta sgom spyod pa la ched du 'dzin
NK101(de)002:1053: pas / 'bras bu la zhes 'dod byed pa de /
NK101(de)002:1054: a ti yo ga rdzogs pa chen po bya bral
NK101(de)002:1055: klong chen rtsol med lhun grub tu brda sprod de
NK101(de)002:1056: / 'og ma'i rtsol ba de kun dang bral bar ston pa'i skabs la bab bo //
NK101(de)002:1058: 'dus ma byas pa'i chos nyid de //
NK101(de)002:1059: btsal ba med par grub pa'i phyir //
NK101(de)002:1060: brtsal dang bral ba'i skabs kyis bstan //
NK101(de)002:1064: snang ba med pa'i chos nyid ni //
NK101(de)002:1065: zhes 'jug pa'i rnam shes tshogs drug yul drug la 'jug pa nyid /
NK101(de)002:1066: dbang drug yul drug sku drug zang thal du shar bas /
NK101(de)002:1067: a nu man chad spong sbyong sgyur ba sogs byed pa /
NK101(de)002:1068: a ti yo ga spro bsdu gang yang mi byed pas /
NK101(de)002:1069: tshogs drug lhug pa yul la ldom du bcug pas /
NK101(de)002:1070: thams cad nas thams cad du tshogs drug yan pa /
NK101(de)002:1075: tshogs drug lhug par 'char ba'i dgongs pa chos nyid kyi klong ngo //
NK101(de)002:1076: skyes bu nad kyi gzir ba lta bu ni /
NK101(de)002:1077: dper na nad tshabs po ches thebs pa'i skyes bu la /
NK101(de)002:1078: ma dang sring mo la'ang ngo tsha mi tsha ba
NK101(de)002:1079: med par spyod lam lhug par gnas pa bzhin du
NK101(de)002:1080: / rig pa rang yan tshugs pa'i rnal 'byor pas sgo gsum lhug pa'i spyod lam la /
NK101(de)002:1081: gnyen po gang yang mi brten par /
NK101(de)002:1082: rang lugs ma bcos pa'i klong du gnas par ston te /
NK101(de)002:1083: de la yul sems tha dad pa med pas chos
NK101(de)002:1084: thams cad gnyis su med pa la btsal na mi
NK101(de)002:1086: cho 'phrul cir yang 'byung ba la brtags na mi
NK101(de)002:1087: rnyed par ngo bo cir yang 'char ba'i gtan tshigs
NK101(de)002:1088: so // des na snang ba med pa'i chos nyid phyogs 'dzin med pa'i dgongs pa la /
NK101(de)002:1089: a ti yo ga rdzogs pa chen po'i lugs kyis gzhi phyogs 'dzin du mi snang /
NK101(de)002:1090: ngo bo nges med la rol pa ngos gzung med /
NK101(de)002:1091: don skye med la mthar 'dzin nam gnyis 'dzin gang yang mi snang ste /
NK101(de)002:1092: cir snang thams cad rang snang la //
NK101(de)002:1093: ci shar thams cad rang shar yin pas /
NK101(de)002:1094: gzhan yul dang yul can gang yang med pa ni ma bcos pa'i chos nyid /
NK101(de)002:1096: ma brtsal bzhag na sgom pa yin //
NK101(de)002:1097: zhes rtsol sgrub med pa'i dgongs pa /
NK101(de)002:1100: tshogs drug zang thal la mi mthun pa dang gnyis su med par brtsal bas /
NK101(de)002:1101: thams cad nas thams cad du tshogs drug lhug pa /
NK101(de)002:1106: a ti yo ga mi sgom pa'i bsgom pa chen po'am /
NK101(de)002:1107: rig pa spyi blugs dbang po rang yan gyi klong chen po yin no //
NK101(de)002:1110: de dang der ni rnam pa brtsal na /
NK101(de)002:1112: mnyam pa nyid la gnyis su 'dzin na 'khrul pa'i rigs pa /
NK101(de)002:1113: 'khor 'das bzang ngan gyis bsdus pa'i chos thams cad
NK101(de)002:1114: thig le nyag gcig dbyer mi phyed pa gcig la
NK101(de)002:1115: / 'khor ba ngan pa dang myang 'das bzang po gnyis su phye ste /
NK101(de)002:1116: dgag sgrub dang blang dor gyis rtsol ba las 'bras bur 'dod pa ni /
NK101(de)002:1117: de las de bzhin de mi 'byung //
NK101(de)002:1118: zhes gnyis 'dzin can la gnyis med mi 'byung ba'i rigs pa bstan te /
NK101(de)002:1120: gnyis 'dzin can gyi gang zag gi lta sgom de las /
NK101(de)002:1121: chos thams cad kyi de bzhin nyid /
NK101(de)002:1122: a ti yo ga ma nor ma bcos pa'i 'bras bu mi 'byung bas bzhi pa ni /
NK101(de)002:1124: cho 'phrul chen po dka' ba min //
NK101(de)002:1125: zhes rang byung ye shes ma nges pa'i gtan tshigs bstan te /
NK101(de)002:1126: spyir na yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas la cho 'phrul chen po bzhi yod de /
NK101(de)002:1127: rdzu 'phrul gyi cho 'phrul gyis gdul bya dad par byas /
NK101(de)002:1128: rjes su bstan pa'i cho 'phrul gyis dad pa bdun par byas /
NK101(de)002:1129: kun brjod pa'i cho 'phrul gyis 'dun pa smin par byas /
NK101(de)002:1130: chos snang ba'i cho 'phrul gyis smin pa grol bar byed pa ni /
NK101(de)002:1131: 'og ma'i cho 'phrul yin yang chen po min no //
NK101(de)002:1132: des na cho 'phrul chen po ni de las khyad
NK101(de)002:1133: par du gyur pa rdzogs pa chen po a ti
NK101(de)002:1134: yo ga / gzhi phyogs med rol pa nges med
NK101(de)002:1135: du 'char ba'i cho 'phrul ni dka' ba med de
NK101(de)002:1136: yo ga / / nam mkha'i cho 'phrul ltar 'byung ba'i phyir ro //
NK101(de)002:1137: 'o na cho 'phrul rang ji ltar 'byung zhe na /
NK101(de)002:1138: yon tan kun ldan stobs kyi rnams //
NK101(de)002:1139: zhes yon tan phyogs med du 'byung ba'i gtan tshigs bstan te /
NK101(de)002:1140: yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kyi che ba dang yon tan /
NK101(de)002:1141: sku gsung thugs yon phrin las rnam pa lnga /
NK101(de)002:1144: stobs dang mi 'jigs pa la sogs pa rnams /
NK101(de)002:1145: ji bzhin rtog pa phra ba yis //
NK101(de)002:1146: zhes zab mo don gyi gtan tshigs bstan te ched du rtsol sgrub bya mi dgos par /
NK101(de)002:1147: ye ji bzhin pa ma bcos pa'i chos nyid zab cing cha phra ba de /
NK101(de)002:1148: ji ltar rang la yod pa ltar rtogs pa de'i mthu las /
NK101(de)002:1149: de ma thag tu rang las 'byung //
NK101(de)002:1150: zhes 'bras bu gzhan nas mi 'byung ba'i gtan tshigs bstan te /
NK101(de)002:1151: theg pa 'og ma ltar mi tshe dang bskal pa
NK101(de)002:1152: grangs su bsgrangs nas sangs rgyas par mi 'dod de
NK101(de)002:1153: / ye grol chen por rtogs pa'i dus na de
NK101(de)002:1154: ma thag tu sangs rgyas kyi dgongs pa dang 'bras
NK101(de)002:1156: de la rjes gdab 'dra'o////da ni skabs lnga pa la /
NK101(de)002:1158: myong snang bstan du med pa'i dgongs pa lkugs pas
NK101(de)002:1159: bu ram gyi ro myong ba lta bur brjod du
NK101(de)002:1160: med pa'i klong du bstan pa /
NK101(de)002:1161: nyan pa thos su med pa'i rigs pa bstan pa /
NK101(de)002:1162: bshad pas brjod du med pa'i gtan tshigs bstan pa /
NK101(de)002:1163: thig le'i nges tshig bshad pa dang lnga las /
NK101(de)002:1165: brjod pa dang bral ba'i skabs /
NK101(de)002:1166: zhes don gyi ngo bo 'di ltar 'dug bya ba'i smra brjod tha snyad thams cad bral ba la /
NK101(de)002:1167: rdzogs pa chen po'i rnal 'byor pas //
NK101(de)002:1168: de ji ltar ba bzhin goms pa klong du gyur
NK101(de)002:1169: nas chos nyid smrar med pa'i klong na rig pa
NK101(de)002:1170: bde blag chen por gnas pas de lta bu'i don
NK101(de)002:1171: zab mo ston pa'i skabs la bab bo //
NK101(de)002:1173: 'dus ma byas pa'i chos nyid de //
NK101(de)002:1174: tshig dang yi ges brjod med phyir //
NK101(de)002:1175: brjod dang bral ba'i skabs kyis bstan //
NK101(de)002:1178: mchog tu gsang ba'i chos nyid ni //
NK101(de)002:1179: zhes myong snang gi yul dang dbang po la snang
NK101(de)002:1180: ba'i chos thams cad rdzogs pa chen po a ti
NK101(de)002:1182: phyi nang dbye bsal med par chos nyid mnyam pa nyid du ro stor ba yin te /
NK101(de)002:1183: chos nyid smra brjod dang bral ba'i klong na rig
NK101(de)002:1184: pa bde blag chen por gnas pas go ba klong
NK101(de)002:1185: du gyur kyang bstan du ma btub ste /
NK101(de)002:1186: tshig thams cad ni mtha' can nam tha snyad yin la /
NK101(de)002:1187: don mtha' med brjod du med pa yin pas smra
NK101(de)002:1188: brjod tha snyad dang bral ba'i dgongs pa chos nyid
NK101(de)002:1189: kyi klong ngo // lkugs pas bu ram gyi ro
NK101(de)002:1190: myong ba ni brjod du ma btub pa'i dpe yin
NK101(de)002:1191: kyi klong ngo // te / mngar bar tshor kyang
NK101(de)002:1192: mngar ro zhes brjod ma shes pa ltar chos nyid
NK101(de)002:1193: ji bzhin pa'i don nyams su myong ba la 'di
NK101(de)002:1194: kho nar 'dug bya ba'i phyogs gcig gang du'ang brjod
NK101(de)002:1195: kyi klong ngo // te / ma shes pas /
NK101(de)002:1196: smra brjod dang bral ba'i klong du bstan pa zhes
NK101(de)002:1197: kyi klong ngo // te / ma shes pas /
NK101(de)002:1198: bya / de la phyi rol gyi don med pas
NK101(de)002:1199: nyan pas thos su med pa'i rigs pa /
NK101(de)002:1200: tshig gi lam dang bral bas bshad pas brjod du med pa'i gtan tshigs 'byung ngo //
NK101(de)002:1202: mchog tu gsang ba'i chos nyid ni /
NK101(de)002:1204: snang ba ci shar rang la shar bar shes pas /
NK101(de)002:1205: rang sems skye 'gag med pa khong du chud pa dang /
NK101(de)002:1206: de 'pho 'gyur med par rtogs pa ni byang chub mchog gi chos nyid yin te /
NK101(de)002:1207: da gzhan a nu man chad kyis go bar dka' bas /
NK101(de)002:1208: gsang ba rmad du byung ba ma bcos gnyug ma'i chos nyid do //
NK101(de)002:1211: rna dbang gzhan las thos mi 'gyur //
NK101(de)002:1212: zhes don gzhan nas mi 'byung ba'i rigs pa ste /
NK101(de)002:1213: chos thams cad mnyam nyid gnyis su med pa'i klong las /
NK101(de)002:1214: phyi rol gyi don du gyur pa cung zad tsam yang med pas /
NK101(de)002:1215: nyan pa pos rna ba'i dbang po la brten nas /
NK101(de)002:1216: rang las ma gtogs pa'i chos gzhan nas thos par mi 'gyur /
NK101(de)002:1218: bdag gzhan gnyis su med par thams cad rang byung yin pa'i phyir ro //
NK101(de)002:1220: de bzhin lce yi dbang pos kyang //
NK101(de)002:1222: de la brjod du rdul tsam med //
NK101(de)002:1223: ces pa gong du bsnyegs pa'i tshig yin te /
NK101(de)002:1224: gong du rna dbang la brten nas chos nyid de
NK101(de)002:1225: rang las gzhan nas thos su med pa de bzhin
NK101(de)002:1226: du / chos thams cad kyi de bzhin nyid de ni de ltar lce'i dbang po la brten nas /
NK101(de)002:1227: dbyibs dang kha dog dngos po dang mtshan ma 'di
NK101(de)002:1228: lta bu zhig 'dug bya bar brjod cing bsam du
NK101(de)002:1229: med de / chos nyid smra brjod med cing tshig
NK101(de)002:1230: mtha' bral ba'i klong du rig pa mtha' med bde
NK101(de)002:1231: blag chen po gcig tu gnas pas so //
NK101(de)002:1235: dang po snod bcud kyi 'byung khungs bstan pa dang /
NK101(de)002:1236: gnyis pa thabs shes kyi byung khungs bstan pa /
NK101(de)002:1237: gsum pa cho 'phrul gyi byung khungs bstan pa /
NK101(de)002:1238: bzhi pa dmigs pa'i mtha' dang bral ba'i dbyings te /
NK101(de)002:1239: rig pa mu mtha' med cing cho 'phrul zad mi shes pas dbyings la /
NK101(de)002:1240: ma spros kun la khyab cing grwa dang zur med pas thig le'o //
NK101(de)002:1242: da ni skabs drug pa la'ang /
NK101(de)002:1244: snying po byang chub sems kyi dgongs pa til 'bru
NK101(de)002:1245: la mar gyis khyab pa lta bur lhun gyis grub
NK101(de)002:1247: snang ba bcu bdun cir yang 'char ba'i rigs pa bstan pa /
NK101(de)002:1248: las mi btsan par thams cad rang byung ye shes yin pa'i gtan tshigs bstan pa dang bzhi las /
NK101(de)002:1250: 'gro ba las kyis mi 'khor ba'i skabs /
NK101(de)002:1252: 'gro ba ni las nas las su 'gro ba'i 'gro ba ni ngan song gsum ste /
NK101(de)002:1253: gsad gcad kyi las kyis dmyal ba /
NK101(de)002:1254: ser sna dang 'jur 'gegs kyi las kyis yi dwags /
NK101(de)002:1255: rmongs shing lus ma bstan pa'i las kyis byol song
NK101(de)002:1256: ste las zad pa 'ga' re grol ba'ang srid mtha'
NK101(de)002:1257: tsam mo // phal che ba las nas las su'ang 'gro mod de /
NK101(de)002:1258: skal ba ldan pa rnams ye shes nas ye shes su 'gro ba'i las ni lha dang mi ste /
NK101(de)002:1259: sngar gyi rgyu phra mo'i ye shes dkar po'i phyogs la spyad pas /
NK101(de)002:1260: da lta lha mi'i rten thob nas 'di la spyad
NK101(de)002:1261: pas gdams ngag dang phrad pas ye shes chen po'i
NK101(de)002:1262: sa la'ang bgrod par nos so //
NK101(de)002:1264: thams cad dbyings nas shar zhir dbyings su 'gro bas na 'gro ba zer ro //
NK101(de)002:1265: las ni bag chags dbang btsan du bzhag pa ste chos nyid kyi rol pa go na /
NK101(de)002:1266: nam mkha' cho 'phrul gyis ma 'gyur ba ltar chos
NK101(de)002:1267: nyid las logs su 'khor te las des mi 'khor
NK101(de)002:1268: bar ston pa'i skabs la bab bo //
NK101(de)002:1269: zhes pa ste 'dus ma byas pa'i chos nyid de /
NK101(de)002:1270: skye ba med pa'i rang bzhin gyis //
NK101(de)002:1271: khams gsum dag tu mi 'khor bas //
NK101(de)002:1272: las kyis mi 'khor skabs zhes bya //
NK101(de)002:1275: 'gro ba'i sdug bsngal byang chub sems //
NK101(de)002:1276: zhes snying po ni chos nyid byang chub kyi sems
NK101(de)002:1277: rtogs pa yin te chos nyid ni gzhi dngos po
NK101(de)002:1278: gshis kyi gnas lugs la bya zhing /
NK101(de)002:1279: byang chub sems ni sems nyid sgrub pa'i lam gyi mtshon tshul bla na med pa yin te /
NK101(de)002:1280: gzhi ji bzhin par rtogs pas 'khor 'das gnyis ka
NK101(de)002:1281: rang sar grol te dgongs pa chos nyid klong ngo
NK101(de)002:1282: // til 'bru la mar gyis khyab pa lta bu ni /
NK101(de)002:1284: ya tha sangs rgyas kyi zhing khams nas /
NK101(de)002:1285: ma tha dmyal ba'i grong khyer yan chad la til la mar gyis khyab pa bzhin du /
NK101(de)002:1287: mtho dman dang yangs dog med par phyogs med du khyab pa la bya /
NK101(de)002:1290: gang ltar 'dug kyang rdzogs pa chen po'i chos nyid las ma 'das par lhun gyis grub pas /
NK101(de)002:1291: lhun grub chen po'i klong du bstan no //
NK101(de)002:1292: de'i ngo bo la nges pa med pas snang ba bcu bdun cir yang 'char ba'i rigs pa /
NK101(de)002:1293: rol pa rang rgyud pa med pas las mi btsan
NK101(de)002:1294: par thams cad rang byung ye shes kyi gtan tshigs
NK101(de)002:1296: 'gro ba'i sdug bsngal byang chub sems //
NK101(de)002:1297: zhes sdug bsngal byang chub sems su 'char ba'i dgong pa bstan te /
NK101(de)002:1298: las nas las su 'gro ba'am ye shes nam ye
NK101(de)002:1299: shes su 'gro ba'i rigs drug gi sems can thams
NK101(de)002:1300: cad theg pa 'og ma pas sems can rang rgyud
NK101(de)002:1301: pa 'dod la / de'i phyir sdug bsngal spangs nas bde ba thob par 'dod kyang /
NK101(de)002:1302: de slar la sdug bsngal nyid du 'gro bas nas rdzogs pa chen po'i lugs kyi /
NK101(de)002:1303: 'gro ba rigs drug gi sems can ye nyid nas
NK101(de)002:1304: rdo rje snying por rang 'khrungs pa'i sangs rgyas yin
NK101(de)002:1305: pas / de las byung ba'i sdug bsngal thams cad
NK101(de)002:1306: chos nyid byang chub sems kyi yo lang du shar
NK101(de)002:1307: pas / bas / byang chub kyi sems rang shar rang grol 'ba' zhig go //
NK101(de)002:1308: kun tu chub pa rnam par rol //
NK101(de)002:1309: zhes rol pa phyogs med du 'byung ba'i dgongs pa ste /
NK101(de)002:1310: 'khor 'das kyi chos thams cad gzhi lhun gyis grub
NK101(de)002:1311: pa'i chos nyid du ma 'dus pa med pa dang
NK101(de)002:1312: / ngo bo nges med chen por lhag ma ma
NK101(de)002:1313: lus par kun tu chub pas bde sdug rang 'khor
NK101(de)002:1314: 'das gnyis su med pa mnyam nyid chen po la
NK101(de)002:1315: dgag sgrub med par rol ba la phyogs ris kun
NK101(de)002:1316: / dang bral ba'o // de la bskyod pa med bzhin du //
NK101(de)002:1318: rig pa yul gyis mi bskyod pa'i dgongs pa bstan te /
NK101(de)002:1319: chos nyid byang chub sems 'gyur ba med pa bya bral gyi klong chen po de la /
NK101(de)002:1320: las dang bag chags ngan pas ngan song du mar mi bskyod /
NK101(de)002:1321: las dang bag chags bzang pos mtho ris su yar mi bskyod /
NK101(de)002:1322: byang chub sems la mtho dman med cing 'pho 'gyur bral ba'i gnad des na /
NK101(de)002:1323: nam mkha'i mtha' ltar mnyam par gnas //
NK101(de)002:1324: zhes kun la khyab par gnas pa'i dgongs pa bstan te /
NK101(de)002:1325: nam mkha' mtha' dbus med cing 'pho 'gyur dang bral bas /
NK101(de)002:1326: 'byung ba chen po bzhi la che chung dang ya
NK101(de)002:1327: yo med par kun khyab mnyam par gnas pa bzhin
NK101(de)002:1328: du bya bral gyi klong lhun grub kyi 'jings /
NK101(de)002:1329: nam mkha' ltar mtha' dbus dang 'pho 'gyur med pa de yis /
NK101(de)002:1330: snang srid 'khor 'das phyi nang snod bcud kyis bsdus pa'i chos thams cad la /
NK101(de)002:1331: che chung bzang ngan dbri bsnan med par phyogs ris
NK101(de)002:1332: dang bral te khyab gdal mnyam pa chen por gnas
NK101(de)002:1335: khyad par cir yang mtshungs pa la //
NK101(de)002:1336: zhes gzhi phyogs med lhun gyis grub par /
NK101(de)002:1337: rkyen phyogs med nges pa bral ba /
NK101(de)002:1338: 'dod pa phyogs med snang tshul tha dad du shar ba la /
NK101(de)002:1339: rang gi snang ba dag gi khyad par gyis /
NK101(de)002:1340: dmyal ba la me chu dang btso sreg /
NK101(de)002:1344: lha la ltung ba dang 'dod yon /
NK101(de)002:1345: mi la 'byung ba rang ga ma 'di /
NK101(de)002:1346: mu stegs la rtag chad gnyis /
NK101(de)002:1350: kri ya la rigs gsum lha'i dkyil 'khor /
NK101(de)002:1351: u pa ya la lta spyod gong 'og /
NK101(de)002:1352: yo gar lha dang lha mo /
NK101(de)002:1353: ma h+aa la thabs dang shes rab /
NK101(de)002:1354: a nu la dbyings dang ye shes /
NK101(de)002:1355: a ti yo gar lhun grub phyogs med du snang
NK101(de)002:1356: ba byang chub kyi sems gcig las snang ba bcu
NK101(de)002:1357: bdun cir yang shar zhing gong 'og gi khyad par
NK101(de)002:1358: cir yang mtshungs pa la bya'o //
NK101(de)002:1360: las so zhes ni rnam par brtags //
NK101(de)002:1361: zhes gzhi lhun grub ngo bo nges med rol pa phyogs med du shar bas na /
NK101(de)002:1362: las yin zhes pa rnam par brtags zhes bya'o //
NK101(de)002:1364: a nu man chad kyi theg pa 'og ma dang /
NK101(de)002:1366: des na las rang rgyud par mi bden pas sun dbyung ba'i phyir /
NK101(de)002:1367: ci ste las kyis dbang 'gyur na //
NK101(de)002:1368: zhes 'gal ba cham la dbab pa'i gtan tshigs bstan te /
NK101(de)002:1369: ci ste'am gal te brgya lam na /
NK101(de)002:1370: theg pa 'og ma pa dang skye bo rnams kyis brtags pa bzhin du /
NK101(de)002:1371: sems kyi chos nyid rgyu rkyen dang bral ba de
NK101(de)002:1372: rgyu rkyen glo bur bas bskyed pa'i las kyi dbang
NK101(de)002:1373: du 'gro na / rang byung ye shes yod ma yin //
NK101(de)002:1374: zhes rgyu rkyen gzhan la mi ltos pa'i phyir /
NK101(de)002:1375: rang byung ye shes bya ba gtan med pa'i skyon du 'gro ste gcig /
NK101(de)002:1377: ngan song dang 'khor ba rigs chad du 'gro ba'i skyon te gnyis /
NK101(de)002:1378: las ngan du song bas rgyal bas thugs rjes mi 'drongs ba'i skyon te gsum /
NK101(de)002:1379: tshigs 'gal bas skabs don rang sub tu 'gro ba'i skyon te bzhi 'byung ngo //
NK101(de)002:1380: 'o na las mi bden na a ti yo ga
NK101(de)002:1381: rang byung gi bde ba de nyid ji lta bu
NK101(de)002:1383: rgyu nyid rdo rje rkyen dang 'dra /
NK101(de)002:1384: zhes rgyu rkyen dang bral ba'i gtan tshigs bstan te /
NK101(de)002:1385: rang gi rig pa byang chub kyi sems de /
NK101(de)002:1386: dus gsum du 'dus ma byas pa rang byung bas /
NK101(de)002:1387: rgyu nyid ni rdo rje dang 'dra ste skye ba med la /
NK101(de)002:1388: ngo bo cir yang 'char zhing gnyen pos gzhigs su
NK101(de)002:1389: med pas rkyen rdo rje dang 'dra ste 'jigs pa
NK101(de)002:1391: ma skyes pas na 'jig pa med //
NK101(de)002:1392: ces skye 'jig med pa'i gtan tshigs bstan te /
NK101(de)002:1393: sems nyid de dang po skye ba'i gzhi med de rgyu las ma skyes pas /
NK101(de)002:1394: tha ma 'gro ba'i lam med de /
NK101(de)002:1395: gnyen pos 'jig pa med par mi 'gyur bar gnas so //
NK101(de)002:1397: gdod nas snying po byang chub la //
NK101(de)002:1398: zhes 'khor 'das kyi chos thams cad ye gdod ma nyid nas rgyu rkyen las ma byung bas /
NK101(de)002:1399: rdo rje snying por rang 'khrungs pa'i sangs rgyas snying
NK101(de)002:1400: po byang chub sems ma bcos pa'i rang bzhin yin
NK101(de)002:1401: pa la / brtsal ba'i bsam pas dbyings mi bskyod //
NK101(de)002:1402: ces 'pho 'gyur med pa'i gtan tshigs bstan te /
NK101(de)002:1403: a nu yo ga man chad kyis /
NK101(de)002:1404: rang rang gi lam lta ba dang sgom pa la
NK101(de)002:1405: ched du brtsal bas yul dang yul can du 'dzin
NK101(de)002:1406: pa'i sems des / dbyings skye 'gag med cing mu
NK101(de)002:1407: mtha' dang bral ba de'i don ji ltar bar gtan
NK101(de)002:1409: phyogs gcig tsam yang bskyod par mi nus pas /
NK101(de)002:1410: ngo bo dmigs su med cing don 'pho 'gyur dang bral bar gnas so //
NK101(de)002:1411: de rnams kyi rgyas 'debs 'dra////da ni skabs bdun pa la /
NK101(de)002:1413: rnam par rtog pa ye shes su ldang ba'i dgongs
NK101(de)002:1414: pa me la shing bsnan pa lta bur rang grol
NK101(de)002:1415: chen po'i klong du bstan pa /
NK101(de)002:1416: brtags na mi rnyed cing rnam par rtog par 'gyur ba'i rigs pa bstan pa /
NK101(de)002:1417: rgyu 'bras dge sdig la mi gnas pa'i gtan tshigs bstan pa dang bzhi las /
NK101(de)002:1419: rtsol sems dang bral ba'i skabs /
NK101(de)002:1421: rang rang gi lam lta sgom spyod pa 'bras bu re bar byas nas so sor rtsol ba dang /
NK101(de)002:1422: a ti yo ga bya bral gyi don go bas
NK101(de)002:1423: rtsol sems de rnams dang bral bar ston pa'i skabs
NK101(de)002:1424: la bab bo // zhes pa ste /
NK101(de)002:1425: chos kun byang chub sems su 'dus //
NK101(de)002:1426: sems nyid brtsal ba med pa la //
NK101(de)002:1427: brtsal ba'i gol sgrib bstan pa'i phyir //
NK101(de)002:1428: brtsal sems bral ba'i skabs zhes bya //
NK101(de)002:1431: yon tan chen po'i bsam gtan ni //
NK101(de)002:1432: zhes de yang bying ba'i rtog pa 'thibs pa dang /
NK101(de)002:1433: rgod pa'i rtog pa 'phro ba dang //
NK101(de)002:1434: 'dzin pa'i rtog pa ma rig pa ste /
NK101(de)002:1435: de la sogs pa'i rnam rtog ji ltar shar yang /
NK101(de)002:1436: rang byung ye shes su rang shar bas /
NK101(de)002:1437: grol yang rang byung ye shes su grol te rnam
NK101(de)002:1438: rtog ye shes su ldang ba dgongs pa chos nyid
NK101(de)002:1439: kyi ngang ngo // me la shing bsnan pa lta bu ni /
NK101(de)002:1440: me la shing bskyur bas me'i grogs su 'gro ba'am /
NK101(de)002:1441: kha char chu'i grogs su 'gro ba bzhin du /
NK101(de)002:1442: rnam pa rtog pa ci skyes pa thams cad chos nyid kyi rol pa yin te /
NK101(de)002:1443: ye shes su klong nol bas rang grol chen po'i klong ngo //
NK101(de)002:1444: de la phyogs gcig par brtags na mi rnyed cing
NK101(de)002:1445: rnam rtog tu 'gyur ba'i rigs pa rtog dang ma
NK101(de)002:1446: rtogs khyad med pas dge sdig la mi gnas pa'i
NK101(de)002:1448: yon tan chen po'i bsam gtan ni /
NK101(de)002:1449: zhes pa yang dag rgyun chad med pa'i dgongs pa bstan te /
NK101(de)002:1450: a ti yo ga rdzogs pa chen po gang la'ang
NK101(de)002:1451: skyon yon du mi lta bas thams cad yon tan
NK101(de)002:1452: chen po rang byung ye shes kyi bsam gtan dang
NK101(de)002:1453: dus rgyun du 'bral ba med pas yon tan shin
NK101(de)002:1454: tu che ste rnam rtog glo bur du byung yang
NK101(de)002:1455: / rang byung rang zhir sel ba'o //
NK101(de)002:1456: 'o na de la yul dang yul can dang ched du bsam rgyu yod dam snyam pa la /
NK101(de)002:1457: bsam gtan nyid pas bsam du med /
NK101(de)002:1458: ces ngo bo dmigs su med pa'i dgongs pa bstan te /
NK101(de)002:1459: bsam gtan nyid ni mnyam pa nyid kyi don yin pas /
NK101(de)002:1460: de la yul dang yul can du bsam du med pa ni yang dag pa'i bsam gtan yin la /
NK101(de)002:1461: dmigs gtad dang mtshan ma can du bsgom du med
NK101(de)002:1462: pa de nyid yang dag pa'i sgom pa yin pas
NK101(de)002:1464: ma bsam ma sbyangs chos bzhin du //
NK101(de)002:1465: zhes rnal ma rang lugs kyi dgongs pa bstan te /
NK101(de)002:1466: a ti yo ga rdzogs pa chen pos a nu
NK101(de)002:1467: pa yo ga bzhin du chos nyid du ma bsam
NK101(de)002:1468: dbu ma pa bzhin du rnam rtog ye shes su
NK101(de)002:1469: ma sbyangs par / sems nyid ma bcos pa'i rnal ma chos bzhin du 'dug pa rang las /
NK101(de)002:1470: rnam rtog nyid las ye shes skye //
NK101(de)002:1471: zhes pa rnam rtog ye shes su ldang ba'i dgongs pa bstan te /
NK101(de)002:1472: rang gi blo la bzang rtog ngan rtog ci 'gyus pa thams cad /
NK101(de)002:1473: chos nyid klong rdol ye shes rang byung la nyams myong phyogs med du skye ba'o //
NK101(de)002:1476: phra ba'i sgo mor ming btags shing //
