NK101(de)002:1477: zhes pa nyan thos kyi 'dod pa rnam par rtog par 'gyur ba'i rigs pa bstan te /
NK101(de)002:1478: 'phags pa nyan thos pa'i lugs kyis /
NK101(de)002:1479: rdul cha med rdzas grub don dam du yod pa de /
NK101(de)002:1480: gzugs can rigs pa skyed pa'i sgo mor ming 'dogs so //
NK101(de)002:1482: nyan thos bye brag pa'i lugs kyis nang gi shes
NK101(de)002:1483: pa las phyi rol gyi don logs na yod par
NK101(de)002:1484: 'dod de / dbus rdul zlum po cha med la
NK101(de)002:1485: mtha' yi rdul gyis bskor ba bar dang bcas par
NK101(de)002:1486: 'dzin byed kyi rlung gis bzung nas yod par 'dod
NK101(de)002:1487: 'dod de / / mdo sde pa'i lugs kyis /
NK101(de)002:1488: gong bu ma 'byar la bar med par reg pas dper na rtsig pa lta bur 'dod de /
NK101(de)002:1489: nang gi shes pa dang yul dang yul can du
NK101(de)002:1490: 'brel te rnam pa dang skad cig 'dab 'byar gyi
NK101(de)002:1491: tshul du lkog na mor bzhed do //
NK101(de)002:1492: sems kyi dben pa'i lam 'tshol zhing //
NK101(de)002:1493: zhes dbu ma'i 'dod pa thams cad rtog pa yin pa'i rigs pa bstan te /
NK101(de)002:1494: theg pa chen po dbu ma pa /
NK101(de)002:1495: phyi nang gzung 'dzin gyi 'khrul pa las dben par
NK101(de)002:1496: bya ba'i phyir na rnam par mi rtog pa'i ting
NK101(de)002:1497: nge 'dzin bsgoms nas lam mtshol lo //
NK101(de)002:1498: de'ang phyi rnam pa dben pa'i ting nge 'dzin nyan
NK101(de)002:1499: thos la sogs pas yul rdzas su brtags pa la
NK101(de)002:1500: / gcig dang du bral sogs kyis gzhal te /
NK101(de)002:1501: rang bzhin med par bsgoms pas dngos yul las dben pa dang /
NK101(de)002:1502: nang rgyu 'bras don dam du 'dzin pa la /
NK101(de)002:1503: rdo rje gzegs ma la sogs pas gzhal te /
NK101(de)002:1504: mi rtog pa'i ting nge 'dzin spros pa'i mtshan ma
NK101(de)002:1505: thams cad las dben pa'i lam du bsgom pa ni
NK101(de)002:1506: / dgon pa'i rgyud du dben 'dzin na //
NK101(de)002:1507: zhes der ma zad sngags phyi nang gi rigs pas
NK101(de)002:1508: rtsol ba rnams rtog par 'gyur ba'i rigs pa bstan
NK101(de)002:1509: te / lar ni rdzogs pa chen po a ti yo ga'i lugs kyis /
NK101(de)002:1510: khrom gyi nang na 'dug kyang rung /
NK101(de)002:1512: sems nyid don dang ma bral bas dgon gnas med kyang chog /
NK101(de)002:1513: de ltar ma go na dgon gnas rang yang rnam rtog yin pas /
NK101(de)002:1514: gsang sngags phyi nang gi sgor zhugs pa rnams kyis phyi nang gi gzung 'dzin nam /
NK101(de)002:1515: 'du 'dzi las dben par bya ba'i phyir /
NK101(de)002:1517: lha 'dre gdug pa can gyi rgyu srang med pa /
NK101(de)002:1518: skye bo phal mo ches mi sleb pa'i dgon gnas dben pa'am /
NK101(de)002:1519: ri rgyud bzang po lhun sdug pa'i sa bzung nas /
NK101(de)002:1522: ting nge 'dzin gyi dkyil 'khor bsgom mo //
NK101(de)002:1523: brtags na rnam par rtog 'gyur sgom //
NK101(de)002:1525: de yo la rdzogs pa chen po a ti yo gas yas nas mar bltas na /
NK101(de)002:1526: a nu man chad rtog pa'i gnyen por mi rtog
NK101(de)002:1527: pa sgom pa de rang bzang rtog gis 'ching ba
NK101(de)002:1528: / rtog pa nyid 'khrul du song ba yin no //
NK101(de)002:1530: rgyu dang 'bras bur ming btags nas //
NK101(de)002:1532: spyir na theg pa 'og ma pa'i lugs kyis /
NK101(de)002:1533: rgyu dge sdig la spyod pa'i dbang gis 'bras bu
NK101(de)002:1534: mtho ris dang ngan song so sor 'byung bar 'dod
NK101(de)002:1537: rgyu rten 'brel yan lag bcu gnyis su byung bas /
NK101(de)002:1538: 'bras bu 'khor ba grub pa'i tshul du 'dod pa dang /
NK101(de)002:1539: rgyu rten 'brel lugs las bzlog pas //
NK101(de)002:1540: 'bras bu myang 'das kyi sa la 'gro ba'i ming 'dogs pa'o //
NK101(de)002:1541: de la mi gnas par la bzla ste /
NK101(de)002:1542: dge sdig gnyis ka rnam par sel //
NK101(de)002:1543: zhes a ti yo ga rdzogs pa chen po'i rnal 'byor bas /
NK101(de)002:1544: thig le nyag gcig la skye shi 'pho 'gyur med par go //
NK101(de)002:1549: mtho ris dang ngan song du skye sa med /
NK101(de)002:1550: rig pa rang sa zin pas /
NK101(de)002:1551: dge ba la phan du re ba dang /
NK101(de)002:1552: sdig pa la gnod du dogs pa grol te /
NK101(de)002:1553: dge sdig gnyis med mnyam nyid chen po chos kyi
NK101(de)002:1554: sku'i klong du 'di ka ltar shar bas rang shar
NK101(de)002:1555: la / 'di ka ltar rang grol bas rang grol te mnyam pa nyid du sel bas /
NK101(de)002:1557: don rtogs rang du go ba yi //
NK101(de)002:1559: de la sgom sgrub dge ba'i chos //
NK101(de)002:1560: dkar po'i phyir dang sdig tu mnyam //
NK101(de)002:1561: zhes rigs pa rang stobs kyis dge sdig gi chos thams cad mnyam pa nyid du la zlo ba'o //
NK101(de)002:1563: zhes las 'bras gtsor 'dzin pa'i gtan tshigs rang log gi tshul yin te /
NK101(de)002:1564: de ltar mgo ba'i theg pa 'og ma pa la /
NK101(de)002:1565: las dge ba'i cha tsam la brten nas kyang /
NK101(de)002:1566: 'jig rten las byung ba'i 'bras bu thob par 'dod la /
NK101(de)002:1567: 'jig rten las yar 'byung ba'i 'bras bu ni dgra bcom pa'i go 'phang lta bu ste /
NK101(de)002:1568: srid pa'i rtse mo man chad zengs 'jigs pa'i dus na /
NK101(de)002:1569: 'dod pa chen po'i sa la gnas pas des mi
NK101(de)002:1570: 'jigs pa 'jig rten pa'i 'bras bu las yar nges
NK101(de)002:1572: blang dor brod pa mchog tu bskyed //
NK101(de)002:1574: de ni brod pas mdun bsu ba'i gtan tshigs te /
NK101(de)002:1575: des na 'og ma pa dkar po dge ba'i chos spyod du blang dgos /
NK101(de)002:1576: nag po mi dge ba'i phyogs rgyab tu dor dgos zer nas /
NK101(de)002:1577: byang chub mchog tu sems bskyed pa la gnas skabs
NK101(de)002:1578: kyi 'bras bur 'dzin pa de blang dor gnyis 'dzin
NK101(de)002:1580: a ti yo ga blang dor med pa'am /
NK101(de)002:1581: phyogs med bya bral gyi don las gol ba yin no //
NK101(de)002:1582: de'i rgyas gdab 'agre'o////da ni skabs brgyad pa la'ang /
NK101(de)002:1583: skabs kyi don bstan pa bden pa dbyer med kyi
NK101(de)002:1584: dgongs pa brag cha lta bur ngo bo ma grub
NK101(de)002:1586: chos thams cad gnyis su med pas phyogs su rgya ma chad pa'i rigs pa bstan pa /
NK101(de)002:1587: de nyid rna brgyud yin par nges pa'i gtan tshigs bstan pa dang bzhi las /
NK101(de)002:1589: gnyis su med pa skyon dang bral ba'i skabs /
NK101(de)002:1590: zhes gnyis su med pa ni thig le nyag gcig /
NK101(de)002:1592: phyi nang rtag chad gnyis sam /
NK101(de)002:1593: yul sems 'khrul grol gnyis sogs gang yang gnyis su med de /
NK101(de)002:1596: 'bras bu rang byung ye shes su gcig ste /
NK101(de)002:1597: gnyis su med pa la 'og ma pa tha dad
NK101(de)002:1598: du 'dzin pa ni mnyam pa nyid la gnyis su
NK101(de)002:1600: a ti yo ga snang srid 'khor 'das /
NK101(de)002:1601: yod med rtag chad phyi nang snod bcud kyis bsdus
NK101(de)002:1602: pa'i chos thams cad mnyam nyid chen po'i rang bzhin
NK101(de)002:1604: mtha' ru 'dzin pa'i skyon thams cad dang bral bar ston pa'i skabs la bab bo //
NK101(de)002:1606: 'dus ma byas pa'i chos nyid de //
NK101(de)002:1607: byang chub sems su gcig pa'i phyir //
NK101(de)002:1608: gnyis med skyon bral skabs zhes bya //
NK101(de)002:1611: chags dang ma chags tshig gi lam //
NK101(de)002:1613: 'khor 'das kyi chos thams cad kun rdzob tu lha dang lha mo'i dkyil 'khor du brtags pa dang /
NK101(de)002:1614: de la rang bzhin med pas don dam bden par btags pa la sogs pa de /
NK101(de)002:1615: a ti yo ga lta ba dbyer med do //
NK101(de)002:1617: gang du dbyer med na gzhi lhun grub ngo bo nges med don skye med /
NK101(de)002:1618: bdag nyid thog tha dang bral bar dbyer med pas /
NK101(de)002:1619: mnyam pa nyid la dgag sgrub med cing dbye ru med pas dgongs pa chos nyid kyi klong ngo //
NK101(de)002:1621: grag tsam nyid na rang bzhin med de glo bur du 'byung ba bzhin /
NK101(de)002:1622: rgyu rkyen du btags pa thams cad glo bur ba yin te /
NK101(de)002:1623: chos nyid 'di yin gyi ngo bor ma grub pas
NK101(de)002:1624: 'khor 'das kyi chos thams cad rang shar rang grol
NK101(de)002:1625: gyi klong ngo // de la 'khor 'das kyi chos thams cad mnyam pas /
NK101(de)002:1626: phyogs su rgya ma chad pa'i rigs pa de kho
NK101(de)002:1627: na lung dang man ngag gi grub pas gzhi rgyu
NK101(de)002:1628: yin nges pa'i gtan tshigs 'byung ngo //
NK101(de)002:1630: chags dang ma chags tshig gi lam //
NK101(de)002:1631: zhes chags pa kun rdzob kyi bden pa dang 'khor ba'i chos /
NK101(de)002:1632: ma chags pa don dam bden pa'am zhi ba myang 'das /
NK101(de)002:1633: de gnyis ka a ti yo ga ltar na /
NK101(de)002:1634: tshig gi lam stegs tsam yin te /
NK101(de)002:1635: dngos gzhi la med pa'i phyir ro //
NK101(de)002:1636: dbu ma bzhin te brag cha 'dra //
NK101(de)002:1637: zhes pa rang dpe rang gis byed pa'i dgongs pa bstan te /
NK101(de)002:1638: dper na brag cha grag tsam rang bzhin med pa bzhin du /
NK101(de)002:1639: 'khor 'das ltar shar yang de la rang bzhin med pa dang /
NK101(de)002:1640: bden gnyis su btags kyang de la gdags gzhi med pa dang /
NK101(de)002:1641: ming thams cad glo bur ba yin pa'i phyir dbu
NK101(de)002:1642: ma chen po rtsol ba dang bral bar rang bzhin
NK101(de)002:1643: med pa dang / brag cha grag tsam na ngo
NK101(de)002:1644: bo stong pa gnyis 'dra ba'i dpe ru bstan pa'o
NK101(de)002:1645: med pa dang / // de rnams kyi skyon bsal dang la bzla 'dra /
NK101(de)002:1647: bde dang sdug bsngal rgyu mthun zhes //
NK101(de)002:1648: zhes pa mya ngan las 'das pa'i bde ba dang /
NK101(de)002:1649: 'khor ba'i sdug bsngal gnyis ka gar mthun rgyu chos nyid /
NK101(de)002:1651: 'bras bu rang byung ye shes su chos mthun pa
NK101(de)002:1652: zhes gnyis su med cing mnyam nyid chen por lta'o
NK101(de)002:1654: 'gro ba'i mgon po sems dpas gsungs //
NK101(de)002:1656: 'o na 'khor 'das sam bde sdug gnyis po rgyu mthun du sus gsungs she na /
NK101(de)002:1657: 'gro ba nyon mongs pas khrid pa rnams kyi skyabs
NK101(de)002:1658: sam mgon nam dpung gnyen lta bur gyur pa'i rgyal
NK101(de)002:1659: mchog kun tu bzang pos rdo rje sems dpa' la
NK101(de)002:1660: gsungs la / rdo rje sems dpas sprul pa'i sku
NK101(de)002:1661: dga' rab rdo rje la gsungs te rim par brgyud
NK101(de)002:1662: gsungs la / do // de rnams kyi rgyas gdab 'agre'o////da ni skabs dgu pa la'ang /
NK101(de)002:1664: dug gsum lam du khyer ba'i dgongs pa rma byas
NK101(de)002:1665: btsan dug zos pa lta bur yon tan chen po'i
NK101(de)002:1667: gang yang ma spangs la skyon gyis ma gos pa'i rigs pa bstan pa /
NK101(de)002:1668: chos thams cad ci yang ma yin pas nges med du 'char ba'i gtan tshigs bstan pa /
NK101(de)002:1669: thig le'i nges tshig bstan pa dang lnga las /
NK101(de)002:1671: ye shes rang las 'byung ba'i skabs //
NK101(de)002:1673: ye shes ni rig pa phyi nang med cing nges
NK101(de)002:1674: med phyogs med du shar bas nub pa med la
NK101(de)002:1675: / sgrib g.yogs dang bral bas mtha' dang mun pa ye nas med pa'o //
NK101(de)002:1676: rang las byung ba ni rgyu rkyen gyis ma bskyed pas 'dus byas ma yin pa dang /
NK101(de)002:1677: byed pa pos ma byas pa'i don ston pa'i skabs la bab bo //
NK101(de)002:1679: chos kun rang gi sems la 'dus //
NK101(de)002:1680: sems kyi rtogs pa bshad pa'i phyir //
NK101(de)002:1681: ye shes rang byung skabs zhes bya //
NK101(de)002:1685: ri rab rtse la nyi ma stong shar bas //
NK101(de)002:1686: ye shes thugs kyi nyi ma gcig shar dro //
NK101(de)002:1687: shar ba nyid na nub pa med ces gsungs //
NK101(de)002:1690: 'dod chags zhe sdang gti mug kyang //
NK101(de)002:1691: zhes dug gsum ni 'khor bar skye bar byed pa'i rgyu yin te /
NK101(de)002:1692: 'dod chags ser sna yid la 'jug cing len pa /
NK101(de)002:1693: zhe sdang mnar gzhi yid la 'jug cing sod par byed /
NK101(de)002:1694: gti mug ni nyon mongs can 'jug dge sdig gnyis la rmongs pas /
NK101(de)002:1695: theg pa 'og ma pa'i gang zag rnams /
NK101(de)002:1696: nyon mongs pa btsan dug lta bu'am dgra dang tsher mar bltas te spor ba nyid /
NK101(de)002:1697: a ti yo ga pas 'dod chags chags bral chen po /
NK101(de)002:1698: zhe sdang rang byung ye shes /
NK101(de)002:1699: gti mug chos nyid dbye med du rang shar bas /
NK101(de)002:1700: dug gsum gtan sprugs te sku gsum dbyer med du lam khyer byas pas /
NK101(de)002:1701: dug gsum lam khyer gyi dgongs pa chos nyid kyi klong ngo //
NK101(de)002:1702: rma byas btsan dug zos pa lta bu ni /
NK101(de)002:1703: btsan dug de kho'i zas skal yin pas /
NK101(de)002:1704: dug gis gnod pa med par yon tan gyi kha dog legs shing skad snyan pa ltar /
NK101(de)002:1705: dug gsum ma spangs bar sku gsum phyogs med du
NK101(de)002:1706: shar bas khams gsum rang sar grol ba'i yon tan
NK101(de)002:1707: yod de / 'khor 'das kyi chos thams cad de las shar zhing de ru grol ba'i klong ngo /
NK101(de)002:1708: de la 'dod pa'i yon tan lnga rgyan du shar
NK101(de)002:1709: bas ma spangs skyon gyis ma gos pa'i rigs pa
NK101(de)002:1710: / de la ye shes phyogs med du 'char bas
NK101(de)002:1711: chos thams cad ci yang ma yin par nges med
NK101(de)002:1712: du 'char ba'i gtan tshigs byung ngo //
NK101(de)002:1714: 'dod chags zhe sdang gti mug kyang //
NK101(de)002:1715: zhes pa ma rtogs pa la dug gsum rang ga ma ste /
NK101(de)002:1716: dper na btsan dug gi phung po chen po gcig yod na /
NK101(de)002:1718: sman pas sman nus kyis bsgyur nas sman du gtong /
NK101(de)002:1719: sngags mkhan gyis sngags kyi nub pas bsad nas za /
NK101(de)002:1720: rma bya des gang yang mi byed par zos pas
NK101(de)002:1721: slar la kha dog legs shing skad snyan pa bzhin
NK101(de)002:1722: du / de dang 'dra ba'i dug gsum mam lnga po 'di la /
NK101(de)002:1723: nyan thos rang rgyal gyis dgra dang tsher mar bltas nas spong /
NK101(de)002:1724: dbu ma sems tsam gyis phyogs dang pha rol phyin pas spyod /
NK101(de)002:1725: gsang ba sngags kyis dbang bzhi'i las kyis bsgyur nas sangs rgyas par 'dod pa la /
NK101(de)002:1726: rdzogs pa chen po de dag gang yang mi byed par /
NK101(de)002:1729: zhe sdang gsal yangs ye shes /
NK101(de)002:1730: gti mug 'byed med chos nyid dam /
NK101(de)002:1731: nga rgyal rang rig rang klong /
NK101(de)002:1732: phrag dog mnyam chen kun grol du rang shar ba la /
NK101(de)002:1733: dug lnga gang yang ma spangs rang sar grol bas /
NK101(de)002:1734: byang chub kyi sems bde ba chen po 'phags lam
NK101(de)002:1735: rang byung ye shes rang las rang 'byung bar rtogs
NK101(de)002:1736: na / nyon mongs pa gang yang spang du med pa'i phyir /
NK101(de)002:1737: byang chub chen po'i lam la 'byung //
NK101(de)002:1739: de'i skyon bsal dang la bzla 'dra'o //
NK101(de)002:1741: kun spyod yon tan rnam lnga yang //
NK101(de)002:1742: zhes pa rgyal ba yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas nas dmyal ba'i gting yan chad /
NK101(de)002:1743: 'dod yon rnam pa lnga la spyod yul thun mong bar gnas pas /
NK101(de)002:1744: chos nyid dbyings kyi rgyan zhes gsungs //
NK101(de)002:1745: zhes 'dod yon spang du med pa'i rigs pa bstan te /
NK101(de)002:1746: 'dod yon ji ltar shar yang thams cad rang byung
NK101(de)002:1747: gi rol pa yin pas chos nyid kyi rgyan yin
NK101(de)002:1748: pa dang / snang ba gang yang mi 'gog par dbyings kyi rgyan yin pa dang /
NK101(de)002:1749: rol pa rang rgyud pa med par chos nyid dbyings kyi rgyan yin pa dang /
NK101(de)002:1750: chad pa'i mtha' bsal bas chos nyid dbyings kyi rgyan yin pas na /
NK101(de)002:1751: de dag la spyad kyang skyon med de spang bya ma dmigs pas mi spong /
NK101(de)002:1752: de ltar yin par sus gsungs she na /
NK101(de)002:1753: kun tu bzang pos rdo rje sems dpa' la /
NK101(de)002:1754: des dga' rab rdo rje la gsungs so //
NK101(de)002:1756: nam mkha'i rtog pa skye med cing //
NK101(de)002:1757: zhes chos nyid skye ba med pa'i gtan tshigs bstan te /
NK101(de)002:1758: gzhi lhun gyis grub pa mtha' yi rtog pa rang ka ma med pa'i dpe yin te /
NK101(de)002:1759: gzhi mi 'gyur lhun gyis grub pa'i chos nyid /
NK101(de)002:1760: mnyam nyid nam mkha' lta bu klong du 'khor 'das
NK101(de)002:1761: lam pas bsdus pa'i chos thams cad ma btsal bzhin
NK101(de)002:1762: du lhun gyis grub pa la /
NK101(de)002:1763: gzhan gyi rtog pa skye sa med do //
NK101(de)002:1764: rtog pa de nyid nam mkha' 'dra //
NK101(de)002:1765: zhes pa rol pa cir yang 'char ba'i gtan tshigs bstan te /
NK101(de)002:1766: ngo bo nges med du 'char ba la mtshan ma rang rgyud par med pa'i dpe yin te /
NK101(de)002:1768: rol pa ji ltar shar yang nam mkha' dang gnyis su med pa bzhin du /
NK101(de)002:1769: rnam par rtog pa glo bur du byung srid na'ang /
NK101(de)002:1770: chos nyid bya bral nam mkha' lta bu de dang dbyer med pa'o //
NK101(de)002:1772: mi chags nam mkha'i dngos po la //
NK101(de)002:1773: zhes mtha' thams cad las grol ba'i gtan tshigs bstan te /
NK101(de)002:1774: don skye ba med pa'i rang bzhin de matha'i skyon gang la'ang mi chags pa'i dpe yin te /
NK101(de)002:1775: dpe na nam mkha' ni dngos po dang mtshan ma gang du'ang mi 'chags pa bzhin du /
NK101(de)002:1776: skye med kyi rig pa yul med du shar ba la mtha' spang du med do //
NK101(de)002:1777: rang don chen po nam mkha' 'byung //
NK101(de)002:1778: zhes pa 'bras bu rang las 'byung ba'i gtan tshigs bstan te /
NK101(de)002:1779: bdag nyid thog mtha' med pa la //
NK101(de)002:1780: yon tan phyogs med du 'byung ba'i dpe yin te /
NK101(de)002:1781: dper na nam mkha' cir yang ma grub pa las
NK101(de)002:1782: 'dod yon lnga'i cho 'phrul byung nas sems can gyi
NK101(de)002:1784: bdag nyid thog mtha' dang bral ba'i chos nyid bya bral gyi klong nas /
NK101(de)002:1785: 'khor 'das kyi yon tan nam lam dang 'bras bu'i chos thams cad mi bslu bar 'byung bas so //
NK101(de)002:1786: lnga pa thig le'i nges tshig bstan pa ni /
NK101(de)002:1787: dang po phyogs ris dag pa /
NK101(de)002:1788: gnyis pa dge sdig dag pa /
NK101(de)002:1789: gsum pa bde sdug dag pa /
NK101(de)002:1790: bzhi pa dug lnga dang 'dod yon dag par bstan pa'o //
NK101(de)002:1791: dbyings rnam par dag pa'i thig le /
NK101(de)002:1792: zhes rig pa mu med cing mtha' thams cad bral bas dbyings /
NK101(de)002:1793: cho 'phrul zad mi shes par 'byung bas kyang dbyings /
NK101(de)002:1794: gnyis 'dzin gyi spros pa thams cad rnam par dag pa la /
NK101(de)002:1795: ma spros kun la khyab pa dang gdal ba chen por gnas pas na thig le'o //
NK101(de)002:1796: rgyas gdab 'agre'o////da ni skabs bcu pa la'ang /
NK101(de)002:1798: chos nyid gnyis su med pa dgongs pa chu zla
NK101(de)002:1799: lta bur gsal 'grib med pa'i klong du bstan pa
NK101(de)002:1800: / kun tu bzang po mnyam pa nyid cir yang 'char ba'i rigs pa bstan pa /
NK101(de)002:1801: yul dang lam ma dmigs pa la bgrod rtsol can
NK101(de)002:1802: gyi sa lam med pa'i gtan tshigs bstan pa bzhi
NK101(de)002:1804: gzungs kyi sbyor thabs kyi skabs /
NK101(de)002:1805: zhes gzungs ni chos nyid 'du 'bral med pa'i don la bya ste /
NK101(de)002:1806: de yis 'khor 'das thams cad la khyab ste mi gtong bar gnas pa na gzungs /
NK101(de)002:1807: thams cad kyi srog yin pas na'ang gzungs /
NK101(de)002:1808: mtha' phyogs gcig ma g.yos pas na'ang gzungs so //
NK101(de)002:1812: gnyis su snang ba thams cad theg le nyag gcig la /
NK101(de)002:1813: ngo bo dbyer med du sbyor ba nyid ston pa'i skabs la bab bo //
NK101(de)002:1815: chos kun rang gi sems la 'dus //
NK101(de)002:1816: sems dang bral ba med pa'i phyir //
NK101(de)002:1817: gzungs kyi sbyor thabs skabs zhes bya //
NK101(de)002:1820: rtog med mnyam nyid chos kyi sku //
NK101(de)002:1821: zhes chos nyid ni rtogs rung ma rtogs rung sems can thams cad kyi sems nyid /
NK101(de)002:1822: rgyu rkyen las ka nas ma byung //
NK101(de)002:1824: dngos po gshis kyi chos nyid do //
NK101(de)002:1825: de la 'khor 'das kyi chos thams cad ngo bo dbyer med pas /
NK101(de)002:1826: gzhi ngo bo don bdag nyid mnyam pa chen po'i
NK101(de)002:1827: rang bzhin la gnyis su med pa'i dgongs pa chos
NK101(de)002:1831: gsal la rtog pa med pa'i dpe ste /
NK101(de)002:1832: thig le byang chub sems la 'khor 'das /
NK101(de)002:1834: skye shi ji ltar snang yang rang bzhin med pa'i
NK101(de)002:1835: ngang la shar zhing de ru grol bas mnyam nyid
NK101(de)002:1836: ngos gzung med pa'i klong zhes bya'o //
NK101(de)002:1837: de la mtha' gang yang ma spangs pas mnyam nyid cir yang 'char ba'i rigs pa /
NK101(de)002:1838: de dmigs pa'i yul las 'das pas yul dang lam
NK101(de)002:1839: la bgrod rtsol can du med pa'i gtan tshigs byung
NK101(de)002:1841: rtog med mnyam nyid chos kyi sku //
NK101(de)002:1842: zhes mnyam pa ris med kyi dgongs pa bstan te /
NK101(de)002:1844: rang rig byang chub kyi sems /
NK101(de)002:1845: ma bcos pa'i chos nyid la /
NK101(de)002:1846: phyi nang gnyis su mi rtog ste zang thal /
NK101(de)002:1847: yul sems gnyis su mi rtog ste ris med /
NK101(de)002:1848: rtag chad gnyis su mi rtog ste mnyam pa nyid
NK101(de)002:1849: la 'pho 'gyur med pas 'bras bu chos kyi sku'o
NK101(de)002:1850: // bzung bas mi zin chu zla 'dra //
NK101(de)002:1851: zhes snang la rang bzhin med pa'i dgongs pa /
NK101(de)002:1852: gzhi lhun grub ngo bo nges med rol pa phyogs med du 'char ba la /
NK101(de)002:1853: mtha' phyogs gcig tu 'di kho na yin no zhes nges bzung du ma rnyed pas /
NK101(de)002:1854: chu zla ltar gsal 'grib med par sprul pa'i sku phyogs med du shar ba'o //
NK101(de)002:1855: de'i skyon bsal dang la ba zla 'dra /
NK101(de)002:1857: kun tu bzang po'i rol pa yis //
NK101(de)002:1858: zhes mtha' thams cad du rang shar ba'i rigs pa bstan te /
NK101(de)002:1859: gzhi ngo bo'i don bdag nyid mnyam pa nyid chen po'i rang bzhin la /
NK101(de)002:1860: dus thams cad bzang ngan dang blang dor med pas kun tu bzang po /
NK101(de)002:1861: yang na ma 'dres la yongs su rdzogs pas kun tu bzang po /
NK101(de)002:1862: rig pa cir yang mi 'gag par cir yang 'char ba ste /
NK101(de)002:1863: 'khor 'das thams cad du ma 'gags par shar ba'i rol pa yis /
NK101(de)002:1864: sgra ji bzhin par bshad na /
NK101(de)002:1865: +aa li k+aa li zab tu bstan /
NK101(de)002:1866: zhes kun tu bzang po shes rab kyi rang bzhin
NK101(de)002:1867: yon tan skye ba med pa'i don kun tu bzang
NK101(de)002:1868: po thabs kyi rang bzhin skye med kyi rig pa
NK101(de)002:1869: phyogs med du ma 'gags pa'i don te /
NK101(de)002:1871: skye 'gag gnyis med pa'i zab mo byang chub kyi sems /
NK101(de)002:1872: thig le nyag gcig de zab cing cha phra la brtag par dka' bas zab tu bstan no //
NK101(de)002:1873: sgra thang log tu bshad na /
NK101(de)002:1874: +aa li zhes pas ma skyes pa rgyu ma tshan /
NK101(de)002:1875: k+aa li zhes pas go bzlog pa ste /
NK101(de)002:1876: skye med nyid skye ba ltar shar bas rgyu mtshan go bzlog go //
NK101(de)002:1877: zab tu bstan zhes skye ba dang skye med la
NK101(de)002:1878: khyad med pas 'bras bu re dogs chod pas shin
NK101(de)002:1879: tu zab bo // yang na +aa li zhes pa skye med rang gi mtshan nyid la /
NK101(de)002:1880: k+aa li zhes pa skye med spyi'i mtshan nyid de /
NK101(de)002:1881: zab tu bstan zhes spyi dang rang gi mtshan nyid gnyis su med pas /
NK101(de)002:1882: thams cad zab mo byang chub kyi sems thig le nyag gcig phyogs med 'ba' zhig tu bstan no //
NK101(de)002:1883: 'di ni a dang mdzes pa'i ta //
NK101(de)002:1884: zhes pa des na chos nyid thig le nyag gcig
NK101(de)002:1885: skye 'gag gnyis med mnyam pa chen po'i don 'di
NK101(de)002:1886: / a dang 'dra ste rgyu rkyen dang bral te skye ba med la /
NK101(de)002:1887: ma skyes pa'i rig pa de cho 'phrul cir yang mi 'gag par 'char bas /
NK101(de)002:1888: skye med kyi rgyan du snang ste longs spyod rdzogs pa'i sku phyogs med yin te mdzes pa'i ta'o //
NK101(de)002:1889: pa dang yan lag spros pa bzhin //
NK101(de)002:1890: zhes pa byang sems skyon med du 'char ba'i rigs
NK101(de)002:1891: pa dper na pad+ma'i rtsa ba 'dam na gnas kyang
NK101(de)002:1893: des na me tog yal ga thams cad skyon med
NK101(de)002:1894: par slar la yon tan gyi kha dog legs shing
NK101(de)002:1896: gzhi lhun grub matha'i skyon med /
NK101(de)002:1897: chos nyid nges med kyi spyod pa phyogs med du shar bas /
NK101(de)002:1898: mthar 'dzin gyi dus dang rnam pa thams cad du ma gos te phyogs med du rang shar ba'o //
NK101(de)002:1899: 'jig rten yongs kyi spyod yul la //
NK101(de)002:1900: zhes pa snang ba gang yang mi 'gog pa'i rigs pa bstan te /
NK101(de)002:1902: bstod smad la sogs par tha mal yongs kyis btags
NK101(de)002:1903: pa'i spyod yul ma dag 'khrul ba'i snang ba rang
NK101(de)002:1905: sangs rgyas gsung gi zab mo 'byung //
NK101(de)002:1906: zhes ston pa rang las 'byung ba'i rigs pa bstan te /
NK101(de)002:1907: rdzogs pa chen po'i don go ba'i dus na /
NK101(de)002:1908: snang zhing srid pas bsdus pa'i chos thams cad /
NK101(de)002:1909: slob dpon du ma song ba'am /
NK101(de)002:1910: dpe char ma song ba gang yang med de /
NK101(de)002:1911: sangs rgyas kyi gsung ni kun tu bzang po'i rol
NK101(de)002:1912: pa phyogs bral nges med du shar ba la bya
NK101(de)002:1913: ste / snang ba 'di dag thams cad ngo bo nyid kyi ston pa kun tu bzang po /
NK101(de)002:1914: rang gi mtshan nyid 'dzin pa'i chos nyid tshul ston pas /
NK101(de)002:1915: sa chu me rlung la sogs pa'i sgra thams cad gsang sngags kyi sgra 'ba' zhig yin te /
NK101(de)002:1917: nam mkha' don gyi glegs bam la //
NK101(de)002:1918: sna tshogs rigs pa'i ye shes bris //
NK101(de)002:1919: 'byung chen bzhi yi sgrar grags nas //
NK101(de)002:1920: gsang sngags rgyal po rgyun mi 'chad //
NK101(de)002:1922: des na cir snang cir srid cir grag thams cad
NK101(de)002:1923: gsang sngags zab mo'i sgra 'ba' zhig tu rtogs par
NK101(de)002:1925: e ma sangs rgyas spyod yul 'di //
NK101(de)002:1926: zhes pa ngam zhing ngo mtshar rmad du byung ba'i gtan tshigs bstan te /
NK101(de)002:1927: snang zhing srid pas bsdus pa'i chos thams cad ye
NK101(de)002:1928: yin chen por ram dngos yin chen por sangs rgyas
NK101(de)002:1929: pas na / 'jig rten 'di nyid zhing dag pa sangs rgyas kyi zhing khams /
NK101(de)002:1930: snang ba 'di nyid kun tu bzang po'i mdzad spyod dam /
NK101(de)002:1931: rnam par dag pa'i spyod yul yin pa la ngo mtshar ba'o //
NK101(de)002:1932: btsal bas rnyed pa'i gnas med de //
NK101(de)002:1933: zhes pa ye nas yin pa'i gtan tshigs bstan te /
NK101(de)002:1934: 'jig rten rang ka ma'i snang ba 'di nyid rang /
NK101(de)002:1935: bde ba chen po'i zhing khams sam /
NK101(de)002:1936: rnam par dag pa sangs rgyas kyi zhing khams phyogs
NK101(de)002:1937: med dngos rang ye nas yin par ma shes na
NK101(de)002:1938: gzhan nas btsal bas rnyed pa'i gnas sam dmigs pa'i
NK101(de)002:1940: drug gi chos bzhin yul med pas //
NK101(de)002:1941: zhes dmigs pa'i mtha' las 'das pa'i gtan tshigs bstan te /
NK101(de)002:1942: chos nyid mtshan ma med pa'i klong du ye nas rang shar ba la /
NK101(de)002:1943: mig gis gzugs su gcad la ce re lta ba'am /
NK101(de)002:1944: rna bas sgra ru bcad la lhag ne nyan pa'am /
NK101(de)002:1945: sna yis dri ru bcad la tu re snam pa'am /
NK101(de)002:1946: lce yis ro ru bcad la rjen ner myong ba'am /
NK101(de)002:1947: lus kyis res byar bcad de ye re reg pa'am /
NK101(de)002:1948: yid kyis chos su bcad de ling nger bsam du med de /
NK101(de)002:1949: rig pa yul dang yul can gnyis su med pa la /
NK101(de)002:1950: gnyis su 'dzin na 'khrul pa yin pas /
NK101(de)002:1951: mdongs pas nam mkha' bsnyabs pa bzhin /
NK101(de)002:1952: zhes dpe'i gtan tshigs bstan te /
NK101(de)002:1953: rig pa yul med la yul du tshol na /
NK101(de)002:1954: dper na dmus long gis nam mkha' la rdzas su
NK101(de)002:1955: btsal nas lag pas bsnyabs pas dngos por ma rnyed
NK101(de)002:1956: pa bzhin du / chos nyid phyogs med dmigs pa'i
NK101(de)002:1957: yul las 'das pa la mtshan mar rnyed pa'i dus
NK101(de)002:1958: pa bzhin du / med do // gang nas gong du tshangs pa'i lam //
NK101(de)002:1959: zhes pa lam la bgrod du med pa'i gtan tshigs bstan te /
NK101(de)002:1960: rgyu mtshan nyid theg pa'i lam la //
NK101(de)002:1961: tshogs lam du dran pa nyer bzhag bzhi /
NK101(de)002:1963: rdzu 'phrul gyi rkang pa bzhi ste bcu gnyis /
NK101(de)002:1964: sbyor lam du nges 'byed bzhi la /
NK101(de)002:1965: dbang po lnga dang stobs lnga /
NK101(de)002:1966: mthong lam du byang chub kyi yan lag bdun /
NK101(de)002:1967: sgom lam du 'phags lam yan lag brgyad dang rnam thar sgo gsum du gsungs pa la /
NK101(de)002:1968: lam gong ma'i yon tan bden pa phra mo re re mthong ba tsam la /
NK101(de)002:1969: 'og ma la skyon du bltas nas spong ba dang /
NK101(de)002:1970: lam gong ma gong ma la /
NK101(de)002:1971: tshangs pa zhi ba gya nom par bgrod rtsol byed pa de /
NK101(de)002:1972: a ti yo ga dang phyogs re tsam du mthong bas gang yang ma bkag pas mthun yang /
NK101(de)002:1973: phyogs mtha' dag nas mthun pa med pa'i khyad par gyis /
NK101(de)002:1974: bya bral chos dang mthun pa med //
NK101(de)002:1975: ces a ti yo ga rdzogs pa chen po'i lugs
NK101(de)002:1976: kyis lam bgrod du med pas nye ring bya rtsol
NK101(de)002:1977: dang bral te bya bral gyi chos de la sa
NK101(de)002:1978: la sbyong du med pas mtho dman gyi chos dang
NK101(de)002:1979: bral bas / gzhi gnas ye grol yin pa la
NK101(de)002:1980: da gdod grol bar 'dod pa'i dmigs mtha' thams cad
NK101(de)002:1981: bral bas / dang bral ba / ji ltar bya
NK101(de)002:1982: bral klong chen gzhi gnas ye grol skye shi rtsad
NK101(de)002:1983: nas gcod pa'i chos zab mo dang /
NK101(de)002:1984: thun mong nus pa 'byin pa'i chos a nu man chad mthun pa med de /
NK101(de)002:1985: a nu man chad bskal pa dang mi tsher bgrangs nas /
NK101(de)002:1986: dus phyi ma la 'tshang rgya bar 'dod pa dang /
NK101(de)002:1987: a ti yo ga dus la mi ltos te /
NK101(de)002:1988: ye yin chen por sangs rgyas pa yin pas mi mthun te khyad par che'o //
NK101(de)002:1989: ci ste lam la bgrod gyur na //
NK101(de)002:1990: zhes pa thug pa med pa'i gtan tshigs bstan te /
NK101(de)002:1993: rtsol bral gyi klung lam du ye nas zhugs zin kyang /
NK101(de)002:1994: 'og ma sa lam nye ring dang gnas mtho dman gzhan du bgrod par gyur na /
NK101(de)002:1995: nam mkha'i mtha' bzhin thug pa med //
NK101(de)002:1996: ces pa 'bras bu mi rnyed pa dpe'i gtan tshigs yin te /
NK101(de)002:1997: dper na nam mkha' la mtha' btsal bas mi rnyed de /
NK101(de)002:1998: kha gting dang rgya khyon med pas thug pa dang bral ba bzhin du /
NK101(de)002:1999: bzang rtog dang ngan rtog lam gong 'og bltas pas /
NK101(de)002:2000: rtog pa rang las byung ba'i phyir lam gyi mtha' stor te /
NK101(de)002:2001: 'bras bu mthar thug pa mi rnyed cing lam la thug pa med pa'i skyon du 'gyur ro //
NK101(de)002:2002: de rnams kyi rgyas gdab 'dra'o////da ni skabs bcu gcig pa la'ang /
NK101(de)002:2004: 'khor ba gzhir bzhengs kyi dgongs pa mig gis kun
NK101(de)002:2005: mthong yang rang ma mthong ba lta bur ye sangs
NK101(de)002:2006: rgyas pa'i klong du bstan pa /
NK101(de)002:2007: dngos po lo rgyus kyi rigs pa bstan pa /
NK101(de)002:2008: chos nyid ris ma chad pa'i gtan tshigs kyis phyogs lta dag par bstan pa dang bzhi las /
NK101(de)002:2011: zhes pa snang srid 'khor 'das yod med rtag chad
NK101(de)002:2012: phyi nang snod bcud kyis bsdus pa'i chos thams cad
NK101(de)002:2016: gzhi ngo bo don bdag nyid mnyam pa nyid kyi thig le nyag gcig /
NK101(de)002:2017: bya rtsol dang bral ba'i klong du rdzogs /
NK101(de)002:2019: ma brtsal lhun gyis grub pa'i tshul du rdzogs pa dang /
NK101(de)002:2020: ma spangs rang sar grol ba'i tshul du rdzogs pa dang /
NK101(de)002:2021: ma 'dres yongs su rdzogs pa'i tshul du rdzogs pa dang /
NK101(de)002:2022: rgya chad phyogs lhung med pa'i tshul du rdzogs par ston pa'i skabs la bab bo //
NK101(de)002:2024: chos kun rang gi sems la 'dus //
NK101(de)002:2025: sems la chos kun rdzogs pa'i phyir //
NK101(de)002:2026: yongs su rdzogs pa'i skabs zhes bya //
NK101(de)002:2029: de ltar de bzhin de yi phyir //
NK101(de)002:2030: zhes 'khor ba rang rgyud pa bya ba gtan nas med de /
NK101(de)002:2031: gzhi nas bzhengs pas a ti yo ga'i lugs kyis /
NK101(de)002:2032: 'khor ba'i gzhi ni mya ngan las 'das par dngos su ye nas bzhengs pa dang /
NK101(de)002:2038: nyon mongs ye shes su dngos kyi tshul du ye nas bzhengs pa dang /
NK101(de)002:2039: snang srid 'khor 'das yod med rtag chad phyi nang
NK101(de)002:2040: snod bcud kyi bsdus pa'i chos thams cad gzhi thig
NK101(de)002:2041: le nyag gcig byang chub sems su bzhengs la /
NK101(de)002:2042: byang chub kyi sems de nyid yod pa med pa
NK101(de)002:2043: gnyis dang gnyis med mdor na gnyis bsdus gang du'ang
NK101(de)002:2044: med par rang bzhin kun tu gsal ba'i gzhi bzhengs
NK101(de)002:2045: chen po dgongs pa chos nyid kyi klong ngo //
NK101(de)002:2046: mig gis kun mthong yang rang ma mthong ba ni /
NK101(de)002:2047: gzugs la sogs pa gzhan gyi legs nyes lta ba byed pa mig yin yang /
NK101(de)002:2048: mig rang gis rang ma mthong ba bzhin du /
NK101(de)002:2049: 'khor 'das kyi chos thams cad sems shar ba yin kyang rang gi ngo bo dmigs su med de /
NK101(de)002:2050: ye sangs rgyas pa'i klong nas 'khor 'das thams cad rang shar rang grol ba'i klong ngo //
NK101(de)002:2051: de nyid bden par yid ches pa dngos po lo rgyus kyi rigs pa /
NK101(de)002:2052: de la rgya chad dang phyogs lhung med pas chos nyid ris ma chad pa'i gtan tshigs byung ngo //
NK101(de)002:2054: de ltar de bzhin de yi phyir //
NK101(de)002:2056: de ltar gzhi bzhengs chen po'i dgongs pa la snang
NK101(de)002:2057: srid 'khor 'das yod med rtag chad phyi nang snod
NK101(de)002:2058: bcud kyis bsdus pa'i chos thams cad de bzhin nyid
NK101(de)002:2059: kyi dbyings su ye thog ma nas sangs rgyas pas
NK101(de)002:2060: / gzhi gnas ye grol bya bral klong chen gyi ngang du ye nas sangs rgyas pa yin kyang /
NK101(de)002:2062: sangs rgyas yin pa la yin pa ru ma shes
NK101(de)002:2063: chos nyid kyi don ma go ba rnams la bstan
NK101(de)002:2064: dgos pa de'i phyir bstan pa dam pa la rag
NK101(de)002:2065: las shing / bshes gnyen bka' drin can bstan dgos so //
NK101(de)002:2066: de'i skyon bsal dang la bzla 'dra /
NK101(de)002:2068: de la de bstan de yang thob //
NK101(de)002:2069: ces pa rgyal ba dgongs pas brgyud pa'i dbang du byas na /
NK101(de)002:2070: longs spyod rdzogs sku ston pa rdo rje sems dpa' de la /
NK101(de)002:2071: chos kyi sku mchog ston pa kun tu bzang po des bstan pa'am /
NK101(de)002:2072: sprul pa'i sku mchog dga' rab rdo rje de la /
NK101(de)002:2073: longs sku'i ston pa rdo rje 'chang chen de yis
NK101(de)002:2074: byin gyis rlabs kyi sgo nas nor bu rin po
NK101(de)002:2076: dgongs pa dbyer med de thob par gyur to //
NK101(de)002:2077: rig 'dzin rig pa'i brgyud pa dang gang zag snyan khungs brgyud pa'idabanga du byas na /
NK101(de)002:2078: gong ma gong ma'i slob dpon pha dang 'dra ba
NK101(de)002:2079: des 'og ma 'og ma'i slob bu bu dang 'dra
NK101(de)002:2080: ba der / gdams ngag nor bu rin po che dang 'dra ba de /
NK101(de)002:2081: rig 'dzin rig pa'i gsung dang gang zag tshig gi gsung gis bstan pas /
NK101(de)002:2082: pha'i rtogs pa de thog bab tu byin rlabs kyis thob nas dgongs pa dbyer med du gyur pa'o //
NK101(de)002:2083: 'o na thob rgyu ji lta ba yin zhe na /
NK101(de)002:2084: de ni snying po de bas na /
NK101(de)002:2085: zhes pa gzhi rang gi sems nyid yin pa'i rigs pa bstan te /
NK101(de)002:2086: rtogs pa bya ba'i don de gzhan na med par
NK101(de)002:2087: sems can rang rang la ye nas gnas pa'i snying
NK101(de)002:2088: po / byang chub kyi sems phyogs med de ni mar gyi yang zhun nam /
NK101(de)002:2089: chang gi nying khu lta bur chos thams cad kyi rang bzhin nam /
NK101(de)002:2090: theg pa thams cad kyi yang rtse'am /
NK101(de)002:2091: lam dang 'bras bu'am 'khor 'das thams cad kyi snying po yin pa de bas na'o //
NK101(de)002:2092: de las de 'byung ngo mtshar che //
NK101(de)002:2093: zhes pa chos nyid rang la 'char ba'i rigs pa bstan te /
NK101(de)002:2095: myang 'das mi sgrub par sems can ye nas sangs
NK101(de)002:2096: rgyas pa'i dgongs pa phyogs med du 'byung ba de
NK101(de)002:2098: yang chos nyid byang chub kyi sems dmigs pa'i mtha' thams cad dang bral ba de la /
NK101(de)002:2099: gzugs sku gnyis po ma btsal bar 'byung bas ngo mtshar che 'am /
NK101(de)002:2100: yang na gdam ngag bstan ma thag de ka rang la /
NK101(de)002:2101: rtogs grol thar pa dus gcig pa de 'byung ba ngo mtshar shin tu che'o //
NK101(de)002:2102: sngon gyi de dang da lta de /
NK101(de)002:2103: zhes pa dus gsum gyi sangs rgyas de las 'byung ba'i rigs pa bstan te /
NK101(de)002:2104: sngon gyi rgyal ba mar me mdzad 'das pa'i chos
NK101(de)002:2105: nyid skye med kyi klong du grol nas sangs rgyas
NK101(de)002:2106: pa dang / da ltar gyi rgyal ba sh+aa kya
NK101(de)002:2107: thub pa lhun gyis grub pa'i ngang la gnas te
NK101(de)002:2108: sangs rgyas pa dang de bzhin de yi gnas su
NK101(de)002:2109: pa dang / che / zhes pa ma 'ongs pa
NK101(de)002:2110: rgyal ba byams pa'i gnas sam rten du'ang chos nyid
NK101(de)002:2112: phyogs ris dang nges pa med pa'i klong 'di che bas na /
NK101(de)002:2113: skye 'gag med pa'i don 'di rtogs pa mngon du gyur te sangs rgyas pa yin nges so //
NK101(de)002:2114: de ltar de yi lam 'dra ba //
NK101(de)002:2116: de gcig pur ma zad dus gsum gyi sangs rgyas
NK101(de)002:2117: thams cad kyi gshegs shul gyi lam chen yin pas
NK101(de)002:2119: de ni de yi rang bzhin no //
NK101(de)002:2120: zhes pa chos nyid byang chub kyi sems de ni khams gsum sems can yongs kyi'ang /
NK101(de)002:2121: mi bskyod klung lam chen po'am /
NK101(de)002:2122: sems can thams cad kyi sems kyi rang bzhin chos nyid ma bcos pa'i don yin no //
NK101(de)002:2125: de dang 'dra ba yongs kyi lam //
NK101(de)002:2126: zhes pa thig le byang chub kyi sems bya bral
NK101(de)002:2127: gyi klong chen po de nyid dus gsum gyi sangs
NK101(de)002:2128: rgyas kyi lam mam gshegs shul yin pa de dang
NK101(de)002:2129: 'dra ba / khams gsum gyi sems can yongs kyis kyang 'gro sa dang grol sa yin pas /
NK101(de)002:2130: bgrod sa med pa'i lam thun mong ma yin pa de yin pa ni nges pa'o //
NK101(de)002:2131: 'o na chos nyid rang snang de thams cad la
NK101(de)002:2132: spyi khyab tu yod pa'i dpe ji lta bu zhe
NK101(de)002:2133: na / zla ba las byung rten dang bcas //
NK101(de)002:2134: zhes pa mtshon byed dpe'i gtan tshigs te /
NK101(de)002:2135: snang gzhi chu'i dkyil 'khor yod tshad tsam du /
NK101(de)002:2136: de nang snang bya zla ba'i dkyil 'khor mi 'gag par gzugs brnyan 'char te /
NK101(de)002:2137: nam mkha' la zla ba gcig shar ba chu'i ldeng ka zlum po'i nang du zla ba zlum po /
NK101(de)002:2138: ldeng ka zur gsum dang gru bzhi la sogs pa
NK101(de)002:2139: chung ngu'i nang du dbyibs rkyen ji ltar yod yod
NK101(de)002:2140: du zla ba'i gzugs brnyan kyang de 'dra re re
NK101(de)002:2141: 'char te / rten chu dang bcas pa'i phyir ro //
NK101(de)002:2142: de la mi mkhas pa'i byis pas /
NK101(de)002:2143: nga'i zla ba zlum po 'di yin la khyod kyi zla ba gru bzhi 'adi'o //
NK101(de)002:2144: zhes sogs su 'dzin pa ni mnyam pa nyid la phyogs su bzung bas skyon te /
NK101(de)002:2145: zla ba ji lta bar gtan la mi phebs so //
NK101(de)002:2146: des na zla ba gzugs brnyan tsam du 'dra ba la phyogs su bzung bas nor ba'o //
NK101(de)002:2147: kun gyi mnyam nyid yin pa la //
NK101(de)002:2148: phyogs su bltas pas 'grub pa med //
NK101(de)002:2149: ces pa mnyam nyid don gyi gtan tshigs yin te /
NK101(de)002:2151: 'khor 'das theg pas bsdus pa'i chos thams cad /
NK101(de)002:2152: chos nyid bya bral gyi klong chen por der /
NK101(de)002:2153: bzang ngan dang dbri bkol med par khyab ste /
NK101(de)002:2155: ngo bo nges med ye shes /
NK101(de)002:2157: bdag nyid thog mtha' med pa'i thig le nyag gcig la /
NK101(de)002:2158: gnas lugs phyogs med cir yang gnas /
NK101(de)002:2161: yin lugs kun kyang rang gsal yin pas /
NK101(de)002:2162: dpe nam mkha' dang chu zla /
NK101(de)002:2165: ji ltar byas kyang mnyam nyid chen po'i don la rang snang thad kar bden pas na /
NK101(de)002:2167: nga tsug yin kho tsug min zer nas phyogs su bltas pas 'ching ste /
NK101(de)002:2168: nyan thos pas chos nyid gang zag gi bdag med la byed pa nas /
NK101(de)002:2169: a nu dbyings dang ye shes la byed pa'i bar ro //
NK101(de)002:2170: de ltar chos nyid mnyam pa nyid grub pa'i dus med do //
NK101(de)002:2172: zla ba las byung rten dang bcas //
NK101(de)002:2173: zhes sogs zla ba dang ma bu'i lta lugs sbyor te /
NK101(de)002:2174: dper na bu chung ngu ba la /
NK101(de)002:2176: ya gi na a bo zla ba byas pas /
NK101(de)002:2177: bu chung gis ci la zer cha med pas ngu 'phro mi chod do //
NK101(de)002:2179: bu ngu ba'i mig gi thad kar mdzum mo bstan nas /
NK101(de)002:2181: bu chung gi mig mdzum mo la 'chags pa na /
NK101(de)002:2182: rten des brid nas mdzub mo je mtho je mtho la btang nas /
NK101(de)002:2183: a bo zla ba ya gi red byas pas bu
NK101(de)002:2184: chung gi mig la ltad mo langs nas ngu 'phro
NK101(de)002:2185: chod do // dpe de dang 'dra bar /
NK101(de)002:2186: theg pa 'og ma'i slob dpon mi mkhas pas /
NK101(de)002:2187: sangs rgyas logs nas thob pa skad byas te spyi yi tshul du bshad pas /
NK101(de)002:2188: chos nyid la go ba'am rtogs pa'i dus med par /
NK101(de)002:2189: 'khor ba'i sdug bsngal dang lam la phyogs ris su 'dzin pa las ma thar ro //
NK101(de)002:2190: a ti yo ga'i slob dpon mkhas pa gdams ngag dang ldan pa des /
NK101(de)002:2191: snod dang ldan pa'i bu mchog la /
NK101(de)002:2192: brda dang tshig gzhan la brten par byas nas /
NK101(de)002:2193: don rang la mdzub tshugs su bstan pas /
NK101(de)002:2194: tshig don dbye ba med par chos nyid cer mthong
NK101(de)002:2195: gi tshul du rig pa tsir gyis zin nas ngo
NK101(de)002:2197: de rnams kyi rgyas gdab 'agre'o////da ni skabs bcu gnyis pa la'ang /
NK101(de)002:2199: 'khor 'das dbyer med kyi dgongs pa ga bur gyi
NK101(de)002:2200: nus pa lta bur dbyer med chen po'i klong du
NK101(de)002:2201: bstan pa / snga phyi med pa'i rigs pa bstan pa /
NK101(de)002:2202: dus gsum skyon gyis ma gos pa'i gtan tshigs bstan pa dang bzhi las /
NK101(de)002:2204: chags pa dang bral ba'i skabs /
NK101(de)002:2206: lta sgom spyod 'bras dang gnas skabs kyi bde ba
NK101(de)002:2207: zhi gnas sam mi rtog pa phra mo'i ro la
NK101(de)002:2208: chags pa de / a ti yo ga bya ba dang bral ba'i gtan tshigs kyis /
NK101(de)002:2209: de la mi gnas par gang la chags pa kun dang bral bar ston pa'i skabs la bab bo //
NK101(de)002:2211: chos kun rang gi sems la 'dus //
NK101(de)002:2212: sems la gzung 'dzin med pa'i phyir //
NK101(de)002:2213: chags dang bral ba'i skabs zhes bya //
NK101(de)002:2216: da lta'i bde dang phyi ma'i bde //
NK101(de)002:2218: chos nyid bya bral gyi klong chen po de nyid /
NK101(de)002:2219: las dang bag chags ltar snang ba la 'khor bar 'khrul yang /
NK101(de)002:2220: 'khor ba ma spangs rang sar grol bas mya ngan las 'das pa ste /
NK101(de)002:2221: de gnyis ka rgyu chos nyid /
NK101(de)002:2223: 'bras bu rang byung ye shes su gcig cing ngo bo dbyer med pa la /
NK101(de)002:2224: gang yang gnyis su med pa'i dgongs pa chos nyid kyi klong ngo //
NK101(de)002:2225: ga pur gyi nus pa lta bu ni /
NK101(de)002:2226: nad kyi rkyen gyis tsha ba can la sman du 'gro /
NK101(de)002:2227: grang ba can la dug tu 'gro bas /
NK101(de)002:2228: nus pa so sor byung yang /
NK101(de)002:2229: ngo bo la dbyer med pa bzhin du /
NK101(de)002:2230: 'khor 'das thams cad byang chub sems la shar ba yin kyang /
NK101(de)002:2231: thig le nyag gcig gi klong la /
NK101(de)002:2233: grol kyang tha dad med pa rang grol bas dbye ba med pa'i klong ngo //
NK101(de)002:2234: de la rgyun chad bral bas snga phyi med pa'i rigs pa /
NK101(de)002:2235: tha dad du 'dzin na gol bas /
NK101(de)002:2236: dus gsum skyon gyis ma gos pa gtan tshigs byung ngo //
NK101(de)002:2238: da lta'i bde dang phyi ma'i bde //
NK101(de)002:2239: zhes pa bde ba chen po kha sprod kyi gtan tshigs te /
NK101(de)002:2240: da lta lus 'khor ba'i sdug bsngal gyis gzir yang /
NK101(de)002:2241: sems bde ba chen po'i don dang ma bral bas /
NK101(de)002:2243: phyi mar lus mya ngan las 'das kyang /
NK101(de)002:2244: sems bde ba chen po'i don dang ma bral bas /
NK101(de)002:2246: ji ltar byas kyang bde ba kha sbyor ram /
NK101(de)002:2247: yang na 'khor bar lhung sa med pas /
NK101(de)002:2248: dogs pa dang bral ba da lta'i bde ba /
NK101(de)002:2250: myang 'das kyi rten dang bral bas phyi ma'i bde ba /
NK101(de)002:2251: de lta bu'i don legs par go zhing rtogs na
NK101(de)002:2252: ji ltar byas kyang chos nyid rgyun chad med pa'i
NK101(de)002:2253: ngang la bde chen du 'byams pa'o //
NK101(de)002:2256: mngon sum pa dang rgyab nas 'byung //
NK101(de)002:2258: dper na lus gcig gi cha la /
NK101(de)002:2259: mdun rgyab gnyis su btags pas /
NK101(de)002:2260: mdun phyogs mngon du mthong yang /
NK101(de)002:2261: rgyab dang dus mnyam pa bzhin du /
NK101(de)002:2262: sems nyid gcig gi cha la rol ba 'khor 'das gnyis ltar shar bas /
NK101(de)002:2263: sems can mngon sum du mthong ba dang /
NK101(de)002:2264: sangs rgyas bag nyal gyi tshul du rgyab nas 'byung
NK101(de)002:2265: ba gnyis dus mnyam pas 'khor 'das dbyer med pa'am
NK101(de)002:2266: / yang na da ltar gyi mngon sum la snang ba nyid chos skur shar bas /
NK101(de)002:2267: rgyab nas 'byung ba'i yon tan gzugs sku gnyis shugs
NK101(de)002:2268: la 'byung ba ste sku gsum dbyer med du shes
NK101(de)002:2270: de yang rnam pa'i skyon yin pas //
NK101(de)002:2271: zhes 'khor 'das dbyer med la snga phyi tha dad nam /
NK101(de)002:2272: chos nyid nges med la sgra ji bzhin par 'dzin pa dang /
NK101(de)002:2273: dus gsum mnyam pa nyid la rim par spyod pa ni /
NK101(de)002:2274: rnam dpyod dus su bgrangs pa'i skyon yin te /
NK101(de)002:2275: 'khor ba'i thog mtha' can du song ba'i skyon yod /
NK101(de)002:2276: thog mtha' can du song na /
NK101(de)002:2277: 'khrul pa zlog thabs med pa'i skyon dang /
NK101(de)002:2279: sangs rgyas thog ma tha ma med //
NK101(de)002:2282: dus gsum gcig ste khyad par med //
NK101(de)002:2283: ces pa'i tshig dang 'gal ba'i skyon yod pas na /
NK101(de)002:2284: de la brten par mi bya'o //
NK101(de)002:2285: zhes dus la mi ltos pa'i gtan tshigs bstan te /
NK101(de)002:2286: a ti yo ga rdzogs pa chen po'i lugs kyis /
NK101(de)002:2287: dus rim gyis pa la brten par mi bya ste /
NK101(de)002:2288: shes bya chig chod du dus gsum thig le nyag gcig tu go ba gdams ngag yin no //
NK101(de)002:2289: de rnams kyi rgyas gdab 'dra////da ni skabs bcu gsum pa'ang /
NK101(de)002:2291: chos nyid 'byung 'jug med pa'i dgongs pa rin po
NK101(de)002:2292: che gser gling lta bur tha mi dad pa'i klong
NK101(de)002:2293: du bstan pa / tha snyad la mi gnas pa'i rigs pa bstan pa /
NK101(de)002:2294: thig le nyag gcig gi gtan tshigs bstan pa dang bzhi las /
NK101(de)002:2296: gdod ma nas che ba snying po nyid kyi skabs /
NK101(de)002:2297: zhes gdod ma nas dus la snga phyi med pa'i gtan tshigs yin te /
NK101(de)002:2298: ye gdod ma ka phyi mo nyid nas /
NK101(de)002:2299: che ba ni sems nyid thig le nyag gcig yin te /
NK101(de)002:2301: gsum gyis che ste sku gsung thugs kyi che dang /
NK101(de)002:2302: lnga yis che ste che ba lnga yis che ba ni bye brag gis che ba'o //
NK101(de)002:2303: thig le nyag gcig de 'gran gyi zla thams cad
NK101(de)002:2304: dang bral bas 'byung ba 'khor 'das theg pa thams
NK101(de)002:2305: cad las che ba ni spyi yis che ba'o //
NK101(de)002:2306: snying po ni byang chub kyi sems de /
NK101(de)002:2308: chang gi snying khu lta bur /
NK101(de)002:2309: chos thams cad kyi snying po sems can thams cad
NK101(de)002:2310: la spyi khyab tu gnas par ston pa'i skabs la
NK101(de)002:2312: chos kun byang chub sems la 'dus //
NK101(de)002:2313: sems nyid ye nas che ba'i phyir //
NK101(de)002:2314: gdod nas che ba'i skabs zhes bya //
NK101(de)002:2317: dus gsum gcig ste khyad par med //
NK101(de)002:2319: de yang 'khor 'das snang srid kyis bsdus pa'i chos thams cad /
NK101(de)002:2320: shar yang gzhi gnas ye grol bya bral klong chen gyi ngang las shar bas /
NK101(de)002:2321: thog mar yang gzhi shar yin te gzhan nas ma byung /
NK101(de)002:2322: tha mar yang dbyings grol yin pas gzhan du mi
NK101(de)002:2323: 'jug par chos nyid mnyam pa nyid 'byung 'jug med
NK101(de)002:2324: pa'i dgongs pa chos nyid kyi klong ngo //
NK101(de)002:2325: rin po che gser gling lta bu ni /
NK101(de)002:2326: rin po che gser gyi gling na gser 'ba' zhig las rdo'i tha snyad bral ba bzhin du /
NK101(de)002:2327: thams cad chos nyid thog mtha' dang bral ba'i rang bzhin la /
NK101(de)002:2328: snga phyi'i tha snyad dang bral te /
NK101(de)002:2329: 'das pa chos nyid skye ba med pa'i klong du snga phyi thog mtha' med par grol ba dang /
NK101(de)002:2330: ma 'ongs pa ma nges pa'i klong na snga phyi thog mtha' med par shar ba la /
NK101(de)002:2331: da lta lhun gyis grub pa'i klong na snga phyi thog mtha' med par gnas pas /
NK101(de)002:2332: dus tha dad du dbye ba'i phyogs kyi tha snyad
NK101(de)002:2333: thams cad dang bral bas chos nyid kyi klong ngo
NK101(de)002:2334: // de la dus gsum tha dad med pas tha snyad dang bral ba'i rigs pa /
NK101(de)002:2335: mnyam pa nyid las ma g.yos pas thig le nyag gcig gi gtan tshigs zer ro //
NK101(de)002:2337: dus gsum gcig ste khyad par med //
NK101(de)002:2338: ces pa snga phyi thog mtha' med pa'i dgongs pa bstan te /
NK101(de)002:2339: dus 'das pa chos nyid skye ba med pa'i klong du grol ba dang /
NK101(de)002:2340: ma 'ongs pa ma nges pa'i klong na 'char ba dang /
NK101(de)002:2341: da ltar lhun gyis grub pa'i ngang la gnas pa de /
NK101(de)002:2342: thig le nyag gcig la dus gsum tha dad med pa gcig pas /
NK101(de)002:2343: snga phyi'i khyad par med de /
NK101(de)002:2344: dus gsum mnyam pa nyid rgyun mi 'chad par grol ba'o //
NK101(de)002:2345: de'i la bzla dang skyon bsal 'dra /
NK101(de)002:2347: sngon med phyis med gdod nas 'byung //
NK101(de)002:2348: zhes pa chos nyid la rgyud chad med pa'i rigs pa bstan te /
NK101(de)002:2349: a ti yo ga chos nyid la snga phyi thog mtha' dang bral bas /
NK101(de)002:2350: phyi ma'i mtha' med pa'i gnad kyis sngon med la /
NK101(de)002:2351: sngon gyi mtha' med pa'i gnad kyis phyi ma'i phyi ma med /
NK101(de)002:2352: snga phyi gnyis ka med pa'i gnad kyis da lta ma grub /
NK101(de)002:2353: da lta ma grub pa'i gnad kyis snga phyi gnyis
NK101(de)002:2354: ka med de 'khor 'das kyi chos thams cad snga
NK101(de)002:2355: phyi thog mtha' med pas ye gdod ma nyid nas
NK101(de)002:2358: chos skus khyab par gcig pa'i phyir /
NK101(de)002:2359: zhes pas ya tha rgyal ba'i dkyil 'khor nas /
NK101(de)002:2360: ma tha dmyal ba'i 'jig rten yan chad la chos sku thig le nyag gcig des /
NK101(de)002:2361: bzang ngan dang che chung snga phyi dang thog mtha' bral te phyogs med par khyab pas /
NK101(de)002:2362: mnyam pa ris med yul dang yul can med pa'i khyab gdal la /
NK101(de)002:2363: 'khor 'das kyi chos thams cad rgyu chos nyid /
NK101(de)002:2365: 'bras bu rang byung ye shes su gcig pa'am /
NK101(de)002:2366: gzhi lhun grub ngo bo nges med /
NK101(de)002:2368: bdag nyid thog mtha' med par gcig pa'i phyir /
NK101(de)002:2369: che ba'i chen po rang bzhin gnas //
NK101(de)002:2370: zhes pa gang gis kyang mtshungs pa med pa'i gtan tshigs bstan te /
NK101(de)002:2371: 'khor ba las che ba ni mya ngan las 'das pa'i chos yin la /
NK101(de)002:2372: de'i yang chen po gyur pa ni /
NK101(de)002:2373: 'khor 'das gnyis ka las che ba'i rang gi rig pa byang chub kyi sems /
NK101(de)002:2374: skye med dang yul dang yul can gnyis med kyi
NK101(de)002:2375: ngo bo ye gdod ma nyid nas bya bral klong
NK101(de)002:2376: chen du sangs rgyas pa'i rang bzhin du gnas pa
NK101(de)002:2377: yin no // de rnams kyi rgyas gdab 'agre'o////da ni skabs bcu bzhi pa la'ang /
NK101(de)002:2379: longs sku thug phrad du 'char ba'i dgongs pa 'khor
NK101(de)002:2380: los sgyur ba'i rgyal po lta bur snang la ma
NK101(de)002:2381: nges pa'i klong du bstan pa /
NK101(de)002:2382: chos nyid mnyam pa nyid la dus mi dmigs pa'i rigs pa bstan pa /
NK101(de)002:2383: rig pa spyi khyab la bogs gdon don du med pa'i gtan tshigs bstan pa dang bzhi las /
NK101(de)002:2385: kun tu smon lam dang bral ba'i skabs /
NK101(de)002:2386: zhes pa a ti yo ga'i rnal 'byor pa ni /
NK101(de)002:2387: dus dang rnam pa kun tu 'phen pa'i smon lam mi gdab /
NK101(de)002:2388: 'bras bu gzhan nas mi sgrub ste /
NK101(de)002:2389: theg pa brgyad kyi lta sgom mam /
NK101(de)002:2390: lam rnams kyi re smon la mi ltos pas /
NK101(de)002:2391: smon lam gdab bya 'debs byed thams cad dang bral bar ston pa'i skabs la bab bo //
NK101(de)002:2393: chos kun byang chub sems la 'dus //
NK101(de)002:2394: sems la skyon yon med pa'i phyir //
NK101(de)002:2395: smon lam bral ba'i skabs zhes bya //
NK101(de)002:2398: srid pa gsum na sbyong ba yang //
NK101(de)002:2400: de yang sbyangs pa mngon gyur gyi longs spyod rdzogs pa'i sku bya ba /
NK101(de)002:2401: sngon gyi smon lam thugs rje'i dbang gis sbyangs pa dang /
NK101(de)002:2402: brtsal ba dang bsgyur ba'i nus mthu las /
NK101(de)002:2403: kun gzhi dang bag chags thams cad gnas gyur pa'i dbang gis /
NK101(de)002:2406: so sor rtog pa'i ye shes thugs su chud pas /
NK101(de)002:2407: mtshan dang dpe byad du shar ba la bya ste /
NK101(de)002:2408: longs sku yin yang thug phrad ma yin no //
NK101(de)002:2409: rdzogs pa chen po'i lugs kyis /
NK101(de)002:2410: rang gi sems nyid 'dus ma byas pas chos kyi
NK101(de)002:2411: sku las 'khor 'das thams cad rang shar zhing rang
NK101(de)002:2413: cir snang cir srid thams cad longs sku thug phrad
NK101(de)002:2414: du 'char ba'i dgongs pa chos nyid kyi klong ste
NK101(de)002:2415: / dper na 'khor los bsgyur ba'i rgyal po la /
NK101(de)002:2416: mtshan dang dpe byad bsod nams khyad par can ci
NK101(de)002:2417: tsam yod kyang gtan du mi sdod de brtags mi
NK101(de)002:2419: chos nyid cir yang snang tsam na /
NK101(de)002:2420: nges pa med par thams cad rang shar zhing de ru grol bas rang grol gyi klong ngo //
NK101(de)002:2421: des na thug phrad la dus rim gyis pa ma dmigs pas /
NK101(de)002:2422: dus dang bar med kyi rig pa mnyam nyid chen po la bogs ched du mi 'dod pas /
NK101(de)002:2423: rig pa spyi khyab la bogs 'don du med pa'i gtan tshigs byung ngo //
NK101(de)002:2425: srid pa gsum na sbyong ba yang //
NK101(de)002:2426: zhes pa srid pa rnam par dag pa'i dgongs pa /
NK101(de)002:2427: sgra ji bzhin pa ma yin pa'i srid pa gsum ni /
NK101(de)002:2428: lhun grub la ye srid pa'i srid pa /
NK101(de)002:2429: skye med la mi srid pa'i srid pa /
NK101(de)002:2430: nges med la ji srid pa'i srid pa gsum ste gnas lugs ma bcos pa'i srid pa yin la /
NK101(de)002:2431: sgra ji bzhin pa'i srid pa gsum ni /
NK101(de)002:2432: rgyu mthun gnas skabs kyi srid pa /
NK101(de)002:2433: sa bla sa 'og sa steng rnam pa gsum gyi sems can ni /
NK101(de)002:2434: bag chags rang rgyud par snang la /
NK101(de)002:2435: de dag sbyang bar bya ba'i phyir gdul bya dag pa'i shes ngo dang /
NK101(de)002:2436: ma dag pa'i shes ngo la /
NK101(de)002:2437: longs sku dang sprul sku'i gzugs brnyan dpag tu med par shar ba de yang /
NK101(de)002:2438: ming tsam sgyu mar snang ba ste //
NK101(de)002:2439: zhes snang la ma nges pa'i dgongs pa bstan te /
NK101(de)002:2440: de yang rang rgyud du grub pa med pas /
NK101(de)002:2441: re zhig snang ba ltar btags par zad kyis /
NK101(de)002:2442: byang chub sems kyi cho 'phrul cir yang snang tsam na /
NK101(de)002:2443: de'i rang bzhin la nges pa med cing phyogs ris med pas sgyu ma lta bu ste /
NK101(de)002:2444: med pa'i don la cir yang snang bas so //
NK101(de)002:2445: 'khor los sgyur ba'i gnas chen yang //
NK101(de)002:2446: zhes pa dpe don gnyis su med pa'i dgongs pa bstan te /
NK101(de)002:2447: dper na 'khor lo sgyur ba'i rgyal po ni 'jig
NK101(de)002:2448: rten na dbang che zhing phun sum tshogs pa yin
NK101(de)002:2449: kyang / gtan du mi sdod de /
NK101(de)002:2450: re zhig gi bsti gnas tsam mam /
NK101(de)002:2451: skad cig gi bde ba tsam yin pa ltar /
NK101(de)002:2452: sgyu mar sbyong ba'i bsti gnas yin //
NK101(de)002:2454: des na gzugs skur snang ba yang ma nges pa sgyu ma lta bus /
NK101(de)002:2455: sems can gyi bag chags sgyu ma lta bu de rang bzhin med par sbyong bas na /
NK101(de)002:2456: sgyu mas sgyu sbyong ba'i bsti gnas tsam yin pa las /
NK101(de)002:2458: nyon mongs dang ye shes sam /
NK101(de)002:2459: sbyong bya sbyong byed gnyis ka ma grub pas so //
NK101(de)002:2462: rnam dpyod dus la ltos pa rnams zhes rnam par dka' ba'i chos spyod la brtan nas /
NK101(de)002:2463: dus rim gyis pa la sangs rgyas thob tu re nas /
NK101(de)002:2464: rgyu 'di la brtsal bas 'bras bu phyi ma la
NK101(de)002:2465: thob par 'dod pa'i dus la sa mtshams gcod pa
NK101(de)002:2466: yi theg pa 'og ma pa rnams la /
NK101(de)002:2468: zhes pa chos nyid la mtha' med pa'i rigs pa bstan te /
NK101(de)002:2469: nyan rang bskal pa 'bum phrag bdun na sangs rgyas par 'dod pa dang /
NK101(de)002:2470: dbu sems grangs med gsum na sangs rgyas par 'dod
NK101(de)002:2471: de sa bcu mthar phyin rdo rje lta bu'i ting
NK101(de)002:2472: nge 'dzin gyis sgro btags thams cad rgyun bcad te
NK101(de)002:2473: / bcu gcig kun du 'od kyi sa la sku
NK101(de)002:2474: gsum ye shes bzhi'i 'bras bu thob par 'dod pa'o
NK101(de)002:2475: / // 'o na de kho na ltar 'byung nges sam zhe na /
NK101(de)002:2476: 'byung bar ma nges pas dus der 'byung bar mi 'gyur te /
NK101(de)002:2478: ma bral smon pa spyod pas na //
NK101(de)002:2479: zhes pa cis kyang mi rnyed pa'i rig pa bstan te /
NK101(de)002:2480: theg pa 'og ma pa de rnams lam la rtsol sgrub dang ma bral /
NK101(de)002:2481: 'bras bu re smon la ltos pas /
NK101(de)002:2482: yul dang phyogs med la phyogs 'dzin du spyod pa'i phyir 'byung ba med do //
NK101(de)002:2484: stong pa'i mtshan nyid gsungs pa bzhin /
NK101(de)002:2485: zhes pa stong pa'i mtshan nyid la phyi stong nang stong la sogs pa'i bgo bsha' byas kyang /
NK101(de)002:2486: dngos po ma rnyed pa bzhin du /
NK101(de)002:2487: skye med kyi rig pa yul med spyi khyab tu shar bas /
NK101(de)002:2488: phyi nang ngam yul dang yul can nam /
NK101(de)002:2489: dus snga phyi'i khyad par gang yang mi dmigs pa sogs so //
NK101(de)002:2490: de bzhi'i rgyas gdab 'agre'o////da ni skabs bco lnga pa la'ang /
NK101(de)002:2492: thig le nyag gcig gi dgongs pa nam mkha'i bya
NK101(de)002:2493: lam lta bur rjes med chen po'i klong du bstan
NK101(de)002:2494: pa / sgro skur dang bral ba'i rigs pa bstan pa /
NK101(de)002:2495: phyi nang med cing bya rtsol dang bral ba'i gtan tshigs bstan pa /
NK101(de)002:2496: thig le'i nges tshig bstan pa dang lnga las /
NK101(de)002:2499: zhes pa dgongs pa 'dus pa las /
NK101(de)002:2500: thig le gcig gis kun la khyab //
NK101(de)002:2501: thams cad lung chen yin par bstan //
NK101(de)002:2503: lung ni rna bar brgyud pa'i lung //
NK101(de)002:2504: mngon du phyung ba'i mdo lung /
NK101(de)002:2505: gtan la 'bebs pa'i nges lung dang gsum ka /
NK101(de)002:2506: thig le nyag gcig bya bral klong chen gyi lung du 'dus pas /
NK101(de)002:2507: rdo rje sems dpa' nam mkha' che dbu zhabs kun
NK101(de)002:2508: la khyab pa'i lung nyid nges par ston pa'i skabs
NK101(de)002:2509: la bab bo // zhes pa ste /
NK101(de)002:2510: chos kun byang chub sems su 'dus //
NK101(de)002:2511: sems la thams cad rdzogs pa'i phyir //
NK101(de)002:2512: lung chen ston pa'i skabs zhes bya //
NK101(de)002:2515: gcig ste rnam par yongs kyis med //
NK101(de)002:2517: de yang gnas lugs thig le nyag gcig cir yang gnas /
NK101(de)002:2518: shar lugs thig le nyag gcig cir yang shar bas /
NK101(de)002:2519: yin lugs thig le nyag gcig ci yang yin pa /
NK101(de)002:2520: grol lugs thig le nyag gcig cir yang grol ba yin te /
NK101(de)002:2521: gnas lugs rang shar yin lugs rang grol la tha dad med de /
NK101(de)002:2522: mnyam nyid chen po gcig gi rang bzhin /
NK101(de)002:2523: grwa dang zur med pas thig le /
NK101(de)002:2524: ma spros kun la khyab pas nyag gcig gi dgongs pa chos nyid klong ngo //
NK101(de)002:2525: nam mkha'i bya lam lta bur ni /
NK101(de)002:2526: bya gar 'phur yang mi 'gal la rjes mi 'ong ba bzhin du /
NK101(de)002:2527: rdzogs pa chen po'i rnal 'byor pa //
NK101(de)002:2528: byed spyod gang yang ma bkag kyang //
NK101(de)002:2529: rjes med rang shar rang grol gyi klong ngo //
NK101(de)002:2530: de la mtha' gang gis kyang ma reg pas sgro skur dang bral ba'i rig pa /
NK101(de)002:2531: mtshan ma thams cad rang sar grol bas bya brtsal dang bral ba'i gtan tshigs 'byung ngo //
NK101(de)002:2533: gcig ste rnam pa yongs kyis med //
NK101(de)002:2534: ces pa snang srid 'khor 'das yod med rtag chad
NK101(de)002:2535: phyi nang snod bcud kyis bsdus pa'i chos thams cad
NK101(de)002:2537: de yang gang du gcig na rang rig skye med kyi ngang du gcig go //
NK101(de)002:2538: ji ltar gcig na dpe don rtags dang gtan tshigs bzhi ru gcig ste /
NK101(de)002:2539: dpe'i dus na nam mkhar gcig /
NK101(de)002:2540: don gyi dus na chos nyid du gcig /
NK101(de)002:2541: rtags kyi dus na rig pa byang chub kyi sems su gcig /
NK101(de)002:2542: des na rgyu rkyen 'bras bu gsum yang /
NK101(de)002:2545: 'bras bu rang byung gi ye shes su gcig go //
NK101(de)002:2547: gzhi lhun gyis grub pa gcig /
NK101(de)002:2548: ngo bo nges pa med par gcig /
NK101(de)002:2549: don skye ba med par gcig /
NK101(de)002:2550: bdag nyid thog mtha' dang bral bar gcig pas /
NK101(de)002:2551: 'khor 'das snod bcud kyis bsdus pa'i chos thams cad la /
NK101(de)002:2552: bzang ngan nam che chung gi rnam pa ngang ngam yongs kyis med par yid ches so //
NK101(de)002:2553: 'o na dpe ji lta bu zhe na /
NK101(de)002:2554: rnal 'byor nam mkha'i bya lam gnas //
NK101(de)002:2556: de lta bu'i dgongs pa la phyogs med pa'i gnad kyis spyod pa 'gag med du phul nas /
NK101(de)002:2557: shugs la dge ba'i las dang /
NK101(de)002:2560: lung ma bstan pa'i las dang /
NK101(de)002:2561: bya ba ci byed pa thams cad la bag chags dkar nag bsogs pa'i rjes med pas /
NK101(de)002:2562: nam mkha'i bya lam dang 'dra ba yin te /
NK101(de)002:2563: de cis na kun gzhi zang thal la /
NK101(de)002:2565: rnal 'byor thang yan la dgongs pa phyogs med yin pas /
NK101(de)002:2567: spyod yul 'di la gnas pa gang //
NK101(de)002:2568: phyogs med don la gnas pa yin //
NK101(de)002:2570: bya lam rjes med bya ba yang don de lta bu zhig rtogs na yin gyi /
NK101(de)002:2571: kha 'ud tsam gyi lta ba la brten pas ci yang phan pa med do //
NK101(de)002:2572: de'i skyon bsal dang la bzla 'dra /
NK101(de)002:2574: ma byung ma skyes snying po la //
NK101(de)002:2575: zhes pa gzhi chos nyid kyi rigs pa /
NK101(de)002:2576: dbyings skye 'gag med pa'i thig le chen po chos kyi sku /
NK101(de)002:2577: sems can rang rang gi rig pa byang chub kyi sems phyogs med de nyid /
NK101(de)002:2578: pha yi rgyu las ma byung /
NK101(de)002:2579: ma yi rkyen las ma skyes /
NK101(de)002:2580: 'dus byas ma yin pas gnyen pos mi 'jig /
NK101(de)002:2581: ye gdod ma nyid nas 'khor 'das kyi chos thams
NK101(de)002:2582: cad rdo rje snying por rang 'khrungs pa'i sangs rgyas
NK101(de)002:2583: yin pas / snying po byang chub kyi sems /
NK101(de)002:2585: sems kyi sems nyid yin pa la //
NK101(de)002:2586: sgro btags chos kun ga la yod //
NK101(de)002:2587: ces pa sgro skur dang bral ba dngos kyi rigs pa /
NK101(de)002:2588: chos nyid bya bral mtha' gang gis kyang ma reg /
NK101(de)002:2589: mtha' gang yang ma spangs pa de /
NK101(de)002:2591: med ces skur pa gdab pa'am /
NK101(de)002:2593: stong zhes skur pa gdab pa'am /
NK101(de)002:2595: chad ces skur pa gdab pa'am /
NK101(de)002:2596: de la sogs pa gang yang med pas /
NK101(de)002:2597: sgro skur dang bral ba'i chos nyid yin no //
NK101(de)002:2599: phyi nang gnyis ka phyi nyid nang //
NK101(de)002:2600: zhes pa chos nyid byang chub kyi sems bya bral klong chen de nyid /
NK101(de)002:2601: ye gdod ma nyid nas dbyer med kyi zang thal /
NK101(de)002:2602: bya bral gyi klong chen du shar ba la /
NK101(de)002:2604: rig pa la phyi nang med de /
NK101(de)002:2609: nang gang yin phyi yin te /
NK101(de)002:2610: des na theg pa 'og ma pa rig pa phyi
NK101(de)002:2611: nang dgag sgrub can du brtags pa de gnyis ka
NK101(de)002:2612: a ti yo gas ma spangs rang grol du gtan
NK101(de)002:2613: la dbab pas / phyi nyid nang ngo //
NK101(de)002:2614: zab mo cha shas rtog yul med //
NK101(de)002:2615: ces pa rig pa yul med kyi gtan tshigs te /
NK101(de)002:2616: zab mo ni chos nyid thig le nyag gcig /
NK101(de)002:2617: zab cing gting ring la cha phra bas brtag par dka' ba'o //
NK101(de)002:2618: 'o na sus mi rtogs she na /
NK101(de)002:2619: cha shas kyi rtog pa'i yul du med ces bya'o //
NK101(de)002:2620: cha shas pa gang zhig yin na /
NK101(de)002:2621: a nu man chad yin la /
NK101(de)002:2622: de'ang a nu dbyings dang ye shes sam /
NK101(de)002:2623: ma h+aa thabs dang shes rab sogs par gnyis su 'dzin pa'i cha shas sam /
NK101(de)002:2624: de'i yang 'og ma pas mtho dman gyi cha shas sam /
NK101(de)002:2625: bzang ngan gyi khyad pas 'dod pas mnyam pa nyid la rtogs pa'i dus med do //
NK101(de)002:2626: srid pa ming tsam log pa'i stobs //
NK101(de)002:2627: zhes pa chos nyid rang log gi gtan tshigs yin te /
NK101(de)002:2628: srid pa ye srid kyi srid pa lhun grub /
NK101(de)002:2629: mi srid pa'i srid pa skye med /
NK101(de)002:2630: ji srid pa'i srid pa nges med /
NK101(de)002:2631: rgyu mthun gnas skabs kyi srid pa /
NK101(de)002:2634: bar mi'i srid pa gsum mam /
NK101(de)002:2635: sa 'og sa steng sa bla'i srid pa gsum ste /
NK101(de)002:2636: de gsum rang yang ming du btags pa tsam las /
NK101(de)002:2637: don chos nyid la gang yang ma grub ste /
NK101(de)002:2638: rgyu mtshan go zlog gi 'bras bur re dogs bcad pas /
NK101(de)002:2639: srid pa gsum po chos nyid mnyam pa nyid du rang log pa'i stobs kyis /
NK101(de)002:2640: 'khor ba ma spangs par rang sar grol lo //
NK101(de)002:2641: de la yon tan ji yod ce na /
NK101(de)002:2642: de bas ting 'dzin mnyam dang bral /
NK101(de)002:2643: zhes pa ting nge 'dzin 'byung 'jug dang bral ba'i gtan tshigs bstan te /
NK101(de)002:2644: de bas na srid pa gsum gyi bag chags sbyang bar bya ba'i phyir /
NK101(de)002:2646: ting nge 'dzin mnyam pa la bzhag dgos pa de /
NK101(de)002:2647: a ti yo ga ting nge 'dzin mnyam pa la
NK101(de)002:2648: bzhag sa med par thams cad chos nyid du shes
NK101(de)002:2649: pas / bsgom du yod pa dang med pa'i tha snyad kun dang bral te /
NK101(de)002:2650: mnyam pa la bzhag tu med do //
NK101(de)002:2651: de la tha tshig phyi dang nang /
NK101(de)002:2652: zhes pa dam tshig grangs srung dang bral ba'i gtan tshigs bstan te /
NK101(de)002:2653: mnyam par bzhag pa dang mi bzhag pa'i rtsol ba dang bral ba de la /
NK101(de)002:2654: gsang sngags phyi nang gi dam tshig /
NK101(de)002:2655: rtog tshogs phung po lha'i nga rgyal du bsgom pa dang bral bas /
NK101(de)002:2656: rang bzhin phung po khams bzhin gnas //
NK101(de)002:2657: zhes pa rdzogs pa chen po'i lugs kyis bsgoms ma bsgoms med par ye gdod ma nyid nas /
NK101(de)002:2658: phung khams skye mched thams cad kun rdzob tu lha
NK101(de)002:2659: dang lha mo'i dkyil 'khor du lhun gyis grub nas
NK101(de)002:2660: gnas pa dang / don dam par chos nyid byang chub kyi sems /
NK101(de)002:2661: ma skyes lhun gyis grub pa'i dkyil 'khor gyi 'khor lo gnas pas /
NK101(de)002:2664: zhes pa yi klung chen po'i ting nge 'dzin bstan te /
NK101(de)002:2665: 'das ma 'ongs da ltar gyi dus rnam pa gsum mam /
NK101(de)002:2666: 'gro nyal 'dug sdod gang gi dus su yang rig pa dang 'bral ma myong bas /
NK101(de)002:2667: chos nyid dang bral ma myong /
NK101(de)002:2668: chos nyid dang bral ma myong bas /
NK101(de)002:2669: dam tshig dang bral ma myong ste /
NK101(de)002:2670: dus 'das pa chos nyid skye ba med pa'i klong du grol ba dang /
NK101(de)002:2671: ma 'ongs pa ma nges pa'i klong nas nges med du 'char ba dang /
NK101(de)002:2672: da lta ba lhun gyis grub pa'i klong du mnyam nyid chen por grol bas /
NK101(de)002:2673: dus gsum chos nyid las mi 'da' bas //
NK101(de)002:2674: tha tshig ming du btags pa med //
NK101(de)002:2675: ces 'da' nyams dang bral ba la phyi nang gi dam tshig so sor phye la /
NK101(de)002:2676: ming du btags te srung du ye nas med do //
NK101(de)002:2678: ye shes chen po'i thig le /
NK101(de)002:2679: zhes shar la nub pa med pas ye shes /
NK101(de)002:2680: phyi nang med par 'od gsal bas na yang ye shes /
NK101(de)002:2681: 'khor 'das theg pa thams cad las khyad par du 'phags pas na chen po /
NK101(de)002:2682: ma spros kun la khyab cing /
NK101(de)002:2683: gdal ba chen por gnas pas na thig le zhes bya'o //
NK101(de)002:2684: de'ang dang po mi rtog pa'i ye shes chen po dang /
NK101(de)002:2685: gnyis pa mnyam nyid ye shes chen po dang /
NK101(de)002:2686: gsum pa snga phyi med pa'i ye shes chen po dang /
NK101(de)002:2687: bzhi pa thog mtha' med pa'i ye shes chen po dang /
NK101(de)002:2688: lnga pa ma nges pa'i ye shes chen po dang /
NK101(de)002:2689: drug pa mi g.yo ba'i ye shes chen por 'dus so //
NK101(de)002:2690: de rnams kyi rgyas gdab 'agre'o////da ni skabs bcu drug pa la'ang /
NK101(de)002:2692: sku gsung thugs thug phrad du 'char ba'i dgongs pa
NK101(de)002:2693: ral gri kha mang lta bur rang shar chen po'i
NK101(de)002:2695: bdag nyid rang shar gyi rigs pa bstan pa /
NK101(de)002:2696: chos nyid mnyam pa nyid kyi gtan tshigs bstan pa dang bzhi las /
NK101(de)002:2699: zhes pa a ti yo ga thig le nyag gcig
NK101(de)002:2700: bya rtsol dang bral ba'i klong du snang srid 'khor
NK101(de)002:2701: 'das yod med rtag chad phyi nang snod bcud kyis
NK101(de)002:2702: bsdus pa'i chos thams cad bzang ngan med pa mnyam
NK101(de)002:2707: mtha' dbus med par mnyam ste /
NK101(de)002:2708: mnyam pa nyid la tha dad med par ston pa'i skabs la bab bo //
NK101(de)002:2710: chos kun byang chub sems su 'dus //
NK101(de)002:2711: sems la bzang ngan med pa'i phyir //
NK101(de)002:2712: mnyam pa nyid kyi skabs zhes bya //
NK101(de)002:2715: mi g.yo ba ni sku yi rgya //
NK101(de)002:2717: de yang 'khor 'das kyi chos thams cad sku gsung
NK101(de)002:2718: thugs thug phrad du ma gyur pa'i chos gang yang
NK101(de)002:2719: med de / lta ba thug phrad kyi man ngag las /
NK101(de)002:2720: blta bya phyi yi yul la bltas pas /
NK101(de)002:2721: rang gi rig pa byang chub kyi sems las /
NK101(de)002:2722: gzhan gang yang yul du mi 'dug ste /
NK101(de)002:2723: lta ba sprul sku thug phrad /
NK101(de)002:2724: blta bya nang gi sems la bltas pas /
NK101(de)002:2725: rang gi rig pa byang chub kyi sems las gzhan gang yang lta mkhan med pas /
NK101(de)002:2726: lta ba longs sku thug phrad /
NK101(de)002:2727: des na rig pa phyi nang med cing mnyam nyid chen po /
NK101(de)002:2728: chos kyi sku'i klong du rang shar rang grol la /
NK101(de)002:2729: ji ltar byas kyang ma bcos chos sku'i klong las mi 'da' bas /
NK101(de)002:2730: lta ba dang lta mkhan zhes pa de ma bcos
NK101(de)002:2731: mthar phyin du shar grol mnyam pa de lta ba
NK101(de)002:2732: chos sku thug phrad yin te /
NK101(de)002:2733: ji ltar byas kyang sku gsum 'dus ma byas pa'i klong du grol lo //
NK101(de)002:2734: sgom pa la sogs pa yod de ltar shes par bya'o //
NK101(de)002:2735: tshogs drug sku gsung thug phrad kyi gdams ngag la /
NK101(de)002:2736: mig gi yul du gzugs su snang ba yer cig shar ba de /
NK101(de)002:2737: chos nyid kyi rol pa yin te spral sku thug phrad /
NK101(de)002:2738: de rang rig tu ngo shes shing rang gsal du longs spyod pa longs sku thug phrad /
NK101(de)002:2739: de rang sar grol nas de la dngos gzhi ma
NK101(de)002:2740: rnyed pas ma bcos pa'i chos nyid de chos sku
NK101(de)002:2741: thug phrad / ji ltar byas kyang sku gsum 'dus ma byas pa'i klong du grol /
NK101(de)002:2742: rna bas sgra sogs de ltar shes par bya la /
NK101(de)002:2743: gang ji ltar byas kyang sku gsum thug phrad du shar ba'i dgongs pa chos nyid kyi ngang ngo //
NK101(de)002:2744: ral gri kha mang lta bur ni /
NK101(de)002:2745: ral gri kha mang de gang la reg pa gcod pa ltar /
NK101(de)002:2746: sku gsum rang shar gyi dgongs pa des /
NK101(de)002:2747: dus gsum gyi rtog pa rgyun gcod pa ste /
NK101(de)002:2748: thams cad de las byung zhing der grol ba'i klong ngo //
NK101(de)002:2749: de gang la'ang thogs pa med pas bdag nyid rang snang gi rigs pa /
NK101(de)002:2750: mtha' ma spangs par rang grol bas mnyam nyid chen po'i gtan tshigs byung ngo //
NK101(de)002:2752: mi g.yo ba ni sku yi rgya //
NK101(de)002:2753: zhes pa chos sku 'jig 'dral med par rang bzhin
NK101(de)002:2754: rnam dag phyag rgya chen por phyogs med du shar
NK101(de)002:2755: ba de / gang gis mi g.yo na /
NK101(de)002:2756: rgyu rkyen gnyen po gang gis kyang mi g.yo bas /
NK101(de)002:2757: chos sku 'pho 'gyur med cing skye shi med par rgya bcad mi bskyod pa ni ye shes te /
NK101(de)002:2759: phyogs su 'dzin pa'i rlung gis ma bardzi //
NK101(de)002:2760: mi len bas na bdag med cing //
NK101(de)002:2762: bdag gzhan gnyis su med pa'i dgongs pa ste /
NK101(de)002:2763: sku gsung thugs che ba'i yon tan phyogs med thams
NK101(de)002:2764: cad rang la rang chas su ye nas gnas pas
NK101(de)002:2765: / 'bras bu gzhan nas mi len zhing /
NK101(de)002:2766: nga bdag tu bzung ba med pas na /
NK101(de)002:2767: mi 'dor tshig bral mnyam nyid do //
NK101(de)002:2768: zhes pa mnyam pa nyid lhun gyis grub pa'i dgongs pa ste /
NK101(de)002:2769: des na bdag gzhan dbyer med /
NK101(de)002:2771: mi mthun pa dang gnyis su med pa la /
NK101(de)002:2772: skyon logs su 'dor du med pas /
NK101(de)002:2773: don gyi sngags tshigs smra brjod thams cad dang bral ba'i klong /
NK101(de)002:2774: dper na ral gri kha mang des /
NK101(de)002:2775: gang la reg pa gcod pa ltar /
NK101(de)002:2776: sku gsung thugs che ba'i phyag rgya rnam pa gsum gyi 'khor los /
NK101(de)002:2777: nyon mongs pa dang mthar 'dzin gyi gol sa thams cad rgyun gcod pa'o //
NK101(de)002:2778: de'i skyon bsal dang la bzla 'dra'o //
NK101(de)002:2780: gang dang gang gis gang du yang //
NK101(de)002:2781: zhes pa 'khor bar 'jug ldog med pa'i rigs pa bstan te /
NK101(de)002:2782: gang dang zhes pa 'das pa'i sangs rgyas mar me
NK101(de)002:2783: mdzad la sogs pa de gang ji snyed pa'i bde
NK101(de)002:2784: bar gshegs pa phyogs med kyi dgongs pa la mnga'
NK101(de)002:2786: gang gis zhes pa da lta ba rgyal ba sh+aakya
NK101(de)002:2787: thub pa la sogs pa ji snyed pa'i sangs rgyas
NK101(de)002:2789: gang du zhes pa ma 'ongs pa'i 'dren pa byams
NK101(de)002:2790: pa la sogs pa ji snyed pa'i sangs rgyas te
NK101(de)002:2791: / dus gsum gyi sangs rgyas ma lus pa kun
NK101(de)002:2792: gyis bde ba'i ye shes phyogs med la longs spyod
NK101(de)002:2793: pa'ang logs shig na med de /
NK101(de)002:2794: bdag nyid chen po byang chub kyi sems las byung
NK101(de)002:2795: zhing de'i yon tan nam rgyan nam shar lugs yin
NK101(de)002:2796: pas / 'khor ba rnam pa gsum dang /
NK101(de)002:2797: 'gro ba rigs drug las kyis 'khor ba yang /
NK101(de)002:2798: bdag nyid chen po byang chub kyi sems kyi rol pa'am /
NK101(de)002:2800: yo lang du shar bas na /
NK101(de)002:2802: zhes pas bdag nyid rang shar gyi rigs pa bstan te gsungs pa'o //
NK101(de)002:2804: 'di la skyes pa bud med ces //
NK101(de)002:2805: zhes pa rigs la bye brag med pa'i gtan tshigs bstan te /
NK101(de)002:2806: chos nyid mnyam pa nyid skye 'gag dang bral zhing /
NK101(de)002:2807: dus gsum du rgyun chad med cing phyogs ris med pa 'di la /
NK101(de)002:2808: skyes pa'i spyod yul yin la bud med kyi min bya ba'am /
NK101(de)002:2809: bud med kyi spyod yul yin la skye ba'i min bya ba la sogs pa gang yang med do //
NK101(de)002:2810: byang chub sems la pho mo dang /
NK101(de)002:2811: ma ning la sogs pa gang yang dmigs su med par /
NK101(de)002:2812: thams cad chos nyid du mnyam pas na /
NK101(de)002:2813: mnyam pa'i rgyal pos yongs ma gsungs //
NK101(de)002:2816: chos thams cad ris med khyab gdal la bzang ngan nam /
NK101(de)002:2817: rtog mi rtog gi khyad par gnyis su yod par ni /
NK101(de)002:2818: chos nyid mnyam pa nyid la ji bzhin par mnga' brnyes pas /
NK101(de)002:2819: rgyal ba'i rgyal mchog kun tu bzang po la sogs pas /
NK101(de)002:2820: sngar yang yongs su ma gsungs /
NK101(de)002:2821: da ltar yang gsung ba med /
NK101(de)002:2822: ma 'ongs par yang gsung bar mi 'gyur ro////da ni skabs bcu bdun pa la'ang /
NK101(de)002:2824: skye med bde ba chen po'i dgongs pa sgyu ma'i
NK101(de)002:2825: cho 'phrul lta bur nges med chen po'i klong du
NK101(de)002:2826: bstan pa / cir snang nges med kyi rigs pa la rtsol ba dgag par bstan pa /
NK101(de)002:2827: ldem dgongs man ngag gi gtan tshigs kyis phyogs lta dag par bstan pa bzhi las /
NK101(de)002:2829: dngos grub chen po'i bde ba la chags pa spong ba'i skabs /
NK101(de)002:2830: zhes pa ma h+aa dang a nu yo ga'i dngos grub chen po ni /
NK101(de)002:2831: thun mong du rig 'dzin phal pa ste /
NK101(de)002:2832: tshe la dbang ba'i rig 'dzin sogs /
NK101(de)002:2833: yo byad dang longs spyod la dbang ba sogs dang /
NK101(de)002:2834: mchog gi dngos grub chen po /
NK101(de)002:2835: yi ge 'khor lo tshogs chen gyi sa dang /
NK101(de)002:2836: ma chags pad+ma spyan gyi sa thob par 'dod pa yang /
NK101(de)002:2837: lam mchog kha sbyor gyi bde ba las 'byung bas /
NK101(de)002:2838: gnas skabs kyi bde ba las 'byung bar 'dod cing /
NK101(de)002:2839: gnas skabs kyi bde ba la chags pa de /
NK101(de)002:2840: a ti yo ga rdzogs pa chen po zhen pa med pa'i chos nyid kyis /
NK101(de)002:2841: chags pa de sbong bar ston pa'i skabs la bab bo //
NK101(de)002:2843: chos kun byang chub sems su 'dus //
NK101(de)002:2844: blang dor med par ma rtogs phyir //
NK101(de)002:2845: bde ba spong ba'i skabs zhes bya //
NK101(de)002:2848: 'di la brtul zhugs drag shul gyis //
NK101(de)002:2850: lar kyang mtha' bzhir ma skyes shing mu bzhir ma 'gags pa la /
NK101(de)002:2851: gcig la gzhan ma skyes pa /
NK101(de)002:2852: lta la ba glang ma skyes pa lta bu /
NK101(de)002:2853: 'gags nas ma skyes pa rdza chag pa lta bu la sogs pa ma yin par /
NK101(de)002:2854: 'khor 'das kyi chos thams cad rang bzhin gyis ma skyes pa'am /
NK101(de)002:2855: ye gdod ma nyid nas ma skyes pa ni /
NK101(de)002:2856: rgyu rkyen gyis ma bskyed pas /
NK101(de)002:2858: thams cad gzhi lhun gyis grub pa la ma skyes pas /
NK101(de)002:2859: phyogs 'dzin gyi rtsol sgrub med de bde ba chen po /
NK101(de)002:2860: ngo bo rang byung gi ye shes la ma skyes pas /
NK101(de)002:2861: mthar 'dzin gyis rtsol sgrub med de bde chen /
NK101(de)002:2862: don skye med la ma skyes pas /
NK101(de)002:2863: gnyis 'dzin gyis rtsol sgrub med pas bde chen /
NK101(de)002:2864: bdag nyid thog mtha' med pa la ma skyes pas /
NK101(de)002:2865: dngos po mtshan ma rang rgyud pa gang gis kyang rtsol sgrub med pa'i bde ba chen po ste /
NK101(de)002:2866: skye med bde chen gyi dgongs pa chos nyid kyi klong ngo //
NK101(de)002:2868: sgyu ma'i cho 'phrul snang bzhin du rang rgyud du ma grub pa ltar /
NK101(de)002:2869: thig le byang chub kyi sems cir yang snang tsam na /
NK101(de)002:2870: de'i rang bzhin la nges pa med de /
NK101(de)002:2871: de'i klong na thams cad shar zhing thams cad grol ba'i dgongs pa dam pa'o //
NK101(de)002:2872: de nyid mi 'gag pas cir snang nges med kyi rigs pa /
NK101(de)002:2873: brjod bral de sgra drang thad kyis rtogs par dka'
NK101(de)002:2874: bas ldem dgongs man ngag gi gtan tshigs byung ngo
NK101(de)002:2876: 'di la brtul zhugs drag shul gyis //
NK101(de)002:2877: zhes pa sbyor sgrol gnyis kyi dgongs pa la blo mi gnas pa dang /
NK101(de)002:2878: nyag gcig bya rtsol dang bral ba 'di la /
NK101(de)002:2879: ma h+aa dang a nu la sogs pa brtul zhugs sbyor ba'i spyod pa dang /
NK101(de)002:2880: drag shul sgrol ba'i spyod pa rim dang cig char la sogs par /
NK101(de)002:2881: gnas su bya ba'i ming med de //
NK101(de)002:2882: zhes pa de dag gis a ti yo ga bya
NK101(de)002:2883: bral gyi don la gnas par mi nus pas so
NK101(de)002:2885: ta na dang g+ha na la ched du brtsal ba'i
NK101(de)002:2886: spyod pa de la rang byung ye shes kyi ming
NK101(de)002:2889: 'o na gang gis grol zhe na //
NK101(de)002:2890: a dang par ni rnam ldan na //
NK101(de)002:2891: zhes pa sgra don gnyis su med pa'i dgongs pa ste /
NK101(de)002:2892: a nu t+pan+d+ha sarba d+harma zhes pa'i sgra las drangs na 'khor 'das kyi chos thams cad /
NK101(de)002:2893: gang nas kyang ma byung ma skyes pa ste /
NK101(de)002:2895: pa ra ma na zhes pa'i sgra las drangs na /
NK101(de)002:2896: rig pa ma 'gags par shar ba la /
NK101(de)002:2897: yon tan gyi rtsal rdzogs pa ste /
NK101(de)002:2898: de gnyis tshig la snga phyi byung yang don la tha dad med de /
NK101(de)002:2899: skye 'gag gnyis su med pa de /
NK101(de)002:2900: ma skyes pa'i rgyan du ma 'gags par ldan pa'o //
NK101(de)002:2902: ces pa nyams myong la zhen pa med pa'i dgongs
NK101(de)002:2903: pa gzhi nges med rol pa phyogs med du shar
NK101(de)002:2904: ba la / ngo bo 'di yin du ma grub
NK101(de)002:2905: pas sgyu ma lta bur ma nges pa'i bde chen
NK101(de)002:2906: ba la / nyid / bya rtsol dang bral bar
NK101(de)002:2907: bde chen du rang shar bas zhe 'dod med par
