NK101(de)002:2908: 'byung ba'i gdengs chen po dang ldan par 'dod do
NK101(de)002:2909: ba la / nyid / // dgongs pa de'i skyon bsal dang la bzla 'dra /
NK101(de)002:2911: rang bzhin gcig tu ma nges par //
NK101(de)002:2912: zhes pa nges med kyi rigs pa bstan te /
NK101(de)002:2913: gzhi dngos po gshis kyi gnas lugs de'i rang bzhin ni /
NK101(de)002:2914: gcig tu ma nges te mtha' thams cad du rang shar bas /
NK101(de)002:2915: 'khor 'das lam pas bsdus pa'i chos mi 'dra ba
NK101(de)002:2916: sna tshogs su shar te skyon med par rang 'byung
NK101(de)002:2917: ba'o // de yang ji ltar byung zhe na /
NK101(de)002:2918: byang chub sems thig le nyag gcig de /
NK101(de)002:2919: sangs rgyas su ma nges te sems can du rang shar la /
NK101(de)002:2920: sems can du ma nges par sangs rgyas su rang
NK101(de)002:2921: shar bas sangs rgyas sems can gnyis kar ma nges
NK101(de)002:2922: te / gnyis su rang shar la /
NK101(de)002:2923: gnyis med du ma nges pas /
NK101(de)002:2924: gnyis gnyis med dang bral bas /
NK101(de)002:2925: ji ltar bltas pa de ltar snang //
NK101(de)002:2926: zhes pa ltar snang gi rig pa bstan te /
NK101(de)002:2927: gzhi phyogs med lhun grub la /
NK101(de)002:2928: rkyen phyogs bral nges pa med pas /
NK101(de)002:2929: 'dod pa phyogs med mthong stangs tha dad du shar bas na /
NK101(de)002:2930: ya gi rdzogs pa chen po a ti yo ga'i lta ba nas /
NK101(de)002:2931: ma gi 'gro ba rigs drug dang /
NK101(de)002:2932: mu stegs rtag chad yan chad /
NK101(de)002:2933: ji ltar bltas pa ltar snang /
NK101(de)002:2936: snang ba bcu bdun nam snang tshad bsam gyis mi khyab par shar ro //
NK101(de)002:2938: snang 'dod rtsol sems bde ba yang //
NK101(de)002:2939: zhes pa zhi gnas kyi bde bas mi grol ba'i rigs pa ste /
NK101(de)002:2940: nyan thos yul sems gnyis su snang ba la /
NK101(de)002:2942: lam la rtsol sems bcug nas gnas skabs kyi bde ba la chags pa la sogs pa ste /
NK101(de)002:2943: snang ba bcu bdun rang ka ma la 'bras bu
NK101(de)002:2944: 'dod cing lam lta sgom spyod 'bras la rtsol sems
NK101(de)002:2945: bcug nas / zhi gnas kyi bde ba la chags pa de yod do //
NK101(de)002:2946: de ni de sgrib skyon chen yin //
NK101(de)002:2947: zhes pa lta sgom spyod pa phyogs re la rtsol zhing /
NK101(de)002:2948: 'bras bu la zhen 'dod byed pa ni /
NK101(de)002:2949: chos nyid mnyam pa nyid de mi rtogs pa'i sgrib pa'am /
NK101(de)002:2950: gnyis su 'dzin pa'i skyon chen po yin te mtha' phyogs re la zhen pas so //
NK101(de)002:2952: byang chub yan lag kun gyi sgo //
NK101(de)002:2953: zhes pa yo ga phyogs lta yin pa'i gtan tshigs yin te /
NK101(de)002:2954: yo ga ba mngon par byang chub pa rnam pa
NK101(de)002:2955: lngas 'jug sgo thabs kyi yan lag tu 'dod do
NK101(de)002:2956: // chos nyid stong pa la mngon par byang chub pa /
NK101(de)002:2960: sku yongs su rdzogs pa la mngon par byang chub par 'dod de /
NK101(de)002:2961: des kyang rdzogs pa chen po bya bral gyi don ma go bas gol bar gyur to //
NK101(de)002:2962: cha lugs sgom pa chu zla bzhin //
NK101(de)002:2963: zhes pa yo ga pas lha rnams kyi cha lugs
NK101(de)002:2964: kyang snang la rang bzhin med pa chu'i zla ba
NK101(de)002:2966: de'ang gzhi rgyu byin rlabs ldan pa'i tshul du brten nas /
NK101(de)002:2967: ye shes pa bcug pa dang /
NK101(de)002:2968: 'khril ba dang ldem pa la sogs par sgom pa'o //
NK101(de)002:2969: ma gos ma chags 'byung gyur kyang //
NK101(de)002:2970: zhes pa goms pas gsal ba'i tshad /
NK101(de)002:2971: zhi gnas la nyon mongs pa'i dri mas ma gos /
NK101(de)002:2972: lhag mthong la shes bya'i dri mas ma gos te /
NK101(de)002:2973: lha'i rang bzhin rang la'ang ma chags pa'i nyams 'byung bar 'gyur yang /
NK101(de)002:2974: rdzogs pa chen po'i lugs la /
NK101(de)002:2975: de gnyis chos nyid du dbyer med pas /
NK101(de)002:2976: bzang ngan dang res 'jog tu sgom pa des mi grol bas /
NK101(de)002:2977: sgom pa byis pa'i spyod yul yin //
NK101(de)002:2978: zhes pa lha'i dkyil 'khor sgom pas /
NK101(de)002:2979: byis pa'i khang bu gal che che ltar brtsigs nas /
NK101(de)002:2980: tha ma dgos pa med par 'jog pa dang 'dra ste /
NK101(de)002:2982: dang po lha dgos dgos ltar bskyed nas /
NK101(de)002:2983: tha ma mi dgos pa ltar badz+ra muhl sogs pas bsdus te /
NK101(de)002:2984: spyod yul la res 'jog yod pa'ang /
NK101(de)002:2985: a ti yo ga bya bral chig chod don las gol lo //
NK101(de)002:2987: khro bo'i lha tshogs sgom pa gol bar bstan pa ni /
NK101(de)002:2988: dkyil 'khor khro gnyen cha lugs kyis //
NK101(de)002:2989: zhes pa ma h+aa phyogs lha yin pa'i gtan tshigs te /
NK101(de)002:2991: dkyil badz+ra he ru ka /'khor rigs bzhi'i khro bos bskor ba dang /
NK101(de)002:2992: khro gnyer brjid pas gnyer mas yas mnan /
NK101(de)002:2993: mdzes 'dzum sdud pa'i gnyer mas mas bteg pa'ang /
NK101(de)002:2994: cha lugs dur khrod kyi chas brgyad de /
NK101(de)002:2995: zhing gi g.yang gzhi la sogs par 'dod do //
NK101(de)002:2996: khro bdag chen po'i lus bzung nas //
NK101(de)002:2998: yang na dkyil 'khor gyi dbus su rang nyid de lta bur sgom pa'am /
NK101(de)002:2999: mdun du bskyed nas sgom pa dang //
NK101(de)002:3000: yi ge mngon du phyung na yang //
NK101(de)002:3001: zhes pa lha de goms pa gsal ba'i tshad dper
NK101(de)002:3002: na yi ge bris pas dbang po'i mngon sum du
NK101(de)002:3003: ce re bltar yod pa ltar /
NK101(de)002:3004: rnal 'byor gyi mngon sum du wa ler gsal kyang /
NK101(de)002:3005: rtsol sgrub kyi skyon yod de /
NK101(de)002:3006: mnyam pa chen po'i don las gol bas na /
NK101(de)002:3007: zhi ba de nyid mthong ba med //
NK101(de)002:3008: ces pa mngon sum gyis gtan la mi phebs pa'i gtan tshigs bstan te /
NK101(de)002:3009: bskyed pa'i rim pas rtog tshogs gnas gyur /
NK101(de)002:3011: zhi ba chen po chos nyid kyi don bya rtsol
NK101(de)002:3012: dang bral ba'i de kho na nyid mthong ba med
NK101(de)002:3013: do // 'o na bskyed rim thams cad don med yin nam zhe na /
NK101(de)002:3014: don med pa ma yin te /
NK101(de)002:3015: rnam grangs brgya stong phrag yangs pas /
NK101(de)002:3016: zhes pa 'jug sgo gang yang ma bkag pa'i gtan tshigs bstan te /
NK101(de)002:3017: sems can gyi sems la nyon mongs pa'i rtog tshogs mi 'dra ba /
NK101(de)002:3018: bsam gyis mi khyab pa yod pas na /
NK101(de)002:3019: de'i gnyen por chos kyi sgo mo brgyad khri bzhi stong phrag yongs su bshad de gsungs pas /
NK101(de)002:3020: gang ltar spyod kyang me tog skye //
NK101(de)002:3021: zhes pa gcig kho nar ma nges pa'i gtan tshigs bstan te /
NK101(de)002:3022: rang rang gar mos kyi sgor zhugs te thad ka'i lta sgom la spyod pas kyang /
NK101(de)002:3023: gnas skabs kyi 'bras bu me tog dang 'dra bar skye'o //
NK101(de)002:3025: mtshan ma med pa'i dbang gis na //
NK101(de)002:3026: zhes pa yang dag don gyi 'bras bu mi 'byung ba'i gtan tshigs bstan te /
NK101(de)002:3027: chos nyid phyogs med kyi rig pa dngos med la /
NK101(de)002:3029: phyogs gcig tsam gyi mtshan med la gnas pas na /
NK101(de)002:3030: ngal bso tsam du rtogs pa'i dbang gis na'o //
NK101(de)002:3032: zhes pa theg pa 'og ma pa ngal bso ba tsam de /
NK101(de)002:3033: stegs 'cha' ba tsam gyi lus sems kyi bde ba gnas skabs kyi 'bras bu yin pas /
NK101(de)002:3034: rang grol chen po ma bcos rang byung ye shes
NK101(de)002:3035: kyi 'bras bu phyogs med nyid 'byung bar mi 'gyur
NK101(de)002:3036: ro // de rnams kyi rgyas gdab 'agre'o////da ni skabs bac+wo brgyad pa la'ang /
NK101(de)002:3038: chos nyid rang la shar ba'i dgongs pa gzhon nu
NK101(de)002:3039: ma'i bde ba lta bu brjod pa dang bral ba'i
NK101(de)002:3041: lhun grub 'byed pa med pa'i rigs pa bstan pa /
NK101(de)002:3042: spyod yul phyogs med rol pa'i gtan tshigs bstan pa dang bzhi las /
NK101(de)002:3044: rtsol ba dang bral ba'i skabs /
NK101(de)002:3045: zhes pa a nu yo ga man chad rgyu dang 'bras bu gnyis su rtsol /
NK101(de)002:3046: 'khor ba dang myang 'das gnyis su rtsol te /
NK101(de)002:3047: lam pa'i lta sgom spyod pa dang 'bras bu ched du rtsol ba de las /
NK101(de)002:3048: rdzogs pa chen po a ti yo ga rtsol ba dang bral bar bstan pa'i skabs la bab bo //
NK101(de)002:3051: chos kun byang chub sems su 'dus //
NK101(de)002:3052: sems la brtsal du med pa'i phyir //
NK101(de)002:3053: rtsol dang bral ba'i skabs zhes bya //
NK101(de)002:3056: gleng bral 'di la gang gnas pa //
NK101(de)002:3057: zhes chos nyid rang gi rigs pa byang chub kyi sems de rtogs rung ma rtogs rung /
NK101(de)002:3058: rgyu rkyen las ka nas ma byung ste /
NK101(de)002:3060: dngos po gshis kyi gnas lugs so //
NK101(de)002:3062: 'khor ba rang las mya ngan las 'das par shar ba'am /
NK101(de)002:3063: bde sdug la sogs pa gnyis bsdus kun kyang de ltar shar bas /
NK101(de)002:3064: rnam rtog rang la chos skur shar /
NK101(de)002:3065: rig pa rang las 'khor 'das su shar bas /
NK101(de)002:3066: gnyis su med pa'i dgongs pa chos nyid kyi klong ngo //
NK101(de)002:3067: gzhon nu ma'i bde ba lta bur ni /
NK101(de)002:3068: nyams su myong yang smra mi shes pa'i dpe ste /
NK101(de)002:3069: chos nyid mtshon du med pa'i klong la /
NK101(de)002:3070: rig pa bde blag chen por gnas pas brjod pa dang bral ba'i dbyings la /
NK101(de)002:3071: thams cad shar zhing de ru grol ba'i klong ngo //
NK101(de)002:3072: de la yul dang yul can gnyis su med pas lhun grub 'byed pa med pa'i rigs pa /
NK101(de)002:3073: snang ba brgya yan yin pas spyod yul phyogs med du 'char ba'i gtan tshigs byung ngo //
NK101(de)002:3075: gleng bral 'di la gang gnas pa //
NK101(de)002:3076: zhes pa chos nyid phyi nang med cing smra brjod dang bral ba'i don /
NK101(de)002:3077: 'dod pa med par rang gi rgyud la shar te /
NK101(de)002:3078: go ba klungs su gyur nas chos nyid mnyam pa
NK101(de)002:3079: nyid la rig pa bde blag chen por gnas pas
NK101(de)002:3080: na / rnal 'byor 'di ni skal pa bzang zhes pa ye nas yod pa'i dgongs pa ste /
NK101(de)002:3082: rig pa btang bzhag med par 'byor pas /
NK101(de)002:3084: sems ye sangs rgyas pa yin te /
NK101(de)002:3087: dus phyi ma la mi ltos te /
NK101(de)002:3088: phugs thag da ltar gyi snang ba la chod nas /
NK101(de)002:3089: rtog grol thar pa mchog nyid dus gcig tu shar
NK101(de)002:3090: nas ye sangs rgyas par mnga' brnyes pas bskal pa
NK101(de)002:3091: bzang ngo // dgongs pa de'i skyon bsal 'dra /
NK101(de)002:3093: bdag dang gzhan don mi 'byed pas /
NK101(de)002:3094: zhes pa gzhi ngo bo don bdag nyid mnyam pa chen po'i rang bzhin la /
NK101(de)002:3095: bdag chos sku mnyam pa nyid la gnas pa dang /
NK101(de)002:3096: gzhan gzugs sku rnam pa gnyis kyis 'gro ba sems kyi don mdzad pa dang /
NK101(de)002:3097: bdag sems can gyi las dang /
NK101(de)002:3098: gzhan sangs rgyas kyi mdzad spyod gnyis ka /
NK101(de)002:3099: chos nyid yul med du shar bas dus dang rnam pa thams cad du dbyer med do //
NK101(de)002:3101: sgyu ma lhun grub yul la rol /
NK101(de)002:3102: zhes pa byang chub sems gzhi nges med rol pa
NK101(de)002:3103: phyogs med cir yang 'char te mtha' ma spangs rang
NK101(de)002:3104: sar grol bas / skye med du lhun gyis grub ste /
NK101(de)002:3105: rig pa yul med chos nyid skyon bral la /
NK101(de)002:3106: spyod yul phyogs med du rol lo //
NK101(de)002:3107: de bzhi'i rgyas gdab 'agre'o////da ni skabs bcu dgu pa la'ang /
NK101(de)002:3109: snang ba yongs su rdzogs pa'i dgongs pa nam mkha'
NK101(de)002:3110: dwangs pa'i dkyil lta bur 'pho 'gyur med pa'i klong
NK101(de)002:3111: du bstan pa / rang byung ye shes lhun gyis grub pa'i rigs pa bstan pa /
NK101(de)002:3112: ngo bo 'di zhes mtshan pa las 'das pa'i gtan tshigs bstan pa dang bzhi las /
NK101(de)002:3114: chos nyid kun tu mi 'gyur ba'i skabs /
NK101(de)002:3116: rtogs rung ma rtogs rung gzhi phyi mo ye nas
NK101(de)002:3117: ma bslad par 'dus ma byas pa'i chos nyid do
NK101(de)002:3119: 'das ma 'ongs da ltar la sogs te /
NK101(de)002:3120: dus dang gnas skabs kun tu /
NK101(de)002:3121: rgyu rkyen gnyen po gang gi dbang du yang mi 'gyur bar ston pa'i skabs la bab bo //
NK101(de)002:3123: chos kun byang chub sems su 'dus //
NK101(de)002:3124: sems la 'gyur ba med pa'i phyir //
NK101(de)002:3125: chos nyid mi 'gyur skabs zhes bya //
NK101(de)002:3128: lhag ma med par yongs su rdzogs //
NK101(de)002:3129: zhes pa snang ba ma dag pa ni /
NK101(de)002:3130: 'khrul pa'i snang ba skye bo rang ka ma /
NK101(de)002:3131: log lta'i snang ba mu stegs rtag chad gnyis /
NK101(de)002:3132: lam pa phyogs 'dzin gyi snang ba theg pa rim brgyad kyi lta sgom /
NK101(de)002:3133: bde gshegs ye shes kyi snang ba rtogs goms las byung ba'i sangs rgyas te /
NK101(de)002:3134: snang ba rnam pa bzhi po de yang dag par rdzogs nas /
NK101(de)002:3135: a ti yo ga rang rig gnyis su med cing
NK101(de)002:3136: mi 'gyur bas gnas lugs ma bcos pa'i snang ba
NK101(de)002:3137: / yongs su rdzogs pa'i dgongs pa dam pa chos nyid kyi ngang ngo //
NK101(de)002:3138: nam mkha' dwangs pa'i dkyil lta bur ni yongs la
NK101(de)002:3139: khyab cing phyogs ris dang bral te ngos bzung med
NK101(de)002:3141: 'pho 'gyur med pa'i klong ni 'dus ma byas pa yin pas gnyen pos mi 'jig ste /
NK101(de)002:3142: 'jig 'bral med pa'i ngang las thams cad shar zhing der grol ba'i klong ngo //
NK101(de)002:3143: de rgyu rkyen gyis ma bskyed pas rang byung ye shes lhun gyi grub pa'i rigs pa /
NK101(de)002:3144: de la dmigs su med pas 'di zhes mtshon pa las 'das pa'i gtan tshigs byung ngo //
NK101(de)002:3146: lhag ma med par yongs su rdzogs //
NK101(de)002:3147: zhes pa ma 'dres yongs rdzogs kyi dgongs pa bstan te /
NK101(de)002:3148: gang rdzogs na snang srid 'khor 'das yod med rtag
NK101(de)002:3149: chad phyi nang snod bcud kyis bsdus pa'i chos thams
NK101(de)002:3150: cad lhag ma med par yongs su rdzogs so //
NK101(de)002:3152: gang du rdzogs na gzhi ngo bo don bdag nyid
NK101(de)002:3153: mnyam pa nyid thig le nyag gcig gi klong du
NK101(de)002:3154: yongs su rdzogs so zhes bya /
NK101(de)002:3156: 'gyur ba ma yin drang por gnas //
NK101(de)002:3157: zhes pa bslu brid med pa'i dgongs pa bstan te /
NK101(de)002:3158: des na chos nyid de rgyu rkyen gnyen po thams
NK101(de)002:3159: cad dang bral bas 'pho 'gyur med cing mnyam pa
NK101(de)002:3160: ris med / chos nyid phyogs med las ma g.yos par /
NK101(de)002:3161: 'khor 'das sam phyi nang mtho dman med de /
NK101(de)002:3162: kun la ya yo med cing /
NK101(de)002:3163: gnyis med drang por gnas so //
NK101(de)002:3164: 'o na de nyid dpe ci dang 'dra bar rdzogs she na /
NK101(de)002:3165: nam mkha' bzhin du mtha' mnyam zhing /
NK101(de)002:3166: zhes pa dpe don gnyis su med pa'i dgongs pa ste /
NK101(de)002:3167: nam mkha' ni phyogs ris dang mtha' dbus kyi phyogs med yin kyang /
NK101(de)002:3168: matha'i dngos po thams cad la ma khyab pa med pa bzhin du /
NK101(de)002:3169: chos nyid mnyam pa nyid nam mkha' lta bus /
NK101(de)002:3170: ya tha sangs rgyas kyi dgongs pa nas /
NK101(de)002:3171: ma tha dmyal ba'i gting yan chad /
NK101(de)002:3172: snang srid 'khor 'das yod med rtag chad phyi nang snod bcud kyis bsdus pa'i chos thams cad la /
NK101(de)002:3173: phyogs ris med par khyab la gzhan med pas na /
NK101(de)002:3174: gzhan la ltos 'gyur chos ma yin /
NK101(de)002:3175: zhes pa gnyen pos gzhig tu med pa'i dgongs pa ma nor ba nyid do //
NK101(de)002:3176: des na rdzogs pa chen po a ti yo ga'i lugs 'di /
NK101(de)002:3177: theg pa 'og ma pa rgyu rkyen la ltos pa dang mi 'dra ste /
NK101(de)002:3178: dus dang gnyen po gzhan la mi ltos pa'i dpes
NK101(de)002:3179: 'bras bu ma brtsal lhun gyis grub pas rang la
NK101(de)002:3180: byung ba'o // dgongs pa de'i skyon bsal dang la bzla 'dra /
NK101(de)002:3182: lhun gyis gnas pas bde chen de //
NK101(de)002:3183: zhes pa yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kyi che ba'i yon tan dang /
NK101(de)002:3184: zab mo'i chos 'bras bu la rag ma las pa dang /
NK101(de)002:3185: 'khor ba'i skyon dang sems can gyi sdug bsngal ma lus pa thams cad /
NK101(de)002:3186: thig le nyag gcig bya rtsol dang bral ba'i klong du ma spangs rang sar grol /
NK101(de)002:3187: gnyis su med par lhun gyis grub nas gnas pas /
NK101(de)002:3188: rnam med rtsol bral zag pa med pa'i bde ba chen po nyid de /
NK101(de)002:3189: mtshungs pa med pa'i ye shes kyis //
NK101(de)002:3190: zhes pa thun mong ma yin pa'i rigs pa bstan te /
NK101(de)002:3191: rdzogs pa chen po'i rang byung gi ye shes chen
NK101(de)002:3192: po de la 'khor 'das theg pa gang gis kyang
NK101(de)002:3195: ma rtogs pas ngan du ma song /
NK101(de)002:3196: bltas pas phyogs re las ma rtogs te /
NK101(de)002:3197: rgyu rkyen med par 'khor 'das thams cad du rang shar bas /
NK101(de)002:3198: rang byung ye shes kyi sa'o //
NK101(de)002:3199: rang gi mthu yis rig pa las //
NK101(de)002:3200: zhes pa yul dang yul can med pa'i rigs pa bstan te /
NK101(de)002:3201: de lta bu'i don de yang chos nyid rang gis
NK101(de)002:3202: rang rig pa'i mthu yis sangs rgyas kyi dgongs pa
NK101(de)002:3203: rang la rang 'char bar rig pa lags te /
NK101(de)002:3205: mngon sum rjes dpag chos nyid tshad ma min //
NK101(de)002:3206: gal te yin na gnas lugs gzhal byar 'gyur //
NK101(de)002:3209: zhes pa chos nyid skye ba med pa'i don rang la bzhag nas /
NK101(de)002:3210: theg pa 'og ma pa bzhin du rtsol sgrub byas pas /
NK101(de)002:3211: 'bras bu gzhan nas 'byung bar mi 'gyur te /
NK101(de)002:3212: rig pa thugs kyi rgyud las /
NK101(de)002:3213: shes rab rig pa gzhi nas shar ba la //
NK101(de)002:3214: rna bas mnyan zhing lce yis brjod mi dgos //
NK101(de)002:3217: sla zhing dka' la dka' phyir sla //
NK101(de)002:3218: zhes dpe la lar sla phyir dka' yang gsungs pa /
NK101(de)002:3219: man ngag yin nges pa'i gtan tshigs yin te /
NK101(de)002:3220: chos thams cad kyi de bzhin nyid rang la yod pa dang /
NK101(de)002:3221: 'bras bu gzhan nas rtsol mi dgos pa dang /
NK101(de)002:3222: snang ba 'di nyid ma spangs rang sar ye nas grol bas sla zhing /
NK101(de)002:3223: a nu yo ga man chad kyis rang la yod kyang ngo ma shes pa dang /
NK101(de)002:3224: rtsol sgrub la sangs rgyas re bas dka' la /
NK101(de)002:3225: a ti bstan ma thag tu ngo shes pa dang /
NK101(de)002:3226: ye grol chen por sangs rgyas kyang ngos gzung dang bral bas sla phyir dka' 'o //
NK101(de)002:3227: de cis sla bar shis she na /
NK101(de)002:3228: mngon sum mi gnas kun la khyab //
NK101(de)002:3229: ces pa don rgyas par bshad pa'i gtan tshigs bstan te /
NK101(de)002:3230: chos nyid skye 'gag dang bral ba de /
NK101(de)002:3232: mtshan ma med pa'i klong du shar bas dbang po'i
NK101(de)002:3233: mngon sum la rdzas lta bur yul dang yul can
NK101(de)002:3235: phyogs dang ris dang rgya chad med pas /
NK101(de)002:3236: 'khor 'das kun tu khyab pa yin no //
NK101(de)002:3238: ming tsam 'di zhes bstan pa ni /
NK101(de)002:3239: zhes pa mtshon bya las 'das pa chos nyid dngos kyi don te /
NK101(de)002:3240: dngos po dang mtshan ma phyogs gcig pa lta ci smos te /
NK101(de)002:3241: thog ma chos nyid phyogs med la phyogs su gcig
NK101(de)002:3242: pa'i brjod pa ming tsam tshig tsam du smos te
NK101(de)002:3244: gang zag gis stangs mtshon par mi nus pas /
NK101(de)002:3245: rdo rje sems dpas mtshon du med //
NK101(de)002:3246: ces pa ston pa rdo rje sems dpa' nyid kyis kyang phyogs gcig tu mtshon du med de /
NK101(de)002:3248: gnas lugs ming la mi gnas shing //
NK101(de)002:3249: rtogs don ldog sa las grol bas //
NK101(de)002:3250: dgongs pa'i ngo bo rang la dris //
NK101(de)002:3251: brda rgyud than pas ci zhig smra //
NK101(de)002:3253: de rnams kyi rgyas gdab 'agre'o////da ni skabs nyi shu pa la'ang /
NK101(de)002:3255: mthong snang thug phrad du 'char ba'i dgongs pa nam
NK101(de)002:3256: mkha' dang cho 'phrul lta bur rang byung ye shes
NK101(de)002:3258: khyab pa rang 'byung gi rigs pa bstan pa /
NK101(de)002:3259: rang la yod kyang mtshon dgos pa'i gtan tshigs bstan pa dang bzhi las /
NK101(de)002:3261: rgyu rkyen las mi 'grub pa'i skabs //
NK101(de)002:3262: zhes pa rgyu rkyen 'bras bur btags pa'i chos thams cad ni glo bur ba yin nges /
NK101(de)002:3263: 'dus byas la sangs rgyas re ba des /
NK101(de)002:3264: chos nyid 'jig 'dral med cing 'dus ma byas pa dang /
NK101(de)002:3265: rgyu rkyen med cing rang byung gi don de mi 'grub par ston pa'i skabs la bab bo //
NK101(de)002:3267: chos kun byang chub sems su 'dus //
NK101(de)002:3268: sems la gnyen po med pa'i phyir //
NK101(de)002:3269: rgyu rkyen bral ba'i skabs zhes bya //
NK101(de)002:3272: ngo mtshar rmad byung rol pa 'di //
NK101(de)002:3273: zhes pa la sogs pas ston te /
NK101(de)002:3274: dbang mthong snang gi mig gis gzugs mthong ba la sogs pa ste /
NK101(de)002:3275: sgo lnga yul du snang tshod dang brtags tshod /
NK101(de)002:3276: grags tshod dang shar tshod 'di rang ngo //
NK101(de)002:3277: thug phrad ni tshogs drug sku gsum thug phrad du 'char ba yin te /
NK101(de)002:3278: gzugs su snang ba sprul sku thug phrad /
NK101(de)002:3279: sgra ru grag pa longs sku thug phrad /
NK101(de)002:3280: dran rtog thams cad chos sku thug phrad du 'char ba'i dgongs pa chos nyid kyi ngang ngo //
NK101(de)002:3281: nam mkha' dang cho 'phrul lta bu ni /
NK101(de)002:3282: rang byung rang zhi'i dpe yin te /
NK101(de)002:3283: 'khor 'das kyi chos thams cad byung yang rig pa
NK101(de)002:3284: rang byung gi ye shes nam mkha' lta bu las
NK101(de)002:3285: rang byung la / zhi yang de rang du zhi bas rang byung ye shes kyi klong ngo //
NK101(de)002:3286: de nyid mtha' gang la'ang ma spangs par khyab pa
NK101(de)002:3287: rang bzhin gyi rig pa ye shes nang nas shar
NK101(de)002:3288: bas rang la yod kyang mtshon dgos pa'i gtan tshigs
NK101(de)002:3290: ngo mtshar rmad byung rol pa 'di //
NK101(de)002:3291: zhes pa chos nyid rang la yod pas gzhan sgrub mi dgos pas ngo mtshar ba dang /
NK101(de)002:3292: a nu man chad kyis rtogs par dka' bas rmad du byung ba dang /
NK101(de)002:3293: yongs la khyab cing ris med pas gsang ba dam pa'o //
NK101(de)002:3294: rol pa ni cir yang mi 'gag la rgya ma chad pas thams cad du shar ba 'adi'o //
NK101(de)002:3295: bya bral nam mkha' ji bzhin du //
NK101(de)002:3297: dpe don gnyis su med pa'i dgongs pa chos nyid
NK101(de)002:3298: bya bral gyi ngang lhun grub kyi 'jings nam mkha'i
NK101(de)002:3300: rig pa cir yang mi 'gag ste phyogs med du
NK101(de)002:3301: 'byung ba'i dpe yang nam mkha' la cho 'phrul kog
NK101(de)002:3302: langs su 'byung ba ji bzhin no //
NK101(de)002:3303: 'o na chos nyid de rang gi ngo bo ji lta bu zhe na /
NK101(de)002:3304: cir yang mi dmigs gti mug las //
NK101(de)002:3305: zhes pa chos nyid mi 'byed pa'i dgongs pa /
NK101(de)002:3306: mnyam pa nyid la phyogs dang ris su dbyer med pa'i bzang ngan legs nyes /
NK101(de)002:3307: mtho dman dang yangs dog med pas gnyis 'dzin gyi spros pa cir yang mi dmigs par /
NK101(de)002:3308: don gyi gdengs rang byung gi ye shes chen po lags te /
NK101(de)002:3310: rnam pa cir yang mi 'byed ye shes gti mug pa //
NK101(de)002:3311: thogs med gsal ba'i mar me bsam pa kun dang bral //
NK101(de)002:3313: de ma thag tu rang las 'byung /
NK101(de)002:3314: zhes pa har ya hur sprugs rig pa kog langs kyi dgongs pa /
NK101(de)002:3315: go ba'am bstan pa'i dus de ma thag tu /
NK101(de)002:3316: yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kyi che ba'i
NK101(de)002:3317: yon tan zab mo'i chos dang 'bras bu'i don thams
NK101(de)002:3318: cad ma brtsal bzhin du rang las phyogs med du
NK101(de)002:3319: 'byung ste / skyon thams cad rang grol du 'byung bas so //
NK101(de)002:3322: 'di ni thams cad mtshungs pa'i lam //
NK101(de)002:3323: zhes pa khyab pa spyi'i rigs pa /
NK101(de)002:3324: chos nyid skye 'gag med cing 'dus ma byas pa'i don 'di ni /
NK101(de)002:3325: khams gsum gyi sems can la tshabs mi chung /
NK101(de)002:3326: dus gsum gyi sangs rgyas la tshabs mi che ste /
NK101(de)002:3327: 'khor 'das thams cad kyi lam chen nam /
NK101(de)002:3329: thams cad thig le gcig tu dbyer med cing /
NK101(de)002:3330: mtshungs dang gcig pa'i klong lam chen po'o //
NK101(de)002:3332: 'gro ba kun la rang bzhin gnas //
NK101(de)002:3333: zhes pa 'du 'bral med pa'i rig pa /
NK101(de)002:3334: las nas las su 'gro ba ni /
NK101(de)002:3336: sngar gyi las ngan pas phyis sdug bsngal gyi khar 'khor ba dang /
NK101(de)002:3337: ye shes nas ye shes su 'gro ba ni /
NK101(de)002:3339: sngar gyi las bzang pos mtho ris su skye nas /
NK101(de)002:3340: da dung sangs rgyas kyi sa la 'gro ba ste /
NK101(de)002:3341: bsdus par thams cad dbyings nas shar zhing dbyings su 'gro ba rigs drug po kun la /
NK101(de)002:3342: chos nyid bya bral gyi klong chen po de /
NK101(de)002:3343: bzang ngan dang dbri bsnan med pas /
NK101(de)002:3344: ye thog ma nyid nas rang bzhin gyis khyab par
NK101(de)002:3345: gnas pas de ji lta bar bstan pa tsam gyis
NK101(de)002:3348: byis pas bslad pas 'khrul pa'i phyir //
NK101(de)002:3349: zhes pa don gang la dgongs pa'i gtan tshigs byis pa la gnyis te /
NK101(de)002:3350: brda la shed ma phye ba'i byis pa so so'i skye bo /
NK101(de)002:3351: don la shes ma phye ba'i byis pa theg pa 'og ma pa /
NK101(de)002:3352: lam lta sgom phyogs re la brtsal bas kyang /
NK101(de)002:3353: phyogs med kyi don ma go ste /
NK101(de)002:3355: mnyam pa nyid kyi ngang la phyis 'khrul ba'i phyir ro //
NK101(de)002:3356: 'o na 'khrul pa de la skyon ci yod ce na /
NK101(de)002:3357: sman nyid sman pa 'tshol ba bzhin //
NK101(de)002:3359: dper na sman rang la yod kyang sman pas ma gtang na ngo mi shes pas /
NK101(de)002:3360: sman pa gzhan nas 'tshol ba bzhin du /
NK101(de)002:3361: chos thams cad ye sangs rgyas pa yin te chos
NK101(de)002:3362: nyid rang rang la mnyam par yod kyang de'i don
NK101(de)002:3363: ston pa slob dpon la rag las pa yin no
NK101(de)002:3364: // de bzhi'i rgyas gdab 'agre'o////da ni skabs nyi shu rtsa gcig pa'ang /
NK101(de)002:3366: rig pa rang grol gyi dgongs pa nam mkha'i dkyil
NK101(de)002:3367: 'khor lta bur gdal ba chen po'i klong du bstan
NK101(de)002:3368: pa / sna tshogs kun gsal cir yang snang ba'i rigs pa bstan pa /
NK101(de)002:3369: phyi nang snod bcud las che ba'i gtan tshigs bstan pa /
NK101(de)002:3370: thig le'i nges tshig bstan pa dang lnga las /
NK101(de)002:3372: 'gro ba yongs la sangs rgyas par bstan pa'i skabs /
NK101(de)002:3373: zhes pa 'gro ba ni rigs drug go //
NK101(de)002:3374: der yang ma zad de rgyal 'gro lam pas bsdus pa'i chos yongs la spyi khyab tu gnas te /
NK101(de)002:3375: thams cad dbyings su grol ba'i phyir ro //
NK101(de)002:3376: ye grol chen po'i klong du ye sangs rgyas par gnas pas /
NK101(de)002:3377: de lta bu'i don zab mo ston pa'i skabs la bab bo //
NK101(de)002:3379: chos kun byang chub sems su gcig /
NK101(de)002:3380: rgyud drug snying por sems gcig phyir //
NK101(de)002:3381: 'gro kun sangs rgyas skabs zhes bya //
NK101(de)002:3384: go ba'i yul na bde ba che /
NK101(de)002:3385: zhes pa la sogs pas ston te /
NK101(de)002:3386: de yang rig pa spyi khyab pa ma rtogs rig gam /
NK101(de)002:3388: shes rig lta bu ma yin /
NK101(de)002:3389: rdzogs pa chen po a ti yo ga'i lugs kyis ye rig ye shar yin te /
NK101(de)002:3390: sems can ye nas sangs rgyas su rig /
NK101(de)002:3391: snang stong la sogs pa gnyis bsdus thams cad 'dra ste /
NK101(de)002:3392: gzhi ye nas lhun gyis grub par rig /
NK101(de)002:3393: ngo bo ye nas nges med /
NK101(de)002:3395: bdag nyid ye nas thog mtha' dang bral bar rig
NK101(de)002:3396: /'khor 'das kyi chos thams cad ye nas rang gi
NK101(de)002:3397: byang chub kyi sems su rig pas /
NK101(de)002:3399: rang grol ni de ka ltar sems can sangs rgyas su grol bas na kun 'dra ste /
NK101(de)002:3400: rig pa rang grol gyi dgongs pa chos nyid kyi klong ngo //
NK101(de)002:3401: nam mkha'i dkyil ni mtha' dbus med par khyab cing gdal ba bzhin du /
NK101(de)002:3402: chos nyid bya bral gyi klong ni /
NK101(de)002:3403: rgya gar yang ma chad la phyogs gang du'ang ma lhung ste /
NK101(de)002:3404: mtha' bral chen po'i ngang la thams cad shar zhing de ru 'dus pa'i klong ngo //
NK101(de)002:3405: de la mtha' phyogs gcig pa gang yang med pas /
NK101(de)002:3406: sna tshogs kun gsal cir yang snang ba'i rigs pa /
NK101(de)002:3407: thams cad de las byung bas phyi nang snod bcud las che ba'i gtan tshigs zhes bya'o //
NK101(de)002:3409: go ba'i yul na bde ba che //
NK101(de)002:3410: zhes pa go ba dang sangs rgyas pa dus mnyam pa'i dgongs pa /
NK101(de)002:3411: rdzogs pa chen po'i rnal 'byor pas /
NK101(de)002:3413: snang ba la 'jal so tshugs pas /
NK101(de)002:3414: go ba phyogs med du skyes tsa na /
NK101(de)002:3415: da ltar gyi snang tshod dang btags tshod /
NK101(de)002:3416: grags tshod dang shar tshod kyi spyod yul wa le khyug ger 'dug pa 'di rang /
NK101(de)002:3417: bde ba chen po'i zhing khams sam /
NK101(de)002:3418: pad+ma can gyi zhing khams sam /
NK101(de)002:3419: rnam par dag pa'i zhing khams sam /
NK101(de)002:3421: de cis na rdzogs pa chen po'i lugs te /
NK101(de)002:3423: ye shes rig pa'i 'khor lo la //
NK101(de)002:3424: ci yang yin no rnam kun bcas //
NK101(de)002:3425: zhes pa ltar ci yang yin pa'i gnad kas so //
NK101(de)002:3428: zhes pa sgrib g.yogs med pa'i dgongs pa ste /
NK101(de)002:3429: de'i phyir skye bo rang ka mas btags pa'i /
NK101(de)002:3430: ma dag 'khrul ba'i snang ba 'di nyid ma spangs par /
NK101(de)002:3431: dag pa ye shes kyi snang bar phyogs med du shar bas dngos rang ye nas yin pas /
NK101(de)002:3434: zhes pa thig le gcig tu 'dus pa'i dgongs pa ste /
NK101(de)002:3435: chos nyid thig le nyag gcig rgya gang du'ang ma chad /
NK101(de)002:3437: mnyam nyid chen po de la /
NK101(de)002:3438: phyogs bzhi mtshams bzhi ste brgyad /
NK101(de)002:3439: steng 'og gnyis te bcur rang grags pa'i chos thams cad ma spangs te /
NK101(de)002:3440: lhun gyis grub par 'dus bas na //
NK101(de)002:3442: ces pa chos nyid rgya ma chad pa'i dgongs pa
NK101(de)002:3443: gzhi lhun grub thig le nyag gcig las ma g.yos
NK101(de)002:3444: par ngo bo ma nges rang byung gi ye shes
NK101(de)002:3445: rol pa cir yang shar bas /
NK101(de)002:3446: phyogs bzhi mtshams bzhi ste brgyad /
NK101(de)002:3447: steng 'og gnyis te bcu la sogs pa'i phyogs mtshams thams cad du ma brtsal bar rang shar bas /
NK101(de)002:3448: bla 'og phyogs mtshams kyi chos thams cad ma bsgrubs par grub pa'o //
NK101(de)002:3449: dgongs pa de'i skyon bsal ba 'dra'o //
NK101(de)002:3451: ma nges 'ja' tshon kha dog las //
NK101(de)002:3452: zhes pa dpe don gnyis med kyi rigs pa /
NK101(de)002:3453: rdzogs pa chen po a ti yo ga la gzhi nges med kun gyi dngos gzhi la /
NK101(de)002:3456: 'khor 'das bde sdug skyon yon cir yang 'char bas /
NK101(de)002:3457: dper na 'ja' tshon snang la rang bzhin med pa ltar /
NK101(de)002:3458: rol pa rang rgyud pa med de /
NK101(de)002:3460: rigs kyi khyad par mngon par snang //
NK101(de)002:3461: zhes pa don gcig tu ma nges pa'i rigs pa bstan pa /
NK101(de)002:3462: gzhi ma nges sna tshogs nor bu rin po che lta bu la /
NK101(de)002:3463: 'gro ba'i rigs ma 'dra ba sna tshogs su shar ba dang /
NK101(de)002:3464: theg pa'i khyad par bsam gyis mi khyab pa tsam du 'byung ba ni /
NK101(de)002:3465: sngon byung sangs rgyas rnams kyis gsungs pa dang /
NK101(de)002:3466: da lta gang zag gi blo la mngon par snang ba 'di nyid yin no //
NK101(de)002:3468: de bzhin g.yo rdul mi g.yo ba //
NK101(de)002:3470: de bzhin nyid kyi dbyings las ma g.yos par /
NK101(de)002:3471: g.yo ba ni nang bcud kyi sems can skye shi la sngas bcas pas mi brtan pa dang /
NK101(de)002:3473: phyi snod kyi 'jig rten rdul phra rab las grub pa de /
NK101(de)002:3474: 'byung ba rang rang gi mthus mi 'jig ste /
NK101(de)002:3476: chu yis chu mi gsher kyang gcig la gcig 'phangs pa'i tshul gyis 'jig pa ni /
NK101(de)002:3479: me bdun chu gcig gi bskal pa'o //
NK101(de)002:3480: des na phyi nang snod bcud gnyis kyi mi g.yo
NK101(de)002:3481: ba ni 'bras bu chos kyi sku 'pho 'gyur med
NK101(de)002:3484: 'byung ba lnga po gtso chen yin //
NK101(de)002:3486: sems nyid thig le nyag gcig 'bras bu chos kyi sku de ni /
NK101(de)002:3487: 'byung ba lnga yi sngon rol nas /
NK101(de)002:3488: snga phyi thog mtha' med par gnas pas /
NK101(de)002:3489: 'khor 'das snod bcud thams cad kyi gang nas /
NK101(de)002:3490: rig pa byang chub kyi sems des thams cad bskyed pas don gyi gtso bo chen po yin no //
NK101(de)002:3492: kun tu bzang po'i thig le /
NK101(de)002:3494: dang po rang bzhin kun tu bzang po bstan /
NK101(de)002:3495: gnyis pa rol pa kun tu bzang po /
NK101(de)002:3496: gsum pa rang rig kun tu bzang po /
NK101(de)002:3497: bzhi pa rang byung kun tu bzang po /
NK101(de)002:3498: lnga pa bya bral kun tu bzang po /
NK101(de)002:3499: drug pa 'bras bu kun tu bzang po so sor ma 'dres yongs rdzogs su 'dus pa'o //
NK101(de)002:3500: gzhi ngo bo don bdag nyid chen po'i rang bzhin
NK101(de)002:3501: la bzang ngan dang blang dor med pas kun tu
NK101(de)002:3502: bzang po / ma spros kun la khyab pa dang /
NK101(de)002:3503: gdal khyab chen por gnas pas na thig le zhes bya'o //
NK101(de)002:3504: de bzhi'i rgyas gdab 'agre'o////da ni skabs nyi shu rtsa gnyis pa la'ang /
NK101(de)002:3506: chos nyid skye 'gag med pa la dus gsum ma
NK101(de)002:3507: dmigs pa'i dgongs pa chu bo lta bur rgyun chad
NK101(de)002:3508: med pa'i klong du bstan pa /
NK101(de)002:3509: mnyam pa nyid la phyogs su bya brtsal dang bral ba'i rigs pa bstan pa /
NK101(de)002:3510: kun tu bzang po las lhag par bsgom du med pa'i gtan tshigs bstan pa dang bzhi las /
NK101(de)002:3514: gsang sngags ma h+aa yo ga'i lugs kyis /
NK101(de)002:3515: 'byor ldan yo byad kyi tshogs zer nas /
NK101(de)002:3516: sha chang mar khu dza gad dza ti /
NK101(de)002:3517: zho dang mar la sogs pa la /
NK101(de)002:3518: sha lnga bdud rtsi rnam pa lnga bran nas /
NK101(de)002:3519: za 'thung byed cing rnge'u chung brdung ba ni /
NK101(de)002:3520: khyi rgan za tshol gyi tshogs yin pas gol lo //
NK101(de)002:3521: rdzogs pa chen po a ti yo ga'i tshogs ni /
NK101(de)002:3522: snang srid 'khor 'das yod med rtag chad phyi nang
NK101(de)002:3523: snod bcud kyis bsdus pa'i chos thams cad rang byung
NK101(de)002:3524: ye shes kyi tshogs yin te /
NK101(de)002:3525: de yang yin lugs la 'di yin med pas gang
NK101(de)002:3526: yang mi dmigs pa'i dbyings su mchod pa 'bul ba'i
NK101(de)002:3529: chos kun byang chub sems su 'dus //
NK101(de)002:3530: sems la tshogs kun 'dus pa'i phyir //
NK101(de)002:3531: ye shes dag pa'i tshogs chen pos //
NK101(de)002:3532: tshogs chen dbul ba'i skabs zhes bya //
NK101(de)002:3536: zhes bya ba la sogs pas ston te /
NK101(de)002:3537: 'das pa chos nyid skye ba med pa'i klong du snga phyi thog mtha' med par grol bas /
NK101(de)002:3538: 'khor 'das kyi chos thams cad mi skye /
NK101(de)002:3539: ma 'ongs pa ma nges pa'i klong nas snga phyi thog tha med par shar bas /
NK101(de)002:3541: da lta lhun gyis grub pa'i ngang la snga phyi
NK101(de)002:3542: thog tha med par gnas pas 'khor 'das kyi chos
NK101(de)002:3543: thams cad la skye 'gag gnyis su med de /
NK101(de)002:3544: dus gsum tha dad kyi dmigs pa dang bral ba'i dgongs pa ni chos nyid 'ba' zhig go //
NK101(de)002:3545: chu bo'i gzhung lta bu ni /
NK101(de)002:3547: dus gsum mnyam pa nyid rgyun mi 'chad pa la /
NK101(de)002:3548: dus gsum tha dad ltar shar zhing de ru grol ba'i klong ngo //
NK101(de)002:3549: de la sogs pa'i sangs rgyas gzhan nas btsal du
NK101(de)002:3550: med pas mnyam pa nyid la phyogs su bya btsal
NK101(de)002:3552: bdag nyid ye nas sangs rgyas pas /
NK101(de)002:3553: kun tu bzang po lhag par bsgom du med pa'i gtan tshigs zhes bya'o //
NK101(de)002:3555: 'das dang ma byon da ltar gyis /
NK101(de)002:3556: zhes pa ma h+aa yo ga la sogs pa 'das pa'i sangs rgyas mar me mdzad /
NK101(de)002:3557: ma byon pa'i sangs rgyas rgyal ba byams pa /
NK101(de)002:3558: da ltar gyi rgyal ba sh+aakya thub pa /
NK101(de)002:3559: dus gsum gyi sangs rgyas rim par 'dod pa de la /
NK101(de)002:3560: a ti yo ga gnas sam zhe na /
NK101(de)002:3561: tha snyad mi la mi gnas te //
NK101(de)002:3563: a ti yo ga rdzogs pa chen po chos nyid snga phyi med pa la /
NK101(de)002:3564: dus gsum gyi sangs rgyas rim par grub pa med do //
NK101(de)002:3565: de med pas theg pa 'og ma pa ltar /
NK101(de)002:3566: dus gsum tha dad du 'dod pa'i tha snyad la blo mi gnas te snga phyi med /
NK101(de)002:3567: de cis mi gnas zhe na /
NK101(de)002:3568: skye 'gag med par rnam brtags shing /
NK101(de)002:3569: zhes pa dus gsum chig chod kyi dgongs pa ste /
NK101(de)002:3570: 'das pa chos nyid skye ba med pa'i klong du snga phyi thog mtha' med par grol ba dang /
NK101(de)002:3571: ma 'ongs pa ma nges pa'i klong na snga phyi thog mtha' med par 'char ba dang /
NK101(de)002:3572: da lta lhun gyis grub pa'i klong na snga phyi thog mtha' med par gnas pa dang dus gsum /
NK101(de)002:3573: skye 'gag med par rnam brtags shing //
NK101(de)002:3575: 'o na dus gsum 'gags sam zhe na /
NK101(de)002:3577: de nyid dus gsum chen por sbyor //
NK101(de)002:3578: ces pa dus gsum thig ler theg pa'i dgongs pa ste /
NK101(de)002:3579: thig le nyag gcig la dus gsum tha dad med de /
NK101(de)002:3580: mnyam nyid chen po gcig tu sbyor zhing /
NK101(de)002:3581: gcig po tha dad du ma 'gags pas /
NK101(de)002:3582: gsum ltar yang 'char zhing sbyor ro //
NK101(de)002:3585: mnyam pas rim par bkod pa med //
NK101(de)002:3586: ces pa dkyil 'khor rim par dgod pa'i bya rtsol dang bral ba'i rigs pa ste /
NK101(de)002:3587: ma h+aa yo ga dkyil 'khor rnam pa bzhi la bzang ngan gyi rim pa 'dod pa la /
NK101(de)002:3588: a ti yo ga ting nge 'dzin gyi dkyil 'khor bskyed ma bskyed dang /
NK101(de)002:3589: gzugs brnyan lha'i dkyil 'khor bzhengs ma bzhengs dang /
NK101(de)002:3590: rdul tshon gyi dkyil 'khor bris ma bris dang /
NK101(de)002:3591: rang bzhin gyi dkyil 'khor spyan drangs ma drangs yod tshad /
NK101(de)002:3594: de yo la ma h+aa ltar che chung dang bzang ngan gyi rim pa dgod du med do //
NK101(de)002:3595: gcig pas phyogs su bsngo dang bral //
NK101(de)002:3596: ces pa mchod pa bsngo bgrang du 'bul zhing phyogs
NK101(de)002:3597: su 'dzin pa'i bya rtsol dang bral ba'i rigs pa
NK101(de)002:3598: ste / sangs rgyas dang sems can 'khor ba dang mya ngan las 'das pa'i chos thams cad /
NK101(de)002:3601: 'bras bu rang byung ye shes su gcig pas /
NK101(de)002:3602: rigs bye brag gi khyad par gang la'ang med de /
NK101(de)002:3603: yi dam dang lha tshom bu'i rnam pa la dkyil
NK101(de)002:3604: 'khor gyi dkyil du 'khor lo'i phyogs su mchod pa'i
NK101(de)002:3606: tshogs kyi rgyan rnams bkram pa yang //
NK101(de)002:3607: zhes pa tshogs ched du 'grim pa'i bya rtsol dang bral ba'i rigs pa ste /
NK101(de)002:3608: rgyu bsod nams kyi tshogs ni rdzas dang yo byad phun sum tshogs pa la rag las te /
NK101(de)002:3609: a ti yo ga 'bras bu ye shes kyi tshogs ni /
NK101(de)002:3610: 'khor ba dang mya ngan las 'das pa'i chos thams cad rang byung ye shes kyi tshogs /
NK101(de)002:3612: rig pa phyogs med du bkram pa'o //
NK101(de)002:3613: rang bzhin gnas pa 'grim pa med //
NK101(de)002:3615: ma h+aa yo ga ltar e ma ho la sogs pas ched du 'grim du med de /
NK101(de)002:3616: 'khor 'das kyi chos thams cad ye gdod ma nyid nas rang bzhin gyis ma skyes shing /
NK101(de)002:3617: kun la khyab par gnas pas /
NK101(de)002:3618: rgyu bsod nams kyi tshogs la rag ma las shing /
NK101(de)002:3620: lhun gyis grub pas mi bsngo zhing //
NK101(de)002:3622: smon lam ched du 'debs pa'i bya rtsol dang bral ba'i rigs pa /
NK101(de)002:3623: yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kyi che ba'i yon tan dang 'bras bu'i chos dang /
NK101(de)002:3624: 'jig rten gyi phun sum tshogs pa yang /
NK101(de)002:3625: thig le byang chub kyi sems la ma btsal bzhin du ye nas lhun gyis grub pas /
NK101(de)002:3626: theg pa 'og ma pa ltar smon lam gzhan du
NK101(de)002:3627: mi bsngo ba de cis nas rdzogs pa chen po
NK101(de)002:3628: a ti yo ga'i rnal 'byor pas ye gdod ma
NK101(de)002:3629: nyid nas / 'khor bar 'khyams ma myong ste /
NK101(de)002:3630: lus kyang mi len la gnas kyang mi bsnyeg tsa na /
NK101(de)002:3631: lha mi'i gnas su skye bar shog ces pa'i smon lam zhig de la dgos rgyu med do //
NK101(de)002:3632: gdod nas dag pa bdud rtsi yin //
NK101(de)002:3633: ces pa bdud rtsi ched du 'bul ba'i bya rtsol dang bral ba'i rigs pa /
NK101(de)002:3634: a ti yo ga'i lugs kyis /
NK101(de)002:3635: ye gdod ma nas sems rig pa la bag chags bsog pa'i gnas med de /
NK101(de)002:3636: skyon gyis ma gos shing rnam par dag pa theg pa 'og ma pa phyogs 'dzin gyi bdud la /
NK101(de)002:3637: a ti phyogs med kyi rtsi gtong ba'i bdud rtsi chen po la /
NK101(de)002:3638: ma h+aa yo ga dang a nu ba de ltar ma go ste /
NK101(de)002:3639: shing gi phye ma la mgo nas nar mar sgrub ste /
NK101(de)002:3640: sman gyi phye tshogs la 'debs pa de la dgos pa med par la bazla'o //
NK101(de)002:3642: 'du mched bcu gnyis khyad par las //
NK101(de)002:3643: zhes pa 'du ba ni dbang po drug /
NK101(de)002:3644: mched pa ni yul drug yin te /
NK101(de)002:3645: ma h+aa yo ga pa yul drug dbang po drug
NK101(de)002:3646: gi rtog tshogs las khyad par du gyur pa ni
NK101(de)002:3647: / gnas gyur lha yi dkyil 'khor bsgom pa yin te /
NK101(de)002:3648: lhag pa'i bsam pas gzung ba med //
NK101(de)002:3650: rang ye nas che ba'i gtan tshigs rdzogs pa chen po a ti yo ga'i lugs kyis /
NK101(de)002:3651: chos nyid kun tu bzang po rang la rang chas su gnas pas /
NK101(de)002:3652: ye shes rang snang gi lha yin pa la /
NK101(de)002:3653: de las lhag pa'i lha zhig logs nas bsam pa bzang pos sgom du med par la bzla /
NK101(de)002:3654: gal te de las gzhan du sgom na yid smon
NK101(de)002:3655: lam bzang rtog yin pas bye ma la gser du
NK101(de)002:3657: lha la grub pa'i dus med pa yin no //
NK101(de)002:3658: rgyas gdab 'agre'o////da ni skabs nyi shu rtsa gsum pa la'ang /
NK101(de)002:3660: dran rtog chos nyid du 'char ba'i dgongs pa rgyal
NK101(de)002:3661: po mthong na gnyan pa'i blo skye ba lta bur
NK101(de)002:3662: thug phrad chen po'i klong du bstan pa /
NK101(de)002:3663: snang ba rang grol gyi rigs pa bstan pa /
NK101(de)002:3664: rdzogs pa chen po'i gtan tshigs bstan pa dang bzhi las /
NK101(de)002:3666: rang bzhin gyis lhun gyis grub pa'i skabs /
NK101(de)002:3668: ma h+aa yo ga ba'i tshogs ni /
NK101(de)002:3669: dza gad dza ti zla rgyas zla phrom la sogs pa tshom bu rgyan du 'grims pas na /
NK101(de)002:3670: rgyu bsod nams kyi tshogs yin la /
NK101(de)002:3671: a ti yo ga snang srid 'khor 'das yod med
NK101(de)002:3672: rtag chad phyi nang snod bcud kyis bsdus pa'i chos
NK101(de)002:3673: thams cad rang byung ye shes kyi tshogs chos nyid
NK101(de)002:3674: dbyings kyi rgyan nam rol pa ni /
NK101(de)002:3675: snang ba sna tshogs su shar ba 'di tsam na skye med kyi rgyan yin la /
NK101(de)002:3676: de yang skye 'gag gnyis med du lhun gyis grub nas gnas par ston pa'i skabs la bab bo //
NK101(de)002:3678: chos kun byang chub sems su 'dus //
NK101(de)002:3679: sems de ye shes shar ba'i phyir //
NK101(de)002:3680: tshogs rgyan lhun gyis grub pa'i skabs //
NK101(de)002:3683: yid kyis bsam pa yon bdag ste /
NK101(de)002:3684: bya ba la sogs pas ston te /
NK101(de)002:3685: dran rtog ni yid la ci 'gyus shing /
NK101(de)002:3686: tshogs drug gis gang du btags pa thams cad yin te /
NK101(de)002:3688: a ti yo ga'i lugs kyis mig gis ci mthong thams cad chos nyid cer mthong /
NK101(de)002:3689: yid la ci bsam thams cad ye shes klong rdol /
NK101(de)002:3690: lus ngag gis ci byas thams cad shugs 'byung rang shar gyi chos nyid la /
NK101(de)002:3691: dgongs pa ni de'i ngang las mi 'da' bas /
NK101(de)002:3694: dper na 'khor los sgyur ba'i rgyal po mthong ba
NK101(de)002:3695: tsam gyis mgo nag phal pa las gnyan pa'i blo
NK101(de)002:3697: yul drug mthong ba tsam gyis thams cad chos sku
NK101(de)002:3698: thug phrad las shar zhing grol ba'i ngo bo shes
NK101(de)002:3699: pas klong ngo // de la yul sems gnyis su med pas snang ba rang grol gyi rigs pa /
NK101(de)002:3700: thams cad de ru 'dus pas rdzogs pa chen po'i gtan tshigs so //
NK101(de)002:3702: yid kyis bsam pa yon bdag ste /
NK101(de)002:3704: yid la ci bsam blo la ci shar thams cad
NK101(de)002:3705: ni rang byung ye shes kyi gzhi byas pa'i yon
NK101(de)002:3707: dper na yon bdag ni rdzas thams cad la gtor zhing dbang sgyur ba dang 'dra bar /
NK101(de)002:3708: 'khor 'das kyi chos thams cad rigs pa byang chub kyi sems phyogs med dbang sgyur bas /
NK101(de)002:3709: rig pa byang chub kyi sems bya bral gyi klong
NK101(de)002:3710: chen po de ni 'khor 'das thams cad kyi yon
NK101(de)002:3712: bltas pas tshogs ni bkram pa yin //
NK101(de)002:3714: chos nyid cer mthong gi dgongs pa de /
NK101(de)002:3715: rdzogs pa chen po'i rnal 'byor pas /
NK101(de)002:3716: mig gis ci mthong thams cad chos nyid cer mthong gi lta ba yin te /
NK101(de)002:3717: chos nyid zang thal la ye shes rang shar bas /
NK101(de)002:3718: snang srid thams cad chos nyid rigs pa'i rgyan du bkram pa la /
NK101(de)002:3719: yul dang yul can gnyis su grub pa med do //
NK101(de)002:3722: mthong bar gyur pas dngos grub la //
NK101(de)002:3725: a ti yo ga pas mig gis ci mthong thams cad ni /
NK101(de)002:3726: chos nyid zang thal gyi lha dngos su grub pa dang /
NK101(de)002:3727: yid la ci bsam thams cad ye shes klong rdol gyi sgom pa dngos su grub pas so //
NK101(de)002:3728: lus ngag gis ci byas pa thams cad shugs 'byung
NK101(de)002:3729: rang shar gyi spyod pa dngos su grub pa dang
NK101(de)002:3730: / ci dang ci ru snang ba thams cad /
NK101(de)002:3731: rang shar rang grol gyi 'bras bu dngos su grub
NK101(de)002:3732: pas theg pa 'og ma pa ltar da gdod bsgrub
NK101(de)002:3733: tu med par bstan pa ni dngos grub chen po'o
NK101(de)002:3735: dngos grub dngos grub ces bya ba //
NK101(de)002:3736: gud na yod pa ma yin te //
NK101(de)002:3737: dngos ni rang gi byang chub sems //
NK101(de)002:3738: grub pa rtogs pa mngon du gyur //
NK101(de)002:3739: dngos grub ces kyang de la bya //
NK101(de)002:3742: de nyid mnyam bzhag rdzogs pa'o //
NK101(de)002:3743: zhes pa snang srid 'khor 'das yod med rtag chad
NK101(de)002:3744: phyi nang snod bcud kyi bsdus pa'i chos thams cad
NK101(de)002:3745: / gzhi ngo bo don bdag nyid mnyam pa chen po'i rang bzhin du dbyer med pas mnyam bzhag /
NK101(de)002:3746: de yang snang ba stong pa ru rdzogs /
NK101(de)002:3750: snang grags kyi chos thams cad rig pa la phyogs med par rdzogs pas na /
NK101(de)002:3751: rdzogs pa chen po zhes bya'o //
NK101(de)002:3752: rgyas gdab 'agre'o////da ni skabs nyi shu rtsa bzhi pa la'ang /
NK101(de)002:3754: sbyor ba btang bzhag med pa'i dgongs pa tsha la
NK101(de)002:3755: dang gar sbyin lta bur 'du 'bral med pa'i klong
NK101(de)002:3756: du bstan pa / dbye bsal blang dor med pa'i rigs pa bstan pa /
NK101(de)002:3757: dbyer med rang shar gyi gtan tshigs bstan pa dang bzhi las /
NK101(de)002:3760: zhes pa a ti yo ga'i lugs kyis /
NK101(de)002:3761: rgyu sems can gyi dus na 'bras bu sangs rgyas kyi ye shes lhun gyis grub nas gnas /
NK101(de)002:3762: snang ba'i dus na stong pa /
NK101(de)002:3763: sdug bsngal gyi dus na bde ba /
NK101(de)002:3764: chos can gyi dus na chos nyid /
NK101(de)002:3765: 'khor 'das kyi dus nas rig par lhun gyi grub nas gnas pas /
NK101(de)002:3766: gnyis su med pa'i don zab mo ston pa'i skabs la bab bo //
NK101(de)002:3768: chos kun byang chub sems su 'dus //
NK101(de)002:3769: sems nyid lhun gyis grub pa'i phyir //
NK101(de)002:3770: lhun gyis grub pa'i skabs zhes bya //
NK101(de)002:3773: yud tsam bzung bas sbyor ba yin //
NK101(de)002:3775: 'khor 'das rtag chad phyi nang snod bcud gnyis bsdus kyi chos thams cad gang sbyor na /
NK101(de)002:3776: gzhi'i dus na lhun gyis grub par sbyor /
NK101(de)002:3777: ngo bo don bdag nyid la thog mtha' med par sbyor bas na /
NK101(de)002:3778: don gyi sbyor ba chen po yin te /
NK101(de)002:3780: btang bzhag kyang med pa'i dgongs pa chos nyid kyi ngang ngo //
NK101(de)002:3781: gar sbyin lta bu ni rgyas thebs pa'i dpe ste /
NK101(de)002:3782: dbyings dang ye shes gzhi dang ngo bo dbyer med cing 'du 'bral med pas /
NK101(de)002:3783: thams cad de las shar zhing de ru grol ba'i klong ngo //
NK101(de)002:3784: de la cir snang chos nyid yin pas /
NK101(de)002:3785: dbye bsal blang dor med pa'i rigs pa /
NK101(de)002:3786: gcig pa kun tu shar bas dbyer med rang shar gyi gtan tshigs zhes bya'o //
NK101(de)002:3788: yud tsam bzung bas sbyor ba yin //
NK101(de)002:3789: ces pa chos nyid skye 'gag med pa'i don 'di la /
NK101(de)002:3790: yun ring po dang lta ci smos te /
NK101(de)002:3791: skad cig tsam du rtogs pa phyogs med du shar bas kyang /
NK101(de)002:3792: chos nyid phyogs med mnyam pa chen po'i don la sbyor ba yin te /
NK101(de)002:3793: snang zhing srid pa'i chos thams cad /
NK101(de)002:3794: gzhi lhun gyis grub pa la /
NK101(de)002:3796: ngo bo nges pa med pa la cir yang 'char bar sbyor ba dang /
NK101(de)002:3797: don skye ba med pa la gnyis su med par sbyor ba dang /
NK101(de)002:3798: bdag nyid thog tha med pa la rgyun mi 'chad pa'i chos nyid du sbyor bas na /
NK101(de)002:3799: sbyor ba chen po'i dgongs pa'o //
NK101(de)002:3802: dga' bar gyur pa dam tshig ste /
NK101(de)002:3804: cir snang cir srid thams cad chos nyid 'ba' zhig la /
NK101(de)002:3805: skyon yon dang bzang ngan gang du'ang mi lta bas /
NK101(de)002:3806: spyod yul gang du shar ba thams cad la /
NK101(de)002:3807: dga' bar lhag lhag shes nas /
NK101(de)002:3808: ci byas chos nyid kyi klong las mi 'da' ba ni /
NK101(de)002:3809: bsrung mtshams dang 'da' nyams med pa'i dam tshig chen po yin no //
NK101(de)002:3811: thabs kyi gar thabs bskyod pa yis //
NK101(de)002:3812: zhes pa thabs rang shar gyi gtan tshigs gzhi lhun grub bya ba med pa thabs kyi rgyal po /
NK101(de)002:3813: ngo bo ma nges pa gar thabs phyogs med du bskyod pas na /
NK101(de)002:3814: gnyis med sbyor ba phul ba yin //
NK101(de)002:3815: ces pa gnyis med kyi gtan tshigs te /
NK101(de)002:3816: rol pa ci shar thabs yin te /
NK101(de)002:3817: don skye med la 'dzin pa med pa shes rab kyi rgyal po bya bral gyi dbyings /
NK101(de)002:3818: 'khor 'das gnyis su med cing mnyam pa nyid du sbyor bas /
NK101(de)002:3819: sbyor ba chen po'i mchod pa 'bul ba yin no //
NK101(de)002:3820: rgyas gdab 'agre'o////da ni skabs nyi shu rtsa lnga pa la'ang /
NK101(de)002:3822: gzung 'dzin bya brtsal med pa'i dgongs pa skyi bser
NK101(de)002:3823: lta bur zhen chags med pa'i klong du bstan pa
NK101(de)002:3824: / rtogs pa bar chad med pa'i rigs pa bstan pa /
NK101(de)002:3825: brjod du med pa'i gtan tshigs bstan pa dang bzhi las /
NK101(de)002:3829: ma h+aa yo ga'i phrin las /
NK101(de)002:3830: zhi rgyas dbang dang mngon spyod la sogs pa thams cad ni /
NK101(de)002:3831: rgya mtsho'i kha'i chu bur dang 'dra ste /
NK101(de)002:3833: bden bden 'dra la mi bden pa /
NK101(de)002:3834: a ti yo ga rdzogs pa chen po bya ba
NK101(de)002:3835: med pa'i phrin las rgya mtsho'i 'jings dang 'dra ba
NK101(de)002:3837: thams cad de ru 'dus par ston pa'i skabs la bab bo //
NK101(de)002:3839: chos kun byang chub sems su 'dus //
NK101(de)002:3840: sems la rtsol sgrub med pa'i phyir //
NK101(de)002:3841: phrin las rgya mtsho'i skabs zhes bya //
NK101(de)002:3844: mi gzung gtong bas gtor ma yin //
NK101(de)002:3846: rdzogs pa chen po a ti yo ga'i lugs kyis /
NK101(de)002:3847: 'khor 'das snod bcud kyis bsdus pa'i chos thams cad /
NK101(de)002:3848: 'dzin med kyi rang shar du byung ba yin te /
NK101(de)002:3851: sangs rgyas sems can gnyis kar mi 'dzin /
NK101(de)002:3853: mdor na gang du yang mi 'dzin pas /
NK101(de)002:3854: gnyis bsdus thams cad de ltar du shes pa ni /
NK101(de)002:3855: 'dzin pa med pa shes rab kyi rgyal po yin te /
NK101(de)002:3856: des la dgag rgyu dang sgrub rgyu ci yang med pas bya btsal med pa'i dgongs pa /
NK101(de)002:3858: skyi bser lta bu ni zhen pa med pa'i dpe ste /
NK101(de)002:3859: a nu man chad kyi spyod yul gang la spyod kyang rang shar rang grol du shes pas /
NK101(de)002:3860: gang la'ang ma zhan par grol ba'i klong ngo //
NK101(de)002:3861: de la zhe 'dod med pas rtogs pa bar chad med pa'i rigs pa /
NK101(de)002:3862: de la tha snyad med pas brjod du med pa'i gtan tshigs so //
NK101(de)002:3864: mi gzung gtong bas gtor ma yin //
NK101(de)002:3865: zhes pa ye shes sbyin gtong phyogs med du gtong ba'i dgongs pa /
NK101(de)002:3866: rdzogs pa chen po phyogs ris dang bral ba'i sbyin gtong chen po ni /
NK101(de)002:3867: gzhi phyogs med la phyogs su mi gzung /
NK101(de)002:3868: ngo bo nges med la mtha' ru mi gzung /
NK101(de)002:3869: don skye med la gnyis su mi gzung /
NK101(de)002:3870: chos nyid mu mtha' med pa la /
NK101(de)002:3871: rig pa gang dgar gtong zhing /
NK101(de)002:3872: phyogs dang ris su mi 'dzin pa ni /
NK101(de)002:3873: ye shes kyi sbyin gtong chen po phyogs ris med par btang ba'o //
NK101(de)002:3874: bya ba med pa'i las rnams te /
NK101(de)002:3875: zhes pa phrin las dus gcig tu zin pa'i dgongs pa ste /
NK101(de)002:3876: sems la gzung 'dzin bya rtsol r+ts+wa rtse tsam yang med par go na /
NK101(de)002:3877: 'di dang phyi ma'i phrin las thams cad dus gcig la 'grub ste /
NK101(de)002:3878: ci yang bya mi dgos pa'i gnad kyis so //
NK101(de)002:3881: mi rtog ye shes bgegs bsal nas //
NK101(de)002:3882: zhes pa mtshams la bar chod med pa'i rigs pa /
NK101(de)002:3883: a ti yo ga'i lugs kyis /
NK101(de)002:3884: gzhi phyogs med la phyogs 'dzin du mi rtog /
NK101(de)002:3886: don la gnyis 'dzin gang du'ang mi rtog ste /
NK101(de)002:3887: rnam par mi rtog rang byung ye shes chen po des /
NK101(de)002:3888: phyi'i bgegs bgegs rigs stong phrag brgyad cus tshe la bar du gcod /
NK101(de)002:3889: nang gi bgegs nyon mongs dug lnga dang dug gsum
NK101(de)002:3890: gyis rtogs pa la bar du gcod pa thams cad
NK101(de)002:3891: phyi nang med cing mnyam nyid chen po dus gcig
NK101(de)002:3892: la rang shar te gnyis su med par rang gsal
NK101(de)002:3893: ba'o // de ltar ma shes na /
NK101(de)002:3894: bgegs yul dang yul can du bzung nas bskrad skad kyang /
NK101(de)002:3895: rang las byung ba'i rol pa yin pas /
NK101(de)002:3898: mi gsungs mnyam nyid sngags tshig go //
NK101(de)002:3899: zhes pa chos nyid smra brjod dang bral ba'i klong na rig pa bde blag chen por gnas na /
NK101(de)002:3900: de kho na don gyi sngags tshig gi bzlas pa ma nor ba yin pas /
NK101(de)002:3902: mtha' ru 'dzin pa'i tha snyad med na /
NK101(de)002:3903: h'u dang phatahkyi bzlas pa bya mi dgos so //
NK101(de)002:3904: rgyas gdab 'agre'o////da ni skabs nyi shu rtsa drug pa la yang /
NK101(de)002:3906: 'khor gsum yongs su dag pa'i dgongs pa /
NK101(de)002:3907: shes sgong g.ya' dag pa lta bu dri ma med pa'i klong du bstan pa /
NK101(de)002:3908: ngo bo 'di yin du mi rtog pa'i rigs pa bstan pa /
NK101(de)002:3909: chags na 'ching ba'i gtan tshigs bstan pa dang bzhi las /
NK101(de)002:3911: bdag dang bcas pas gtor ma 'ching ba'i skabs //
NK101(de)002:3912: zhes pa gang la bdag 'dzin yod na de la 'ching ba yod de /
NK101(de)002:3913: theg pa 'og ma sbyin gtong ci byas pa thams cad dngos po'am mtshan ma can du song bas /
NK101(de)002:3914: zhen pa de dang ma bral na slar la 'ching bar ston pa'i skabs la bab bo //
NK101(de)002:3916: chos kun byang chub sems su 'dus //
NK101(de)002:3917: sems nyid chags shing g.yo med la //
NK101(de)002:3918: ma chags mi g.yo'i sems med pas //
NK101(de)002:3919: 'ching ba chen po'i skabs zhes bya //
NK101(de)002:3922: bla ma mchod dang gtong ba dang //
NK101(de)002:3924: yar la bla ma dang dkon mchog mchod pa dang /
NK101(de)002:3925: mar la sbyin gtong rgya che chung gang byed kyang /
NK101(de)002:3928: gtang bar bya ba'i rdzas dang gsum ka mi dmigs te /
NK101(de)002:3929: dmigs pa'i yul las 'das par bstan pas /
NK101(de)002:3930: 'khor gsum yongs su dag pa chos nyid kyi klong ngo //
NK101(de)002:3931: shes sgong g.ya' dag pa lta bu ni /
NK101(de)002:3932: phyi nang med cing dri mas ma gos pa'i dpe yin te /
NK101(de)002:3933: 'jig rten chos brgyad kyi dri ma med par go ba la /
NK101(de)002:3934: yon tan thams cad 'byung zhing de ru 'dus pa'i klong ngo //
NK101(de)002:3935: de la tshad gzung med pa ni //
NK101(de)002:3936: ngo bo 'di yin du mi rtog pa'i rigs pa /
NK101(de)002:3937: yul dang yul can du 'dzin pa'i 'khrul pa chags na 'ching ba'i gtan tshigs zhes bya'o //
NK101(de)002:3939: bla ma mchod dang gtong ba dang //
NK101(de)002:3942: gtong ba la mar bltas gnyis 'dzin gyi dgongs pa yin te /
NK101(de)002:3944: don gyi bla ma dang rtags kyi bla ma'o //
NK101(de)002:3945: don gyi bla ma ni sems can rang rang gi
NK101(de)002:3946: rig pa thig le nyag gcig byang chub kyi sems
NK101(de)002:3947: yin no // de gang gis mchod na /
NK101(de)002:3948: go ba klong du gyur na rtogs pa nyi ma shar ba lta bu'i sgo nas mchod pa yin /
NK101(de)002:3950: bdag la lung dang man ngag gi don ma nor bar ston pa'i dge ba'i bshes gnyen yin pas /
NK101(de)002:3951: de yang mchod lugs gnyis te /
NK101(de)002:3952: chos kyi mchod pas rgyud bzung ba dang /
NK101(de)002:3953: zang zing gi mchod pas rgyud tshim par bya ba'o //
NK101(de)002:3955: bla mas ji ltar bstan pa'i bka' srol ma nor bar gzhan la ston shes pas na /
NK101(de)002:3956: bla ma'i thugs rgyud bzung bar 'gro bas /
NK101(de)002:3957: bla ma mnyes pa rab yin no //
NK101(de)002:3960: rgyal srid dang ni rang gi lus //
NK101(de)002:3961: bu dang chung ma nor gyi dbyig /
NK101(de)002:3964: de yang rab shes rab kyis ma nyes pa /
NK101(de)002:3966: tha ma zang zing nor gyis mnyes par bya'o //
NK101(de)002:3968: yar la dkon mchog mchod pa dang /
NK101(de)002:3969: mar la snying rje ba rnams la sbyin gtong skyabs
NK101(de)002:3970: dang zang zing chos kyi sbyin pa gsum las gang
NK101(de)002:3971: byed kyang ngo // de bzhin bsod nams thams cad kyang //
NK101(de)002:3973: lta ba srog dang ldan pa'i dgongs pa ste /
NK101(de)002:3974: lar bsod nams rang la thun mong dang /
NK101(de)002:3975: thun mong min pa gnyis las /
NK101(de)002:3976: rang dang gzhan gyi bsod nams glang po chu chod kha lan ngo srung med pa'o //
NK101(de)002:3977: de yang ma zad gzhan gyi 'dus byas kyi dge rtsa bya'o cog la zer /
NK101(de)002:3978: de yo gong du bstan pa bzhin 'khor gsum yongs
NK101(de)002:3979: dag gi rtsis zin dgongs pas na mi dmigs par
NK101(de)002:3982: ma chags mi g.yo'i stobs med na //
NK101(de)002:3983: zhes pa ched du bya ba med pa'i rigs pa ston te /
NK101(de)002:3984: de gang la'ang ma chags pa'i lta ba rtogs pa dang /
NK101(de)002:3985: mi g.yo ba'i dgongs pa brtan pa dang /
NK101(de)002:3986: mi dmigs pa'i sbyin stobs ldan pa dang /
NK101(de)002:3987: phyogs med kyi nyams myong gsal ba dang bzhi med na mi grol zhes pa'o //
NK101(de)002:3992: 'dus byas kyi dge rtsa gang la yang /
NK101(de)002:3993: ngas byas dang rlom sems dang /
NK101(de)002:3994: phyogs 'dzin gyis byas na slar la 'ching ba chen por 'gyur la /
NK101(de)002:3995: ngas byas dang rlom sems phyogs su 'dzin pa med
NK101(de)002:3996: na ma byas kyang grol ba chen por 'gyur ro
NK101(de)002:3997: // rgyas gdab 'agre'o////da ni skabs nyi shu rtsa bdun pa la'ang /
NK101(de)002:3999: lung chen sgrog grol gyi dgongs pa gyi ling sgrog
NK101(de)002:4000: bkrol ba lta bu yan pa chen po'i klong du
NK101(de)002:4001: bstan pa / gnas skabs 'dra gzhi dang nor ba'i rigs pa bstan pa /
NK101(de)002:4002: 'dod pa thog tu ma phebs pa'i gtan tshigs bstan pa /
NK101(de)002:4003: thig le'i nges tshig bstan pa dang lnga las /
NK101(de)002:4005: lung 'grel ba ming tsam brdar bstan pa'i skabs //
NK101(de)002:4007: lung gis gtan la 'bebs pa'i drang lung dang /
NK101(de)002:4008: mngon du phyung ba'i drang lung thams cad /
NK101(de)002:4009: a ti yo ga rdzogs pa chen po rna brgyud zab mo'i nges lung phyogs med du bkrol nas /
NK101(de)002:4010: rdo rje sems dpa' nam mkha' che dbu zhabs thams cad bsdus pa de /
NK101(de)002:4011: brda' 'am zur du bkral nas mngon par bstan pa'i skabs la bab bo //
NK101(de)002:4014: chos kun byang chub sems su 'dus //
NK101(de)002:4015: sems nyid chos kyi khungs yin phyir //
NK101(de)002:4016: lung chen 'grel ba'i skabs zhes bya //
NK101(de)002:4019: de bas de lung de nyid las //
NK101(de)002:4022: rna ba nas rna bar brgyud pa'i lung dang /
NK101(de)002:4023: mngon du phyung ba'i lung dang /
NK101(de)002:4024: gtan la 'bebs pa'i lung dang gsum /
NK101(de)002:4025: 'di gtan la 'bebs pa'i drang lung a nu yo ga man chad dang /
NK101(de)002:4026: mngon du phyung ba'i drang lung la mi zer te /
NK101(de)002:4027: de'i gnas skabs su rna ba nas rna bar brgyud pa'i nges lung du bstan te /
NK101(de)002:4028: rgyal ba dgongs pa'i brgyud pa /
NK101(de)002:4030: gang zag snyan khung du brgyud pa'i lung ngo //
NK101(de)002:4031: man ngag zab mo rdo rje sems dpa' nam mkha' che 'di bstan pas /
NK101(de)002:4032: nyon mongs pa lcags sgrog dang 'dra ba las grol ba chos nyid kyi klong ngo //
NK101(de)002:4033: gyi ling sgrog bkrol ba ni kha yan du 'gro ba'i dpe yin te /
NK101(de)002:4034: rdzogs pa chen po'i rnal 'byor pas /
NK101(de)002:4035: mi mthun pa dang gnyen por 'dzin pa'i lcags sgrog med par /
NK101(de)002:4036: 'khor 'das kyi chos thams cad la rang yan tshugs te /
NK101(de)002:4037: gang gis kyang 'ching grol med pa'i ngang la /
NK101(de)002:4038: thams cad shar zhing de ru grol bas klong ngo //
NK101(de)002:4039: de la rtsol sgrub byed na theg pa 'og ma ba dang khyad med pas /
NK101(de)002:4040: gnas skabs 'dra zhing nor ba'i rigs pa /
NK101(de)002:4041: 'bras bu ched du 'dod na gol sa yin pas
NK101(de)002:4042: 'dod pa thog tu mi phebs pa'i gtan tshigs byung
NK101(de)002:4044: de bas de lung de nyid las //
NK101(de)002:4046: de bas ni gong la bsnyegs pa'i tshig la gong
NK101(de)002:4047: du gsungs pa bzhin du snang srid 'khor 'das kyi
NK101(de)002:4048: chos thams cad / gzhi gnas ye grol bya bral
NK101(de)002:4049: klong chen gyi ngang du sangs rgyas pa yin pas
NK101(de)002:4050: chos thams cad / / de bas na /
NK101(de)002:4051: de ni lung thams cad kyi nang nas kyang /
NK101(de)002:4052: bya bral rdzogs pa'i lung thams cad 'dus pa yin
NK101(de)002:4053: pas lung gi rgyal po nyid du rigs par bya
NK101(de)002:4054: ste / byang chub sems la 'dus pa lags /
NK101(de)002:4055: lar lung bya ba de rgyud na kha 'thor zhing dkrugs nas yod pa rnams la /
NK101(de)002:4057: snod la lung btags pa lta bur spyod bde ba'am nyams su blang bde ba la zer te /
NK101(de)002:4059: rgyud kyi don lam bsdebs pa'i lung zhes bya //
NK101(de)002:4060: rnam grangs rgyan du bkod pas phreng ba ste //
NK101(de)002:4062: de'i skyon bsal dang la bzla 'dra /
NK101(de)002:4064: de la de byar sgrib par 'gyur //
NK101(de)002:4066: bya bral klong chen zab mo yis /
NK101(de)002:4067: zhes pa'i lung de yang snying por nges pa'i bsgrub byar bzung ste de nyid rtogs par 'dod nas /
NK101(de)002:4068: mnyam pa nyid la rtsol sgrub byas pas /
NK101(de)002:4069: theg pa 'og ma pa'i drang lung rtsol sems can dang nor te /
NK101(de)002:4070: slar chos nyid zab mo'i don ma rtogs te /
NK101(de)002:4071: mnyam pa nyid la rtsol sems bcug pa phyogs med kyi don la sgrib par 'gyur ro //
NK101(de)002:4073: de ltar de la de rtog na //
NK101(de)002:4074: zhes pa bzang rtog ched du byed na mi grol ba'i gtan tshigs bstan te /
NK101(de)002:4075: de ltar de bzhin nyid kyi lung /
NK101(de)002:4078: rgyu rkyen gnyen po gang gis kyang ma bskyed pa'i chos nyid phyogs med de la /
NK101(de)002:4085: bdag gzhan gnyis su rtog cing phyogs med la phyogs su bltas pas nor ro //
NK101(de)002:4086: de la de nyid 'grub pa med //
NK101(de)002:4087: ces pa gnyis 'dzin can gyis mi 'grub pa'i gtan tshigs bstan te /
NK101(de)002:4089: ye nas gzhi gnas ye grol bya bral klong chen po mnyam pa nyidakyi ngang du sangs rgyas pas /
NK101(de)002:4090: a nu yo ga man chad kyis de ltar ma go ste /
NK101(de)002:4092: skyon yon gnyis su 'dzin pa can de las /
NK101(de)002:4093: de bzhin nyid ma nor ma bcos pa'i don la
NK101(de)002:4094: phyogs pa med de 'grub pa'i dus med pa lags
NK101(de)002:4096: lhun gyis grub pa'i thig le /
NK101(de)002:4098: dang po bye brag lhun gyis grub pa /
NK101(de)002:4099: gnyis pa rang bzhin lhun gyis grub pa /
NK101(de)002:4100: gsum pa gnyis su med par lhun gyis grub pa /
NK101(de)002:4101: bzhi pa mnyam pa nyid du lhun gyis grub pa /
NK101(de)002:4102: lnga pa ma chags par lhun gyis grub pa /
NK101(de)002:4103: drug pa de bzhin nyid du lhun gyis grub par ston /
NK101(de)002:4104: ma spangs la rang grol bas na lhun gyis grub pa /
NK101(de)002:4105: ma spros kun la khyab cing gdal khyab chen por gnas pas na thig le zhes bya'o //
NK101(de)002:4106: 'o na dpe don rigs pa gtan tshigs bzhi po de tha dad dam zhe na /
NK101(de)002:4107: bshad pa dkyus thog tu btang ba'i dbang du byas na de ltar 'gro la /
NK101(de)002:4108: gdams ngag don thog tu dril na /
NK101(de)002:4109: tshig rkang lnga po 'dir 'dus te bshad tshod de
NK101(de)002:4110: dag thams cad kyi mdo thig le nyag gcig tu
NK101(de)002:4111: bsdu ba dang / 'gag bya rtsol med par bsdam pa dang /
NK101(de)002:4112: gnad 'khor 'das dbyer med du bkrol ba dang /
NK101(de)002:4113: phugs thag da ltar gyi snang ba la bcad pa dang /
NK101(de)002:4114: 'gro sa chos kyi dbyings su btang ba dang lngar 'dus so //
NK101(de)002:4115: de tsho hril gyis dril bas /
NK101(de)002:4118: skabs nyi shu rtsa bdun gyi sgo nas /
NK101(de)002:4119: rdo rje sems dpa' nam mkha' che /
NK101(de)002:4120: lung thams cad kyi bdag nyid /
NK101(de)002:4121: dpal rdo rje sems dpa'i zhal nas gsungs pa rdzogs so //
NK101(de)002:4122: dpe don rigs pa gtan tshigs bzhi bstan pa /
NK101(de)002:4123: slob dpon sh+r+ai sing+ha'i dgongs pa ste /
NK101(de)002:4124: gzu lums ras chad mkhan la shor ba re //
NK101(de)002:4125: rin chen gser bas dkon pa'i man ngag 'di //
NK101(de)002:4126: mi nub rgyal mtshan snying gi nying khu yin //
NK101(de)002:4127: bee ro tsa na thugs kyis brnag par chongs //
NK101(de)002:4128: zhes pas rgya gdab par gsal lo //
NK101(de)002:4131: de ltar zab las ches zab snying po'i don //
NK101(de)002:4132: rang snang chos dbyings 'od gsal gdod ma'i gzhi //
NK101(de)002:4133: mtshon bya zab don gnyug ma gshis kyi bab //
NK101(de)002:4134: gab spas med par rang ngo rjen par snang //
NK101(de)002:4135: 'on kyang mtha' bral phyogs ris grol ba'i dbyings //
NK101(de)002:4136: khyab gdal rig pa nyag gcig thig le'i ngang //
NK101(de)002:4137: dmus long dag la gzi ldan nyi ma bzhin //
NK101(de)002:4138: phyogs lhung blo ngor rang gsang thabs kyis chod //
NK101(de)002:4139: de phyir lung dang rigs pa man ngag gis //
NK101(de)002:4140: gzur gnas skal bzang blo dang ldan pa la //
NK101(de)002:4141: ma nor rdzogs pa chen po'i don mtshon phyir //
NK101(de)002:4142: sku gsum dgongs bcud rin chen 'phrul gyi thabs //
NK101(de)002:4143: tshul 'dir gzhi lam 'bras bu'i nges gsang gi //
NK101(de)002:4144: gnad kun ma 'dres yongs su rdzogs pa'i phyir //
NK101(de)002:4145: rtogs par dka' yang ji bzhin mthong tsa na //
NK101(de)002:4146: theg mchog rgyal po'i dgongs don lhun po ltar //
NK101(de)002:4147: kun grol kun las 'das shing kun gyi bcud //
NK101(de)002:4148: theg pa kun rdzogs kun gyi yang snying du //
NK101(de)002:4149: mthong ba'i blo mig nyi zla'i 'od bzhin 'char //
NK101(de)002:4150: des na rigs ldan d+r+wa mas nan tan mdzod //
NK101(de)002:4151: sngon byon mkhas grub brgyud pa'i rnam thar bzhin //
NK101(de)002:4152: legs par shes pa'i dad ldan blo gsal rnams //
NK101(de)002:4153: shes rab tshad mas snying po'i chos nyid la //
NK101(de)002:4154: go ba klung du gyur tshe nges shes 'char //
NK101(de)002:4155: de phyir brgyud pa'i ring lugs ma nor bar //
NK101(de)002:4156: 'khrul med nges pa'i lung gis zur brgyan te //
NK101(de)002:4157: gdams ngag snying po dus kyi yang mtha' 'dir //
NK101(de)002:4158: bla ma'i bka' la brten nas gsal bar byas //
NK101(de)002:4159: de ltar brgyud gsum nor bu'i zhal lung bzhin //
NK101(de)002:4160: man ngag tshad ma'i lam mchog cud zad bkral //
NK101(de)002:4161: gang de'i dge bas mkha' khyab 'gro ba kun //
NK101(de)002:4162: gdod ma'i rgyal sar mngon par byang chub shog /
NK101(de)002:4163: bkra shis gang zhig sku gsum ston pa nas //
NK101(de)002:4164: rim brgyud rig 'dzin gong ma'i snyan rgyud don //
NK101(de)002:4165: blo ldan skyes bu'i dgongs pa rtsal rdzogs te //
NK101(de)002:4166: bstan pa'i snying po phyogs mthar rgyas gyur cig /
NK101(de)002:4167: de ltar rdo rje sems dpa' nam mkha' che'i 'grel
NK101(de)002:4168: chung 'di nyid rig 'dzin chen po sh+r+ai sid+hasa lo
NK101(de)002:4169: chen bee ro tsa na la snyan rgyud du stsal
NK101(de)002:4170: ba'i dpe rnying ji lta ba bzhin la yig nyams
NK101(de)002:4171: gso ba dang / mdo chen po'i dka' gnad la
NK101(de)002:4172: brten pa'i dgos pa dang bstun te che ba dang
NK101(de)002:4173: thig le rnams cung zad bkral nas lung gi spras
NK101(de)002:4174: te sngar zhig mchog sprul kun tu bzang po nas
NK101(de)002:4175: nam mkha' che la nan tan byed bar ma 'chugs
NK101(de)002:4176: gso ba dang / gsungs pa dang / rjes sor
NK101(de)002:4177: skyabs rje rigs bdag bka' drin mtshungs med mkhan chen
NK101(de)002:4178: legs bshad dul pa'i sdes sems phyogs la'ang gsal byed
NK101(de)002:4179: kyi yi ge re cis kyang gyis shig ces bka'
NK101(de)002:4181: mchog sprul pad+ma tshul khrims gyis kyang gsung bskul bri
NK101(de)002:4182: gzhi bcas gnang ba la brten nas sprang 'khyams thub
NK101(de)002:4183: bstan mkhyen brtse'i blo gros kyis 'og min kahthoga gi
NK101(de)002:4184: yang dben gser khang ri khrod bdud 'dus phrin las
NK101(de)002:4185: kun khyab gling gi gzims spyil 'od gsal theg mchog
NK101(de)002:4186: mdzod khang nas zhal bshus te rdzogs par bgyis pa
NK101(de)002:4187: 'dis kyang rgyal bstan spyi dang snga 'gyur mdo sgyu
NK101(de)002:4188: sems gsum gyi bstan pa rin po che phyogs dus
NK101(de)002:4189: kun tu dar zhing rgyas pa'i rgyur gyur cig /
NK101(de)002:4190: chos nyid bde gshegs snying po'i klong chen por //
NK101(de)002:4191: 'khor 'das lam gyi snang ba ji snyed pa //
NK101(de)002:4192: mnyam nyid khyab brdal chen por byang chub pa'i //
NK101(de)002:4193: theg mchog 'od gsal rdo rje snying po che //
NK101(de)002:4194: de yi rgyud kyi rtsa ba nam mkha' che //
NK101(de)002:4195: rdo rje sems dpa'i dgongs pa'i gnad gcig pu'i //
NK101(de)002:4196: chos sgo rin chen nor bu'i mdzod chen po //
NK101(de)002:4197: mkhan chen mkhyen brtse blo gros mchog gis phyes //
NK101(de)002:4198: de yi bka' drin dran phyir rtsa 'grel spar //
NK101(de)002:4199: gsung gi bdud rtsi myong ba'i slob tshogs nas //
NK101(de)002:4200: lhag bsam dkar pos bsgrubs pa'i dge tshogs kyis //
NK101(de)002:4201: 'gro rnams 'od gsal lam mchog mthar phyin shog //
NK101(de)002:4202: ces spar gzhi'i mthun rkyen sogs mkhan chen rin po
NK101(de)002:4203: ches sbyar nas gus pa slob tshogs rnams kyis spar
NK101(de)002:4204: gsar du bskrun pa'i skabs 'jam dpal bzang pos smon
